NK129(to)003:1: // chos 'byung bstan pa'i sgron me rtsod bzlog seng ge'i nga ro zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK129(to)003:3: na mo gu ru b+hud+d+h+aa ya /
NK129(to)003:6: thub dbang stobs sogs yon tan kun gyi mdzod mnga' ba //
NK129(to)003:7: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes mngon gyur cing //
NK129(to)003:8: yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa'i nyon mongs rab zhi zhing //
NK129(to)003:9: bden pa gnyis kyi yang dag dam chos rin chen dang //
NK129(to)003:10: nyan thos sde gnyis ston pa'i bstan pa rab 'dzin cing //
NK129(to)003:11: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun tshogs dang der slob bcas pa la //
NK129(to)003:12: bdag gis thal mo spyi bor cod pan 'dzin pas ni //
NK129(to)003:13: skyabs mchog de dag zhabs sen nyin 'byed ltar dmar ba //
NK129(to)003:14: sgo gsum dad pas rtag tu de la 'dud cing bstod //
NK129(to)003:15: chos dbyings rnam dag dbyings kyi rang bzhin mkha' khyab gzhir //
NK129(to)003:16: kun 'byung rig pa'i sa 'dzin lhun grub phyogs lhung bral //
NK129(to)003:17: 'od gsal snying po'i rta bdun thugs rje'i tsha zer 'phro //
NK129(to)003:18: skal bzang 'gro ba'i pad+mo'i rnam dkar 'bras bu'i tshal //
NK129(to)003:19: dga' ba'i dri bsung sku bzhi'i rnam par rab tu 'byed //
NK129(to)003:20: blo gros mkhyen pa'i rkang drug 'dod pa'i nor bus tshim //
NK129(to)003:21: skyabs gsum 'dod pa'i don grub chu 'dzin khyab che zhing //
NK129(to)003:22: gdul bya'i tshal du brtse chen thugs rje'i char gyis 'gengs //
NK129(to)003:23: shes dang shes bya'i ku mud mun pa'i grwa zlum kyang //
NK129(to)003:24: 'di rtog ri wong 'dzin rgyal kun nas rnam mkhyen pas //
NK129(to)003:25: ma rig mun pa'i ku mud shes gsal rab tu phyed //
NK129(to)003:26: bdag blo'i sems bskyed chu 'dzin khri'i gnas chen de //
NK129(to)003:27: phan bde'i rlung gis brlabs chen g.yo ba'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK129(to)003:28: rjes 'jug rnams la yid bzhin nor bus kun tu rgyal //
NK129(to)003:29: rtogs dang ma rtogs log rtog phyogs 'dzin gyis //
NK129(to)003:30: thams cad mkhyen par ma gyur de bar du //
NK129(to)003:31: ji srid 'jug pa'i 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK129(to)003:32: de srid 'dod pa'i chos ni mi 'dzad cing //
NK129(to)003:33: lung dang rig pas so sor 'then pa na //
NK129(to)003:34: gang ltar 'dod 'dzin de ltar btub na yang //
NK129(to)003:35: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i tshad bzung nam mkha'i mtha' //
NK129(to)003:36: 'phags pas kyang ni de yi rdul cha tsam //
NK129(to)003:37: rtogs shing 'di zhes dpyod par mi nus na //
NK129(to)003:38: rang rgyud so so'i skye bos lta ci smos //
NK129(to)003:39: lo ts+aa la sogs bod kyi mkhas pa ru //
NK129(to)003:40: bzhed pa rnams kyang so so'i skye bo'i blos //
NK129(to)003:41: rang che 'dod cing gzhan phyogs 'geg pa dang //
NK129(to)003:42: khe dang grags pa'i rnyed 'dod phyogs snga yis //
NK129(to)003:43: gsar rnying grags shing dag dang ma dag gis //
NK129(to)003:44: phyogs snga'i 'dod 'dzin du ma byas pa mthong //
NK129(to)003:45: de phyir bdag blo gzu bo gzhir bzhag ste //
NK129(to)003:46: log lta'i rtsod bzlog seng+ge'i nga ro yis //
NK129(to)003:47: phyogs ris rtogs ge'i gcan gzan skrag bya'i phyir //
NK129(to)003:48: bka' rgyud lung dang gang zag dam pa yi //
NK129(to)003:49: gsung rnams phyogs gcig thos pas rgya bskyed nas //
NK129(to)003:50: ma nor rjes 'jug lam 'dir 'jug rnams kyi //
NK129(to)003:51: don du yang dag bdag gis brtsam par bya //
NK129(to)003:52: 'dir dam chos bstan pa spyi'i babs so //
NK129(to)003:54: log lta can gyis rtsod pa bzlog pa seng ge'i
NK129(to)003:55: nga ro zhes bya ba 'di la don lnga ste
NK129(to)003:56: / de la bskal pa bzang po 'di la bdag
NK129(to)003:57: cag gi ston pa rdo rje thub pa'i dbang po
NK129(to)003:58: 'di nyid ji ltar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK129(to)003:59: / pa'i tshul dang / de'i zhal nas ji ltar gsungs pa'i chos dang /
NK129(to)003:60: rjes su 'phags pa rnams kyis ji ltar bsdus pa'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:61: lha dang mi'i yul du ji ltar grags pa dang /
NK129(to)003:62: chos de rnams kyi rnam par bzhag pa bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)003:63: de la dang po ston pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK129(to)003:64: pa'i sangs rgyas pa yang 'dod lugs mi mthun pa
NK129(to)003:65: bdun byung ste / nyan thos sde pa rnam gnyis
NK129(to)003:66: kyis ston pa 'di bskal pa grangs med gsum du
NK129(to)003:67: bdun byung ste / tshogs bsags shing / so so skye bo tha mal du gnas pa zhig /
NK129(to)003:68: khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung na /
NK129(to)003:70: stan thog der sa bcu non par mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:71: rdo rje gdan du sangs rgyas pa yin zer /
NK129(to)003:72: de skad du mngon pa mdzod las /
NK129(to)003:73: 'phags pa min yang pha ma dang //
NK129(to)003:74: nad pa dang ni chos smra dang //
NK129(to)003:75: skye matha'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK129(to)003:76: yon ni gzhal du med pa yin //
NK129(to)003:78: yang rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa chen po pa rnams kyi bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)003:79: ston pa 'di dang por byang chub tu sems bskyed /
NK129(to)003:80: bar du bskal pa grangs med gsum du bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs bsags /
NK129(to)003:81: sa bcu rim gyis bsgrod nas sa bcu rgyun gyi
NK129(to)003:82: tha ma la dam pa tog dkar por skye ba
NK129(to)003:83: bzhes / skabs der lha'i ston pa mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:84: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad kyi /
NK129(to)003:85: sngon gyi thugs bskyed mthar phyin par bskul ba'i sgra la brten nas /
NK129(to)003:87: dbus 'gyur rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs /
NK129(to)003:88: ser skya'i gnas su yum gyi lhums su zhugs te /
NK129(to)003:89: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul gyis sangs rgyas par bzhed de /
NK129(to)003:92: mngon par 'byung ba rnams mthun no //
NK129(to)003:93: de skad du yang rgyud bla ma las /
NK129(to)003:94: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK129(to)003:95: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK129(to)003:96: skye ba mngon par skye ba nas //
NK129(to)003:97: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK129(to)003:98: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK129(to)003:99: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK129(to)003:100: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol pa dang //
NK129(to)003:101: nges 'byung dka' ba spyad pa dang //
NK129(to)003:102: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK129(to)003:103: bdud sde bcom dang rdzogs par ni //
NK129(to)003:104: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK129(to)003:105: mya ngan 'da' bar ston mdzad rnams //
NK129(to)003:106: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK129(to)003:107: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK129(to)003:109: yang gsang sngags yo ga ba rnams kyis 'dod pa ni /
NK129(to)003:110: ston pa byang chub tu thugs bskyed pa la sogs pa rnams ni gong dang mthun la /
NK129(to)003:111: khyad par du rgyal bu don grub kyis lus dka'
NK129(to)003:112: thub kyi lus khog pa'i tshul du mi yul du
NK129(to)003:113: bzhag nas / thugs 'og min du rnam par snang
NK129(to)003:114: mdzad chen por sangs rgyas te phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK129(to)003:115: rnams kyis byang chub rnam pa lnga btab cing /
NK129(to)003:116: de nas ri rab kyi rtse mo la sogs yo
NK129(to)003:117: ga gzhung dum bu bzhi la sogs pa gsungs nas
NK129(to)003:118: / slar mi yul du byon te dka' thub kyi khog par bzhugs /
NK129(to)003:119: n+aa ra dza na'i 'gram du lo drug dka' ba
NK129(to)003:120: spyad nas rdo rje'i gdan du sangs rgyas pa'i tshul
NK129(to)003:122: de skad du'ang yo ga las /
NK129(to)003:123: gtsang ma'i gnas dag rab spongs pa'i //
NK129(to)003:124: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' bar //
NK129(to)003:125: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK129(to)003:126: sprul pa po ni 'dir sangs rgyas //
NK129(to)003:128: de yang sgyu 'phrul lam rim las //
NK129(to)003:130: n+aa ra dza ra'i 'gram sogs su //
NK129(to)003:131: dka' thub dka' ba spyod pa'i tshe //
NK129(to)003:132: phyogs bcu'i sprul pa longs spyod skus //
NK129(to)003:133: byang chub lnga btab dbang bskur nas //
NK129(to)003:134: 'og min nyid du don grub nyid //
NK129(to)003:135: sprul pa'i dka' thub khog pa la //
NK129(to)003:136: ye shes snang mdzad tshul du gshegs //
NK129(to)003:137: ri rab rtse mor 'khor lo bskor //
NK129(to)003:138: de rtogs pa ni gzugs sku yin //
NK129(to)003:140: a nu'i mdo lung dgongs pa 'dus pa nas /
NK129(to)003:141: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK129(to)003:142: pa las 'di sprul pa nyag gcig yin par yang
NK129(to)003:143: gsungs so // yang ma h+aa yo ga ba rnams kyi bzhed la /
NK129(to)003:144: thub pa'i dbang po 'di nyid bskal pa dang po shad du thugs bskyed pa nas /
NK129(to)003:145: grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags pa rnam ni drang don du dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:147: dpal kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi mkha' mtshams nas /
NK129(to)003:148: rigs drug gi gnas su 'dul zhing dang mthun pa'i
NK129(to)003:149: thub pa drug tu sprul nas rigs drug gi don
NK129(to)003:150: mdzad pa yin / khyad par mi yul du sangs
NK129(to)003:151: rgyas sh+aakya thub par sprul nas sems can rnams kyi
NK129(to)003:152: blo thar par 'dren pa'i lam gyi 'tsham dang sbyar
NK129(to)003:153: mdzad pa yin / nas / mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul bstan nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:154: rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK129(to)003:155: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug ces bya ba /
NK129(to)003:156: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las thon to //
NK129(to)003:158: de'i 'grel pa spar khab can las /
NK129(to)003:159: drang don du dga' ldan las babs zer ba yang bden mod kyi /
NK129(to)003:160: byang chub sems dpa' dbang thob pa las 'gal ba med mod /
NK129(to)003:161: nges par kun tu bzang po'i sprul pa'o //
NK129(to)003:163: yang slob dpon zla ba grags pa dang skal ldan grags pa'i bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)003:164: ston pa nyid bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol du sangs rgyas zin nas /
NK129(to)003:165: bskal pa bzang po 'di la yang sh+aakya thub pa
NK129(to)003:166: zhes bya bar gdul bya'i snang ngor sangs rgyas pa'i
NK129(to)003:168: de bzhin du dus gsum kun tu sangs rgyas pa'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:169: mdzad pa sna tshogs ston cing bzhugs par 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:171: bcom ldan 'das ni bskal pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sngon rol du sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)003:172: 'dir sh+aakya'i rigs su skye ba ston par bzhed de /
NK129(to)003:174: mtha' thug rdzogs pa chen po rnams kyi bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:175: gong ma rnams ltar bskal pa dang por thugs bskyed /
NK129(to)003:176: grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags /
NK129(to)003:177: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul du sangs rgyas par bstan pa yang /
NK129(to)003:178: sems can rnams kyi gdul bya'i snang ngo la 'gal ba med kyi /
NK129(to)003:179: nges pa'i don yang dag pa na /
NK129(to)003:180: chos thams cad byed pa po med par ye nas
NK129(to)003:181: sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid du gnas pa yin pa
NK129(to)003:182: la / de ltar ma rtogs pas 'khrul pa'i rtsal sna tshogs su shar ba ni /
NK129(to)003:183: 'dod khams kyi lha gnyid log pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:184: de ltar 'khrul yang don la g.yo ba med pa'i
NK129(to)003:185: yon tan gyis gdul bya sems can rnams kyi dbang
NK129(to)003:186: po'i rim pa dang thun par sku gsum gyi snang
NK129(to)003:187: ba shar nas / bstan pa'i snod dang theg pa'i
NK129(to)003:188: rnam grangs du mar bstun nas sems can gyi don
NK129(to)003:191: rdzogs pa chen po rmad du byung ba'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:192: de yang ye nas sangs rgyas bdag nyid mngon sum du gnas pa la /
NK129(to)003:193: grib ma gzugs kyi dpe bzhin de las rtogs pa byung /
NK129(to)003:195: 'o na gang zag rnams kyi blo dang ldan pa gcig la ston pa sh+aakya thub pa nyid /
NK129(to)003:196: sku ngo bo gcig yin pa la /
NK129(to)003:198: 'dod pa mi mthun pa 'di ji ltar yin snyam
NK129(to)003:199: nas blor mi bde ba dag 'byung ba yang srid
NK129(to)003:200: de / de dag gi tshul 'thad phyogs gang du yin no zhe na /
NK129(to)003:201: gang zag dbang po rab 'bring tha ma'i khyad dang /
NK129(to)003:202: gdul bya'i blo mthun rang rang gi go skabs dang 'tsham par bstan pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:203: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba bsam gyis
NK129(to)003:204: mi khyab pa mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK129(to)003:205: la / thugs rje dang mdzad pa'i rnam 'phrul bsam
NK129(to)003:206: gyis mi khyab pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo gdul bya
NK129(to)003:208: sems can rnams kyi rang rang gi las dang skal bar 'tsham pa /
NK129(to)003:209: dbang po'i go rim bzhin du gang la gang 'dul du bstan pas /
NK129(to)003:210: de rnams gang la yang theg pa'i rim pa ni bden pas 'gal ba med de /
NK129(to)003:211: nam mkha'i cho 'phrul ltar shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:212: de la gang zag blo chung phyogs 'dzin dang rang
NK129(to)003:213: 'thad kyi phyogs rtag brtan ther zug tu bgrang zhing
NK129(to)003:214: don gyi dgongs pa ma lon pa rnams kyis ni
NK129(to)003:215: rgya mtsho'i ru sbal dang khron pa'i ru sbal ltar
NK129(to)003:216: shes par bya'o // don gnyis pa ston pas ji
NK129(to)003:217: ltar gsung pa dam pa'i chos la yang gnyis te
NK129(to)003:218: shes par bya'o // / rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:219: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa ji ltar gsung pa'i tshul lo //
NK129(to)003:220: dang po rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:221: mdzad pa bcu gnyis las ji ltar byung ba rnams ni 'dir yi ge 'jigs pas /
NK129(to)003:224: 'dul ba lung las ci ltar 'byung ba ltar go sla bas shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:225: bye brag tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar mdzad pa ni /
NK129(to)003:226: thub pa'i dbang po de nyid dgung lo nyer dgu la pho brang nas phyung ste rab tu byung /
NK129(to)003:227: dgung lo so lnga dpyid zla 'bring po'i tshes brgyad la mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)003:228: dbyar zla ra ba'i tshes brgyad kyi nub mo tshun
NK129(to)003:229: chod la zhag bdun phrag bdun chos ma gsungs te
NK129(to)003:230: / mi gsungs pa'i rgyu mtshan gang yin na /
NK129(to)003:231: bdun phrag dang po la chos kyi sku gnyis su
NK129(to)003:232: med pa brnyes pas de'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK129(to)003:233: go // gnyis pa la byang chub kyis shing drung du bzhugs te /
NK129(to)003:234: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i dus nas rdo rje'i
NK129(to)003:235: gdan la sangs rgyas pa'i bar la thugs mnyam par
NK129(to)003:236: bzhag go // gsum pa seng+ge'i khri r+ts+wa yi gdan las bzhengs te /
NK129(to)003:237: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi mthar zhabs kyis bcags te /
NK129(to)003:238: rang gi gdul bya dang zhing khams grub par mdzad /
NK129(to)003:239: bzhi pa la phyogs bzhi'i mthar rgya mtsho'i bar du 'chag par mdzad do //
NK129(to)003:240: lnga pa la klu'i rgyal po btang bzung gi gnas su byon par mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:241: klu yul du 'tshubs ma chen po langs pa las /
NK129(to)003:242: klu rnams sbrul gyi gzugs kyis sangs rgyas kyi sku dkris te /
NK129(to)003:243: sku la 'tshubs ma dang rdul skyob par byas pa la /
NK129(to)003:244: gdug pa can de dag gis kyang sngar ma myong
NK129(to)003:245: ba'i bde ba khyad par can lus kyis myong bar
NK129(to)003:246: byas so // drug pa la shing nya gro ta dang /
NK129(to)003:247: rab 'byams la sogs pa'i mdun du chos thams cad
NK129(to)003:248: mnyam pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs so
NK129(to)003:249: // bdun phrag bdun pa la shing sgrol rgyu zhes bya ba'i drung tshal du /
NK129(to)003:250: chos thams cad dus gsum du rnam par grol ba
NK129(to)003:251: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs
NK129(to)003:252: so // de'i dus su tshong dpon ga gon bzang po dang /
NK129(to)003:253: nor bu bzang po zhes bya ba rnams rta cang shes pa dang /
NK129(to)003:254: glang po rig shes ded nas /
NK129(to)003:255: phyi'i rgya mtsho nas nor bu rin po che blangs nas log pa dang /
NK129(to)003:256: rta dang glang po che rnams shing sgrol rgyu'i tshal la skor ba byed cing 'dug nas /
NK129(to)003:258: ston pa sangs rgyas nas ring por ma lon pa dang mjal lo //
NK129(to)003:259: der chos zhus pas ma gnang ste 'di skad du gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:260: ngas ni gang tshe bzod pa thob pa'i tshe //
NK129(to)003:261: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad kyis bdag lung bstan //
NK129(to)003:262: 'jig rten mtha' yas kun la snying rje yang //
NK129(to)003:263: gzhan gyi gsol ba btab kyang ngas mi 'chad //
NK129(to)003:265: yang nan du zhus te tha ma yang bdag cag
NK129(to)003:266: rnams yul du ma sleb bar du bar chad med
NK129(to)003:267: cing bkra shis pa'i chos shig zhu zhes zhus pas
NK129(to)003:268: zhal nas gsungs pa la snga ba shis pa brjod
NK129(to)003:270: tshong dpon de yang ma 'ongs pa na sbrang rtsi
NK129(to)003:271: 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i sangs rgyas su lung bstan
NK129(to)003:272: to // de nas bdag gis rtogs pa'i chos 'di lta bu gzhan la bstan kyang /
NK129(to)003:273: go zhing phan par mi 'gyur bas /
NK129(to)003:274: reng byed kyi bu lhag spyod dang /
NK129(to)003:275: sgyu rtsal shes kyi bu reng 'phur gnyis la bstan dgongs nas /
NK129(to)003:276: de gnyis btsal bas gcig gums nas zhag bdun song /
NK129(to)003:277: gcig gums nas zhag gsum song nas thugs mug pa lta bu yang mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:278: de ni ma legs te 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:279: de gnyis ni bdag gi bstan pa'i don go bas
NK129(to)003:280: gdul bya'i snod du gyur te gums pa de ni
NK129(to)003:281: de gnyis kyis sde dpon ma re ste de ni
NK129(to)003:282: shin tu ste bor ma stes so //
NK129(to)003:284: yang mdo mngon par 'byung ba nas /
NK129(to)003:285: de gnyis ma gums par thub pa dang bgro gleng mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:286: don ston pa'i ston pa lta bur gyur pa yang bshad do //
NK129(to)003:288: bdag la drin che ba sh+aakya rnams yin te /
NK129(to)003:289: de rnams la bstan snyams nas byon pas sh+aakya rnams 'dul dus la cung ma babs pas /
NK129(to)003:291: don 'grub 'di ni sangs rgyas pa mi bden te /
NK129(to)003:292: n+aa ra dza rar dka' thub kyi ma shi ba ya mtshan /
NK129(to)003:293: da skyeng nas pho brang du 'ong 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:294: ba yi 'o ma 'thungs pas rigs bsled mi rung na /
NK129(to)003:296: bsnyen cing bkur bar mi bya'o //
NK129(to)003:298: der ston pa'i dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)003:299: sh+aakya rnams la snying brtse ba dang /
NK129(to)003:300: thugs mug pa'i tshul gyis slar log nas byang chub shing drung gi rtsar lus gnad bcas te /
NK129(to)003:301: ye shes rol pa chen po seng+ge rnam par bsgyings
NK129(to)003:302: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs so
NK129(to)003:304: bdag gis rtogs pa'i don 'di shin tu zab cing phra la 'dzangs pas /
NK129(to)003:305: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas bdag rang gcig pu nags su gnas pa la /
NK129(to)003:306: lan gcig 'das pa'i dus su ring bsrel gyis sems
NK129(to)003:307: can rnams la phan gdag shing bsod nams bsags pa'i
NK129(to)003:308: rten du bya'o dgongs nas tshigs su bcad pa 'di
NK129(to)003:309: gsungs so // zab cing spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK129(to)003:310: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos zhig bdag gi rnyed //
NK129(to)003:311: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK129(to)003:312: mi smra gcig pur nags su bsgom par bya //
NK129(to)003:314: sgra de tshangs pa'i 'jig rten du grags so //
NK129(to)003:315: gsung de skad grags pas tshangs pa 'dun pa skyes te /
NK129(to)003:316: bdag ni bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong rtsa
NK129(to)003:317: gnyis kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar sems bskyed
NK129(to)003:318: pa yin gyi / e ma ho ston pa 'jig
NK129(to)003:319: rten du byon pa ni ngo mtshar che snyam nas
NK129(to)003:320: pa yin gyi / / bcom ldan 'das kyi drung
NK129(to)003:321: du song ste 'di skad ces gsol ba btab bo
NK129(to)003:322: pa yin gyi / / // kye ma ho /
NK129(to)003:323: ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor rab bsgrub nas /
NK129(to)003:324: phyogs bcu dag tu 'od zer rab bkyes pas //
NK129(to)003:325: ye shes zer gyis blo yi kha 'byed do //
NK129(to)003:326: smra ba'i seng+ge de ring btang snyoms bzhugs //
NK129(to)003:327: ces gsol bas ma gnang ste cang mi gsungs /
NK129(to)003:329: ma ga ta yi yul 'dir sngon chad chos //
NK129(to)003:330: ma dag dri ma'i rdzas su 'brel pa byung //
NK129(to)003:331: bdud rtsi'i sgo mo khyod kyis dbye bar mdzod //
NK129(to)003:332: gdul bya rnams la dri med bshad du gsol //
NK129(to)003:334: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NK129(to)003:335: tshangs pa nga yi tha ma kun //
NK129(to)003:336: bcom nas tshegs med gang rtogs bu'i //
NK129(to)003:338: bsgribs pas bde blag rtogs pa min //
NK129(to)003:339: gyen phyogs las ni bzlog pa'i las //
NK129(to)003:340: zab la shin tu brtags dka' ste //
NK129(to)003:341: 'dod chags kyis bsgribs mun pa yi //
NK129(to)003:342: phung po bsgribs pas mi mthong ngo //
NK129(to)003:343: ces gsung ste ma gnang ngo //
NK129(to)003:344: de nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin kyang lhags nas zhabs la gtugs te zhus pa /
NK129(to)003:345: zla ba nya ba gza' las thar ba ltar //
NK129(to)003:346: khyod kyi thugs ni rnam par grol ba las //
NK129(to)003:347: g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba bzhes su gsol //
NK129(to)003:348: 'jig rten mun par shes rab 'od 'byung mdzod //
NK129(to)003:349: kun tu 'tshal bar gyur pa mchis lags kyang //
NK129(to)003:350: thugs rje chen pos chos ni bshad du gsol //
NK129(to)003:351: zhes zhus pas kyang ma gnang ste /
NK129(to)003:352: slar tshangs pa la bka' stsal pa /
NK129(to)003:353: skye bo rnams ni tshangs la dad pa ste //
NK129(to)003:354: de yi gsol ba btab na chos 'khor bskor //
NK129(to)003:355: rnam pa mang po 'tshal 'gyur sems dpa'i chos //
NK129(to)003:356: gya nom rdul bral chos bshad gsol ba thob //
NK129(to)003:359: bcom ldan 'das 'jig rten na dbang po rtul po yang mang mchis /
NK129(to)003:361: rab tu gyur pa yang mchis na /
NK129(to)003:362: de dag gi don du bka'i 'khor lo yang lan gsum du bskor du gsol /
NK129(to)003:364: de'i tshe shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams nas /
NK129(to)003:365: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:366: byang chub sems dpa' chos kyi 'khor lo zhes bya ba byung ste /
NK129(to)003:367: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa zhig
NK129(to)003:368: tshangs pa la gtad de phul nas gnyis kas zhus
NK129(to)003:369: / de'i tshe ci yang mi gsung bar snang ngo //
NK129(to)003:370: de ltar zhu ba gnyis byung ba'i tshul gyi ming gi bye brag /
NK129(to)003:371: yang na ni gnyis po de tshangs pa ni sangs rgyas stong gi zhu ba po yin la /
NK129(to)003:372: gcig ni phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi
NK129(to)003:373: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba yin te
NK129(to)003:374: / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar zhal gyis bzhes so //
NK129(to)003:375: de'i tshe thog mar bdag gis gang 'dul bar bya snyam nas dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK129(to)003:376: thog mar lnga sde bzang po 'dul bar mkhyen nas /
NK129(to)003:377: w+aa r+aa na si'i phur lnga sde bzang po'i phyogs su lho phyogs nas byang phyogs su gshegs so //
NK129(to)003:378: de'i shul kar kun tu rgyu phyi rol pa 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas pa /
NK129(to)003:379: lho phyogs na g.yas su 'gro ba dang 'phrad pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:380: de rnams kyi bsam pa la koo ta ma ni
NK129(to)003:381: slob dpon med par sangs rgyas thob po zhes pa
NK129(to)003:382: ni mi rigs so snyam nas smras pa /
NK129(to)003:383: khyod kyi slob dpon su yin zhes smras pa dang /
NK129(to)003:385: nga la slob dpon su yang med //
NK129(to)003:386: nga ni gcig pu rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK129(to)003:387: nga dang 'dra ba gzhan med de //
NK129(to)003:388: bsil rgyur zag pa zad pa yin //
NK129(to)003:390: zag pa zad pa yin ces pas /
NK129(to)003:391: dgra bcom pa yin zer ba go nas yang smras pa /
NK129(to)003:392: 'o na khyod dgra bcom pa yin nam zhes zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:394: nga ni 'jig rten dgra bcom pa //
NK129(to)003:395: nga ni ston pa bla na med //
NK129(to)003:396: lha dang mi dang lha min yang //
NK129(to)003:397: nga dang 'dra ba yod ma yin //
NK129(to)003:399: 'o na khyod sangs rgyas yin par zhal gyis bzhes sam zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:401: gang zag zag pa zad rnyed pa //
NK129(to)003:402: nga 'dra rgyal bar shes par bya //
NK129(to)003:403: sdig pa'i chos las nga rgyal ba //
NK129(to)003:404: nyer 'gro de gzhan nga rgyal ba'o //
NK129(to)003:406: sangs rgyas yin par yid ches so //
NK129(to)003:408: 'o na khyod gang du 'gro zhes zhus pas /
NK129(to)003:410: nga ni w+aa r+aa na s+air 'gro //
NK129(to)003:411: grong khyer bsil ldan der song nas //
NK129(to)003:412: mun pa lta bu'i sems can la //
NK129(to)003:414: ces pa la sogs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa 'ga' gsungs pas /
NK129(to)003:416: w+aa r+aa na s+air ni shing grib kyang chung /
NK129(to)003:417: sems can la phan pa yang chung /
NK129(to)003:418: grong khyer gzhan zhig tu gshegs la chos gsung bar zhu zer ba la /
NK129(to)003:420: yul w+aa r+aa na s+ai ni dus gsum gyi sangs
NK129(to)003:421: rgyas thams cad kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK129(to)003:422: gnas yin pas / thog mar de ma yin par
NK129(to)003:423: bskor du mi rung ngo zhes gsung nas bzhud do
NK129(to)003:424: gnas yin pas / // de'i tshe w+aa r+aa na
NK129(to)003:425: s+ai'i phu na mu stegs lnga sde bzang po yod
NK129(to)003:426: pa sangs rgyas 'byon par thos nas /
NK129(to)003:427: ldang bar mi bya ba dang /
NK129(to)003:429: bsnyen cing bskur bar mi bya zhing /
NK129(to)003:430: 'gran gzugs te the tshom dri bar dam bcas te 'di skad ces /
NK129(to)003:431: dge sbyong koo ta ma de la 'phags pa'i shes rab kyang med de /
NK129(to)003:432: mi chos kyi bla ma mkhan zhig yin no //
NK129(to)003:433: zhes gong du dam bcas pa dang /
NK129(to)003:435: de'i thugs rje dang gzi brjid ma bzod de /
NK129(to)003:436: gcig gis dris pa tshe dang ldan pa khyod mi chos kyi bla ma mkhan zhig yin snyams na /
NK129(to)003:437: 'od dang gzi brjid de tsam che na khyod 'phags pa'i rigs gcig cang yin nam /
NK129(to)003:440: nga la tshe dang ldan pa ma zer cig /
NK129(to)003:441: nga ni khams gsum las 'das pa'o //
NK129(to)003:442: sdug bsngal sel ba'i ljon shing /
NK129(to)003:445: de rnams rang dbang med par 'dus te /
NK129(to)003:447: de nas chos gsung bar bzhed nas /
NK129(to)003:448: gang dag 'khor bsdu ba'i gan+di brdungs pa'i sgra las /
NK129(to)003:449: bde gshegs slob mar gyur pa'i sems can gang su
NK129(to)003:450: dag /'jig rten khams 'dir gnas pa kun nyon cig
NK129(to)003:451: / deng 'dir ston pas chos kyi char 'bebs kyi /
NK129(to)003:452: gang dag nyan par 'dod rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK129(to)003:453: zab mo rgyal ba'i bka' la kun nyon cig /
NK129(to)003:454: ces pa'i tshig kyang byung bas /
NK129(to)003:455: de nas chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum bskor ba las /
NK129(to)003:456: don rnam pa lnga lngas ston te /
NK129(to)003:462: de yang 'khor lo dang po 'di yi skabs kyi yul ni w+aa r+aa na s+ai /
NK129(to)003:463: yon bdag ni rgyal po gzugs can snying pos mdzad /
NK129(to)003:464: dus dpyid zla 'bring po'i tshes brgyad la sangs rgyas nas gsungs te /
NK129(to)003:465: 'khor lnga sde bzang po la sogs pa la bka'
NK129(to)003:466: 'khor lo dang po'i tshad ni lo bdun la zla
NK129(to)003:467: ba gnyis kyi ma long par gsungs /
NK129(to)003:468: spyir bka' la gsung lugs kyang gnyis su 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:471: tshad med par gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:472: mdo lang kar gshegs pa las //
NK129(to)003:473: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK129(to)003:474: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK129(to)003:476: 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du chos gsung bar 'dod de tshad med do //
NK129(to)003:477: tshad can du gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:479: mos pa'i bye brag gi don la dgongs nas gsungs pa la gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:480: gnyan po la dgongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong /
NK129(to)003:481: dbye ba'i don la dgongs pa la gsung rabs yan lag bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:482: bsdu ba'i don la dgongs pa la sde snod rnam pa gsum /
NK129(to)003:483: de la dbang po dang mos pa'i bye brag la
NK129(to)003:484: dgongs pa ni 'khor lnga sde bzang po la sogs
NK129(to)003:485: pa dbang po tha ma'i don du bden pa bzhi
NK129(to)003:486: / 'bring po la mtshan nyid nges pa'i don gnyis /
NK129(to)003:487: rab la gsang sngags kyi theg pa gsungs pa /
NK129(to)003:489: sngar gsungs pa'i shis pa brjod pa'i mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:490: grangs khar gsungs pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis /
NK129(to)003:493: de gnyis ni bka' yin kyang 'khor lo gsum du mi 'du ste /
NK129(to)003:494: tshangs pas ma zhus pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)003:496: de gnyis bsnan pas 'khor lo lnga yin te /
NK129(to)003:499: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis ni //
NK129(to)003:500: chos kyi 'khor lo lnga bskor te //
NK129(to)003:502: 'o na dang po'i 'khor lo cig dbang po tha ma la ji ltar gsung na /
NK129(to)003:508: de dag la mthong ba'i lam skyes te ye shes skad cig ma bcu drug skyes so //
NK129(to)003:509: de la lam gong ma skyes te /
NK129(to)003:510: sdug bsngal ni shes par bya /
NK129(to)003:516: de nas yang gong ma ma skyes pa la /
NK129(to)003:517: sdug bsngal ba shes par bya ste shes zin shes su med /
NK129(to)003:518: kun 'byung ni spang bar bya ste spang zin spang du med /
NK129(to)003:519: 'gog pa ni mngon du bya ste byas zin bya ru med /
NK129(to)003:520: lam bsgom par bya ste sgom zin bsgom du med /
NK129(to)003:521: ces bstan pas lnga sde bzang po thul te bden pa thob par gyur to //
NK129(to)003:522: de'i 'og tu 'od srungs ral pa can gyis sde stong btul lo //
NK129(to)003:523: de'i rjes la nye rgyal dang pang na skyes btul lo //
NK129(to)003:524: de'i rjes su rgyal po zas gtsang ma la sogs
NK129(to)003:525: sh+aakya'i rigs rnams btul te sh+aakya'i gzhon nu lnga brgya
NK129(to)003:527: de rnams ni theg pa chung ngu'i mdo sde ru rtogs par bzhed do //
NK129(to)003:528: yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon kha cig gi bzhed pas ni /
NK129(to)003:529: mngon pa yang dang po'i bkar 'du bar bzhed /
NK129(to)003:531: mngon pa sde bdun dgra bcom pas phyis gsungs pas bkar cang 'agro'am snyam na /
NK129(to)003:532: de ni cig tu ma nges te /
NK129(to)003:533: sangs rgyas nyid kyis dang po'i dus su dum bu
NK129(to)003:534: dang sil pur gsungs pa rnams phyis nas dgra bcom
NK129(to)003:536: ched du brjod pa'i tshig rnams so //
NK129(to)003:538: de ltar gsungs pa'i chos rnams kyang /
NK129(to)003:539: nyan thos sde pa rnams gnyis dang bstun nas /
NK129(to)003:540: gang zag gi bdag med la /
NK129(to)003:541: chos kyi bdag bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)003:542: don dam par yod par zhal gyis bzhes nas bden
NK129(to)003:543: pa bzhi la lan bcu gnyis su gsungs pa yin
NK129(to)003:544: no // don gnyis pa bka' 'khor lo bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK129(to)003:545: yul rgyal po'i khab bya rgod phung po'i ri la sogs par /
NK129(to)003:546: rgyal po mchod sbyin gyis sbyin bdag byas nas 'khor 'dus pa gsum la gsungs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:547: dus lo bzhi bcu zhe gnyis nas /
NK129(to)003:548: lnga bcu rtsa bzhi'i bar du lo bcu gnyis su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:549: mdo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa mngon par rtogs pa'i mdo rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum /
NK129(to)003:550: snying po'i mdo shes rab snying po la sogs pa gzhung chung bcu gsum gsungs /
NK129(to)003:551: de yang spyir chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsung tshung yang /
NK129(to)003:552: 'dod chags las gyur pa'i nyon mongs pa nyi khri
NK129(to)003:553: chig stong gi gnyan por 'dul ba'i sde snod mi
NK129(to)003:554: bsdug pa bsgom pa la sogs nyi khri chig stong
NK129(to)003:555: / nyon mongs pa zhe sdang las gyur pa nyi
NK129(to)003:556: khri chig stong gi gnyan por mdo sde'i sde snod
NK129(to)003:557: byams pa bsgom pa la sogs pa nyi khri chig
NK129(to)003:558: / stong / nyon mongs pa gti mug las gyur
NK129(to)003:559: pa nyi khri gcig stong gi gnyan por mngon pa'i
NK129(to)003:560: sde snod byams pa bsgom pa la sogs pa nyi
NK129(to)003:561: / stong / khri chig stong / nyon mongs pa
NK129(to)003:562: dug gsum cha mnyam pa las gyur pa na mi
NK129(to)003:563: mthun pa nyi khri chig stong gi gnyan por sde
NK129(to)003:564: snod gsum spyir rigs cig pa la /
NK129(to)003:565: gnyan po dang khams kyis rab tu phye ba'i nyi khri chig stong gsungs te /
NK129(to)003:566: de ltar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK129(to)003:567: de ltar yang lha'i dbang pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK129(to)003:568: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong gi grangs rnyed kyi /
NK129(to)003:569: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK129(to)003:570: phung po zhes pa'i tshad ni /
NK129(to)003:571: brjod bya phung po'i khams la sogs pa mi 'dra ba re re bzhag pa'am /
NK129(to)003:572: phung po re re la'ang sho lo ka stong stong du bzhag pa'am /
NK129(to)003:573: yang na glang po che sa srung gi rgyab khal re la phung po re ru bzhag /
NK129(to)003:575: dbye ba'i don du mdo sde yan lag bcu gnyis su bzhag pa ni /
NK129(to)003:577: dbyangs kyi bsnyad pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:581: ltung ba dang bcas pa'i sde /
NK129(to)003:587: gtan la phab pa'i sde dang bcu gnyis su gsungs pa las /
NK129(to)003:588: de dag gi dgongs don rnam grangs don du bsdu na'ang 'di ltar shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:589: thog mar 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus cig ces pa nas /
NK129(to)003:590: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK129(to)003:591: ces pa'i bar te de yang mdo'i sde zhes pa la yang /
NK129(to)003:592: dgongs pa'i don 'dus pa'i phyir mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:593: don sder langs pa las tshig mdor bsdus pa'am /
NK129(to)003:594: tshig sder langs pa las don mdor bsdus pa ste /
NK129(to)003:595: dper na sa lu ljongs pa'i mdo lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:596: yang na tshig ma rdzogs kyang don rdzogs pa sangs
NK129(to)003:597: rgyas kyis sh+aa ri'i bu la gsungs pa lta bu
NK129(to)003:598: ste / rten cing 'brel pa mthong na chos mthong ngo //
NK129(to)003:599: mdo'i dgongs pa las nges par 'grel pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK129(to)003:600: sus chos mthong ba de la sangs rgyas mthong ngo //
NK129(to)003:601: zhes pa des kyang sder langs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:602: gnyis pa dbyangs kyi bsnyad pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:603: mdo de nyid dbu dang bar dang tha mar tshigs su bcad na dbyangs kyi bsnyad pa'i sde ste /
NK129(to)003:604: dper na bu mo blo gros bzang mos zhus pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:605: gsum pa lung du bstan pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:606: nges pa'i don gyi mdo la sogs pa ma 'ongs
NK129(to)003:607: par sangs rgyas rnams 'byung bar lung gis bstan pa
NK129(to)003:609: dus 'di zhes bya bar khyod sangs rgyas 'di zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:610: dper na dge slong lnga brgya po lung bstan pa lta bu'am /
NK129(to)003:611: sring mo gang g+aa'i lha mo lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:612: bzhi pa tshigs su bcad pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:615: bzang po spyod pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK129(to)003:616: lnga pa ched du brjod pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:617: gang la ston pa yi rangs pa'i tshul mdzad pa lta bu rnams te /
NK129(to)003:623: dge slong dag khyed rnams pha rol tu gzhan gyi phyir rnyed pa mi tshol ba legs so //
NK129(to)003:624: 'dod pa chung ba ni legs so //
NK129(to)003:625: chog shes pa ni legs so //
NK129(to)003:627: drug pa ltung ba dang bcas pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:628: ltung ba dang bcas pa'i bslab pa gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:629: nyes pa'i rgyu bstan pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:631: skyes bu gcig gis cig bzung nas chu dang 'bras snyed de slar phyir btang ngo //
NK129(to)003:632: de la sangs rgyas kyis nyes ltung bstan pa //
NK129(to)003:633: sdig pa phra zhing chung ba yang //
NK129(to)003:634: mi gnod snyam nas brnyas mi bya //
NK129(to)003:635: chu yi thigs pa chung bas kyang //
NK129(to)003:636: snod chen po yang gang bar 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:637: ces gsungs pa la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:638: bdun pa rtogs pa brjod pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:639: dpe dang bcas nas gsungs pa'am /
NK129(to)003:640: bde gshegs rigs lnga rtogs brjod phul ba lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:641: brgyad pa de lta bu'i sde rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:642: gang sngon gyi sbyor ba dang ldan pas te /
NK129(to)003:643: dge slong dag 'jig rten du 'byung gnas bshad pa ni khams kyi mdo sde'o zhes bya ba dang /
NK129(to)003:644: yang sangs rgyas bsod nams skyabs kyis gsungs pa ni bdud rtsi lnga zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)003:645: rnam par gzigs kyis gsungs pa ni chos kyi me long zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)003:646: 'od srungs kyis gsungs pa ni snying po rnams rnam par 'byed par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:648: dgu pa skyes pa rabs kyi sde ni /
NK129(to)003:649: sngon thub pa byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la zhugs pa'i tshul te /
NK129(to)003:650: drin lan bsabs pa'i mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:651: dang po'i skyes rabs la sogs pa lta bu rnams so //
NK129(to)003:652: bcu pa shin tu rgyas pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:653: theg pa chen po'i don rgya che ba /
NK129(to)003:654: dpe dang don du mthun pa /
NK129(to)003:655: nam mkha'i khams lta bu'i mdo shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:656: sangs rgyas phal po che lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:657: bcu gcig pa rmad du byung ba'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:658: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK129(to)003:660: sangs rgyas rnams kyi rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba dang /
NK129(to)003:661: rmad du byung ba'i chos gsungs pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:662: rgyal ba btsas ma thag tu /
NK129(to)003:663: phyogs bzhir gom pa bdun bor nas /
NK129(to)003:664: skye rgas na 'chi thams cad kyi tha ma'o //
NK129(to)003:666: byang chub sems dpa' la sprel 'us shing thog sbrang rtsi phul ba la lung bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:667: phyis chos nyan pa la zhe sdang rang dag la song ba dang /
NK129(to)003:668: bdud kyi bar du gcod pa la sogs rnams rnam grangs kyi sder longs pa rnams so //
NK129(to)003:669: bcu gnyis pa gtan la phab pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:670: spyir sde snod gsum du ma 'dus pa med pa dang /
NK129(to)003:671: de yang mdo yi sde nas rmad du byung ba'i bar gyi bdun ni mdo'i sde /
NK129(to)003:672: gling bzhi la sogs pa bzhi ni 'dul ba /
NK129(to)003:673: gtan la phab pa ni mngon pa'i sde snod do //
NK129(to)003:674: de ltar bcu gnyis po de dag kyang sde snod gsum du cis 'du zhes na /
NK129(to)003:675: rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa tsam gyi don du mdo sde /
NK129(to)003:676: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa'i gnyan por 'dul ba /
NK129(to)003:677: rang gis lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i gnyan
NK129(to)003:678: por mngon pa'i sde snod gsungs par bstan pa yin
NK129(to)003:679: no // de dag kyang mdor bsdu na bslab pa gsum du 'dus pa ste /
NK129(to)003:680: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa bstan pa'i phyir mdo sde /
NK129(to)003:681: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa bstan pa'i phyir 'dul ba /
NK129(to)003:682: lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa bstan pa'i phyir mngon pa'i sde snod bstan pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:684: don rnams nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo las /
NK129(to)003:685: yul yangs pa can dang rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi
NK129(to)003:686: tshal la sogs su khyin bdag mgon med zas sbyin
NK129(to)003:688: 'khor theg pa sna tshogs pa la mos pa byang
NK129(to)003:689: chub sems dpa' nas so so skye bo'i bar rnams
NK129(to)003:690: la gang la gang 'dul du gsungs pa yang /
NK129(to)003:691: khyad par du theg pa chen po'i rigs can rnams kyi go ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:692: theg pa chen po'i chos dang /
NK129(to)003:693: mdo'i dgongs pa la nges par 'grel pa la sogs pa rnams gsungs te /
NK129(to)003:694: dgung lo lnga bcu nga bzhi nas brgyad cu gya gnyis kyi bar te /
NK129(to)003:695: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad du gsungs /
NK129(to)003:696: de yang gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i chos 'di
NK129(to)003:697: bka' 'khor lo gsum pa'i khongs su 'du bar bshad
NK129(to)003:699: gsang sngags gsungs pa'i ston pa nyid kyang /
NK129(to)003:700: gnas dang dus dang 'khor la sogs pa ma nges pa /
NK129(to)003:701: theg pa gsum du mi 'du ste /
NK129(to)003:702: bla med don gyi theg pa zhes bya ba rang
NK129(to)003:703: so yin no zhes zer na yang theg pa bka'
NK129(to)003:704: tha ma'i theg par 'du ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:705: gsang sngags kyi babs so chen mo nas /
NK129(to)003:706: ston pas o rgyan za hor gyi yul du /
NK129(to)003:707: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i cha lugs kyis rgyal po dza
NK129(to)003:708: in+d+ra b+hu d+hi btsun mo lnga brgya dang bcas pa
NK129(to)003:709: bde chen mkha' spyod la dbang bar byas pa dang
NK129(to)003:710: / yangs pa can gyi gnas su 'khor 'dus pa
NK129(to)003:711: bzhi dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs rnams la pha
NK129(to)003:712: rol tu phyin pa dang don dam pa'i nges pa'i
NK129(to)003:714: rgya mtsho'i 'gram dang nye ba lang ka'i gnas su
NK129(to)003:715: sde brgyad la sogs pa dag dang ma dag gi
NK129(to)003:716: 'khor rnams la rgyu lam 'bras bu gsum du phyes
NK129(to)003:717: nas / rten cing 'brel pa'i chos rnams rgya cher gsungs pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:718: gnas dang 'khor rnams su ston pas dus cig la sprul pa mdzad nas gsungs pa rnams la yang /
NK129(to)003:719: de dag gi rang rang gi gnas na ston pas
NK129(to)003:720: ni bdag cag la chos 'di lta bu gsungs te
NK129(to)003:721: / ston pa ni gzhan du ma byon pas /
NK129(to)003:722: nged rnams kyi gnas su gsang sngags bla med chos
NK129(to)003:723: kyi 'khor lo bskor nged kyi gnas su chos 'di
NK129(to)003:724: gsungs zer ba rnams rdzun no //
NK129(to)003:725: ces smras pa lta bu ste /
NK129(to)003:726: bka' theg pa tha ma'i khongs su shin tu 'du ba nges pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:728: in+d+ra b+h+au d+hi ston pa'i dus min /
NK129(to)003:729: phyis 'byung bar lung bstan phyag na rdo rjes 'dul ba'o zhes 'byung ba yod de /
NK129(to)003:730: in+d+ra b+h+au d+hi gsum du byung ba'i dza chen po
NK129(to)003:731: de ni ston pa'i sbyin bdag dang dngos slob yin
NK129(to)003:732: no // tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes pas phyag na rdo
NK129(to)003:733: rjes ri ma la ya gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtse
NK129(to)003:734: mor po ti glegs bam gyi char pa babs pa
NK129(to)003:735: no // yang bden no // gsang sngags ni bka'
NK129(to)003:736: gsum kar 'du bar slob dpon 'phags pa yab sras
NK129(to)003:737: no // yang bden no // kyang bzhed de /
NK129(to)003:738: +aar+ya d+he wa'i spyod pa bsdus pa'i sgron mar yang
NK129(to)003:739: no // yang bden no // kyang bzhed de /
NK129(to)003:740: gsal lo // brjod bya ni theg pa chen po
NK129(to)003:742: smra bsam brjod du med pa /
NK129(to)003:743: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba dang /
NK129(to)003:745: bla med gsang sngags kyi theg par 'jug par dbang bzhi yang gzhi lam 'bras bu /
NK129(to)003:746: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug mtha' thug sku bzhi'i ngang du bstan pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:747: de ltar bka' 'khor lo rim pa gsum po de dag kyang /
NK129(to)003:748: gang zag dbang po'i go rims kyi gsungs pa /
NK129(to)003:749: the tshom gyis gnas kyang byung ste /
NK129(to)003:751: sems can thams cad dngos po la zhen pa rags pa'i don du /
NK129(to)003:752: gzung 'dzin don dam par yod par zhal gyis bzhes
NK129(to)003:753: pa de la theg pa chen po rnams yid ma
NK129(to)003:754: ches te rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur to //
NK129(to)003:756: chos thams cad rang bzhin med par gsungs pas nyan
NK129(to)003:757: thos pa rnams the tshom za zhing de la yang
NK129(to)003:758: rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur to //
NK129(to)003:759: bka' 'khor lo gsum pa la yod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:760: med par 'dod pa thams cad kyi mtshan nyid gtan la phab ste /
NK129(to)003:763: ngo bo dbyer med mnyam pa nyid du bstan pa'am /
NK129(to)003:764: chos thams cad sems kyi 'char lugs sam sems las ma 'das par gsungs pas kun yid ches te /
NK129(to)003:765: rtsod pa dang bral ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:766: de yang mdo dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK129(to)003:767: bcom ldan 'das kyis dang por yul w+aa r+aa na
NK129(to)003:768: s+air nyan thos kyi theg pa la yang dag par
NK129(to)003:770: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhis rnam par bstan pas sus kyang ma bskor ba'i 'khor lo bskor bas /
NK129(to)003:771: 'khor lo de bla na ma mchis pas drang ba'i don rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur pa lags /
NK129(to)003:772: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pa nas brtsams te /
NK129(to)003:773: thog mar yod par yang gsungs la /
NK129(to)003:774: rjes su gnyis ka'i mtha' dang bral ba /
NK129(to)003:775: theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la legs par phyes nas gsungs pas /
NK129(to)003:776: shin tu ngo mtshar ba dang ldan pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo gsum pa bskor te /
NK129(to)003:777: chos kyi 'khor lo ni bla na ma mchis pa nges pa'i don /
NK129(to)003:778: rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur pa yang ma lags so //
NK129(to)003:780: de ltar bka'i 'khor lo rim pa gsum bskor ba de la yang /
NK129(to)003:782: bka'i 'khor lo rim pa gsum po de rnams sangs
NK129(to)003:783: rgyas kyis gsung cig gdul bya dbang po'i rim par
NK129(to)003:785: so sor thos pa yin zer la /
NK129(to)003:787: ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid cig pu las
NK129(to)003:788: ma gsung na la las gzugs stong zhes bya bar
NK129(to)003:789: mthong / la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos kha gcig so //
NK129(to)003:791: gsang snying las dper na de bzhin sbrid sangs bzhin /
NK129(to)003:792: gsung gcig sgra yis so sor go zer ba yang yod de /
NK129(to)003:793: de dag la yang 'gal ba med de /
NK129(to)003:794: yang dag par na gzugs dang sgrar snang ba med de /
NK129(to)003:795: gdul bya dag pa'i snang ba yin pas gang yang 'thad cing /
NK129(to)003:796: drang don dang nges pa'i don dang /
NK129(to)003:797: dbang po'i rim pa dgongs pa'i tshul du rtogs par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:798: de dag gi rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul rnams rgyas par bshad cing /
NK129(to)003:799: gsang sngags kyang theg pa'i khongs su 'du bar zhor gyis bshad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:800: gnyis pa ni 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa gsungs pa'i tshul la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)003:804: mi ma yin pa'i gnas so //
NK129(to)003:805: 'og min chen po'i gnas de gang yin zhe na /
NK129(to)003:807: gtsang ma'i gnas dag rab spangs pa'i //
NK129(to)003:808: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK129(to)003:813: gnyis 'gyur shin tu dpag pa yis //
NK129(to)003:817: ngo bo mtha' gnyis las 'das pa //
NK129(to)003:818: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang //
NK129(to)003:819: yon tan lnga yi bdag nyid de //
NK129(to)003:820: gru bzhi'i spyi bo 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK129(to)003:823: gnas de'i don la mtshan du smos pa ni /
NK129(to)003:824: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK129(to)003:825: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi gzhal yas /
NK129(to)003:826: gsang chen yum gyi mkha' klong /
NK129(to)003:827: dag pa dbyings kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK129(to)003:828: rnam dag stug po bkod pa /
NK129(to)003:829: rang snang ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK129(to)003:830: ces pa la sogs pa rnam grangs so so la /
NK129(to)003:831: don ngo bo gcig tu mthun pa'i gnas de nyid du /
NK129(to)003:832: ston pa rang shes rig pa'i rgyal po /
NK129(to)003:834: rdo rje 'chang chen po de nyid /
NK129(to)003:835: chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang las sku zhal phyag gi rnam par bzhengs te /
NK129(to)003:836: nges pa lnga ldan gyi tshul gyis 'khor nyid las mi zhan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:837: las dag pa byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor dang /
NK129(to)003:838: rig pa 'dzin pa mchog gi 'khor rnams la rung gi skal bar 'tsham pa'i las dang /
NK129(to)003:841: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:847: phyi ma'i phyi ma nges par bstan pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:848: nus pa bstan pa sngags kyi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:849: 'byed par byed pa lde mig gi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:850: ma tshang ba kha bskong ba'i rgyud la sogs te dpag tu med pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:851: gnyis pa lha'i gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:852: 'og min gyi gnas der bgrod mi nus pa'i lha
NK129(to)003:853: dang mi'i byang chub sems dpa' skal ba dang ldan
NK129(to)003:854: pa rnams la 'og min gtsang ma ris kyi gnas
NK129(to)003:855: dang / dbang bsgyur gyi khang bzangs dang /
NK129(to)003:857: rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang dang /
NK129(to)003:858: 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i 'du khang dam pa /
NK129(to)003:859: lcang lo can gyi pho brang rnams su /
NK129(to)003:860: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams gang la gang 'dul gyi tshul du dpag tu med pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:861: gsum pa mi'i gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:863: lha gnas gsum la sogs par bsgrod mi nus pa'i gang zag skal ba can rnams la /
NK129(to)003:864: ston pa sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK129(to)003:865: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i cha lugs su bstan te dus kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK129(to)003:866: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khri drug stong dang /
NK129(to)003:868: rim pa gnyis pa'i rgyud dang bcas pa mang du gsungs /
NK129(to)003:869: bsil ba tshal la sogs par kri ya'i rgyud mang du gsungs /
NK129(to)003:870: rgyal po in+da b+h+au d+hi'i pho brang du /
NK129(to)003:871: 'og min du gsungs pa'i sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor 'dab pa'i tshul du gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:872: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde ni dpag tu med pa gsungs /
NK129(to)003:873: bzhi pa mi ma yin pa'i gnas su gsungs pa la /
NK129(to)003:874: gnod sbyin gyi gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:875: phyag na rdo rje'i rgyud phal cher dang /
NK129(to)003:876: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud 'bum sde la sogs pa gsungs /
NK129(to)003:877: gshin rje'i gnas su gshin rje dgra nag dang /
NK129(to)003:885: las gshin rgya mtsho'i skor la sogs pa dpag tu med pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:886: srin po'i grong khyer dga' ba can du /
NK129(to)003:890: ya ma snying gzer la sogs pa dpag tu med pa gsungs /
NK129(to)003:891: klu'i gnas su rtogs pa rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:892: 'chi bdag gan log gi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:897: gtsug na me 'bar gyi rgyud la sogs pa dpag tu med pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:898: de ltar ston pas ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul rnams rgyas par bshad nas /
NK129(to)003:899: spyi don gsum pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i bka' de dag bsdus pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:900: gang zag gang gis ji ltar bsdus pa dang /
NK129(to)003:903: de la dang por gang zag gang gis ji ltar bsdus pa ni /
NK129(to)003:904: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dgung lo brgyad cu la mya ngan las 'das pa las /
NK129(to)003:905: bram ze 'dun na 'don dang tsun+d+hasa gsol ba btab pas lo gnyis bzhugs te /
NK129(to)003:906: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis la r+ts+wa mchog drung du shing
NK129(to)003:907: s+aa la zung bzhi'i bar seng ge'i khri steng su
NK129(to)003:909: seng ge'i nyal stabs kyis gzims ste bsnyun pa'i tshul bstan /
NK129(to)003:910: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bka' tha ma gsungs pa'i rjes su /
NK129(to)003:911: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i
NK129(to)003:912: 'jig rten la sogs te 'khor 'dus pa thams cad
NK129(to)003:913: kyi dbus su / ston pa nyid rtag pa rdo
NK129(to)003:914: rje'i sku la bgres rgud 'das grongs la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:915: kyi dbus su / mi mnga' yang / kun rdzob rtag par lta ba rnams sun phyungs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:916: le lo can rnams chos la bskul ba'i brdar /
NK129(to)003:917: dgongs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul bstan te /
NK129(to)003:919: ring bsrel ma ga ta'i khal bre bco brgyad yang
NK129(to)003:920: zer brgyad ma 'ongs pa'i sems can bsod nams bsags
NK129(to)003:922: tshems g.yas kyi mche ba g.yas pa ni /
NK129(to)003:923: sum cu rtsa gsum du lha'i dbang pos lha rnams kyis mchod pa'i rten du gdan drangs /
NK129(to)003:924: dbu thod dpral ba'i phyogs ni /
NK129(to)003:925: ka ma la'i rgyal pos pho brang du gdan drangs
NK129(to)003:926: pa la sogs mdzad pa ni mya ngan las 'das
NK129(to)003:927: pa las ji ltar gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK129(to)003:928: de nas dgra bcom pa rnams kyis bka'i bsdu ba byed par 'dod pa na /
NK129(to)003:929: sangs rgyas ma 'das pa'i gong du mo'u mgal gyi bu dang /
NK129(to)003:930: sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pa dgra bcom pa mang
NK129(to)003:931: po zhig ston pa mya ngan las 'da' ba sems
NK129(to)003:933: mya ngan gyi dbang du 'chi bas de bas da lta rung /
NK129(to)003:934: zhes me'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs shing mya ngan las 'das so //
NK129(to)003:935: yang kha cig gis bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:936: mo'u 'gal gyi bu ni bas mtha' zhig tu mu stegs pas bgrongs pa'i brjod bya yang snang ngo //
NK129(to)003:937: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i dus su yang /
NK129(to)003:938: skyo ba skyes pa'i tshul gyis /
NK129(to)003:939: dgra bcom pa grangs med pa mya ngan las 'das pas /
NK129(to)003:940: 'phags pa 'od srung gis dgra bcom pa rnams la smras pa /
NK129(to)003:941: dgra bcom pa thams cad 'di ltar yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa na ni /
NK129(to)003:942: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dus cig la nub ste /
NK129(to)003:943: bka'i bsdu ba yang sus byed /
NK129(to)003:944: bka'i bsdu ba ma byas par ni /
NK129(to)003:945: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad mun pa dang 'dra bar gyur pas /
NK129(to)003:946: dgra bcom pa rnams mya ngan las mi 'da' ba'i khrims bya'o //
NK129(to)003:948: der dgra bcom pa lnga brgyar cig gis ma langs pa las /
NK129(to)003:949: kun dga' bo ni bslab pa la rgyun du zhugs pa las /
NK129(to)003:950: dgra bcom pa ma thob pas /
NK129(to)003:951: lnga brgya la cig gis ma langs nas /
NK129(to)003:952: de'i tshe lho phyogs kyi bas mtha' zhig na /
NK129(to)003:953: 'phags pa ba lang bdag ces pa'i dgra bcom pa gcig yod pa la /
NK129(to)003:954: kun dga' bo 'bod du btang bas /
NK129(to)003:955: dgra bcom pa de'i drung du phyin nas /
NK129(to)003:956: 'phags pa 'od srungs la sogs pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyi mtshan nyid nas /
NK129(to)003:957: rtsa mchog grong khyer du byon zhes smras pas /
NK129(to)003:958: ba lang bdag gis smras pa /
NK129(to)003:959: ces sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas mi gsungs shing /
NK129(to)003:960: dgra bcom pas de skad zer ba 'gro ba'i mgon po de gzhan du ma gshegs sam /
NK129(to)003:961: sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las sgrol ba'i mnyan pa gru dang bcas pa gang du gshegs /
NK129(to)003:962: lha sbyin gyis zhu ba'i dbang du ma gyur tam /
NK129(to)003:964: kun dga' bo mig mchi mas gang ste smra bar ma nus so //
NK129(to)003:965: der ba glang bdag gis sangs rgyas 'das par shes nas /
NK129(to)003:966: 'gro bar bya ba'i blo yod pas /
NK129(to)003:968: dgra bcom pa grangs kyis thems par bya ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:969: chos gos dang lhung bzed bskur te /
NK129(to)003:970: de nyid du me'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs shing 'das so //
NK129(to)003:971: de nas kun dga' bo slar log ste /
NK129(to)003:972: chos gos dang lhung bzed gtad de ba lang bdag gis ji ltar gyur pa rnams smras pa dang /
NK129(to)003:974: mdo sde rnams kun dga' bos bsdu dgongs pas /
NK129(to)003:975: dgra bcom pa ma thob pas /
NK129(to)003:976: nyid kyis 'dul dgos par gzigs so //
NK129(to)003:977: yang zhi drag gang gis 'dul mnyam par bzhag pas yang /
NK129(to)003:979: de nas 'od srungs kyis kun dga' bo la skyo ba rnam pa brgyad kyis tshar bcad de /
NK129(to)003:980: sangs rgyas 'das pa khyod kyi lan zhes smras /
NK129(to)003:981: ngas ci lan zhes smras pas /
NK129(to)003:982: bdud lha sbyin gyis gsol ba btab pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:983: khyod kyis mi 'da' bar gsol ba ma btab pas lan no //
NK129(to)003:988: sangs rgyas la chu rnyog ma can drangs pas lan zhes rgol /
NK129(to)003:990: de'i tshe bdud kyis chu thams cad med par byas pas /
NK129(to)003:991: ngas phyogs kun tu btsal bas chu de las ma rnyed ces smras so //
NK129(to)003:993: de'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi lhung bzed nam mkha' zed na lhas bdud rtsi'i chus 'gengs so //
NK129(to)003:994: zhes smras pas lan med do //
NK129(to)003:995: yang 'od srungs kyis ston pa 'das pa khyod kyis lan /
NK129(to)003:996: sangs rgyas kyi chos gos 'tshems pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:997: khyod kyis rdog pas mnan pas lan zhes so //
NK129(to)003:998: kun dga' bos de'i tshe 'then mi med zer ro //
NK129(to)003:999: 'od srungs kyis nam mkha' la gtad na lha'i bus 'then no //
NK129(to)003:1000: zhes smras pas lan med do //
NK129(to)003:1001: 'od srungs kyis sangs rgyas 'das pa khyod kyis lan te /
NK129(to)003:1002: tshe lo brgya'i dus na skye dgu'i bdag mo rab tu byung ba'i zhu ngo khyod kyis byas pas /
NK129(to)003:1003: sku tshe nyi shu bstungs te lan no zhes rgol bas /
NK129(to)003:1004: kun dga' bos 'di dang po yum 'das pa'i dus
NK129(to)003:1005: su ma ma byas pas drin che'o zhes pa las
NK129(to)003:1007: gzhan yang bstan du mi rung ba la sangs rgyas
NK129(to)003:1008: kyi mtshan dpe bstan pa la sogs pa skyon yod
NK129(to)003:1009: pa'i spyod pa drag po byas pas /
NK129(to)003:1010: kun dga' bo mig mchi mas gang bzhin du dgra bcom pa de dag gi nang nas phyung nas /
NK129(to)003:1011: phyogs gzhan zhig tu song ste /
NK129(to)003:1012: 'od srungs la sogs pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis bdag phyung ngo //
NK129(to)003:1014: de'i dus su kun dga' bos /
NK129(to)003:1015: 'phags pa 'bri rdzi bu zhes bya ba cig la /
NK129(to)003:1016: ston pa'i bka' mtshan nyid med pa'i chos zhig bstan pas /
NK129(to)003:1017: des tshul bzhin yid la byas pas /
NK129(to)003:1018: lam dri ma med pa'i dgra bcom pa thob bo //
NK129(to)003:1019: de nas 'phags pa 'bri rdzi'i bus kun dga' bo la lung bstan te /
NK129(to)003:1020: nye gnas chen po kun dga' bo /
NK129(to)003:1021: rtse cig tu bsgom na skad cig la dgra bcom pa 'thob par 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:1023: der kun dga' bos rtse cig tu bsgoms pas skad cig ma de la dgra bcom pa thob bo //
NK129(to)003:1024: der dgra bcom pa rnams kyis kun gyi tshogs su spyan drangs te /
NK129(to)003:1025: bsnyen cing bskur te bka' bsdu bar byas so //
NK129(to)003:1026: bka' bsdu ba la yang theg pa che chung gi bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:1028: theg pa chung ba'i bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:1029: 'dul ba gnas brtan nye bar 'khor gyis bsdus /
NK129(to)003:1030: mdo sde kun dga' bos bsdus /
NK129(to)003:1031: mngon pa 'od srungs kyis bsdus par 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:1032: theg pa chen po'i bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)003:1035: mngon pa byams pas bsdus par 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:1036: 'di ni gong 'og gnyis ka la 'gal ba med de /
NK129(to)003:1038: zhib tu bsdus pa'i rnam par 'byed pas so sor byas pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1039: dang po gsum gyis sde snod gsum chos kyi phung po bsdus /
NK129(to)003:1040: 'og ma gsum gyis chos kyi mdzod chen po 'bum phrag bcur bsdus pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1041: gzhan yang rang rang gis thos pa yang yod pas mi 'gal ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:1042: don gnyis pa dus ji tsam nas bsdus pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1043: ston pa 'das pa'i phyi de'i lo dbyar du 'gyangs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1044: kun dga' bos dgra bcom pa ma thob pas 'gyangs pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1045: de nas dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus te /
NK129(to)003:1046: rgyal po ma skyes dgras yon bdag byas nas /
NK129(to)003:1047: a su ra'i brag phug tu snam phran lnga brgya gdan du bting ba la /
NK129(to)003:1048: snga dro 'phags pa nye bar 'khor bzhugs nas 'dul ba'i mdo sde gsungs /
NK129(to)003:1049: gung la 'phags pa kun dga' bo bzhugs nas mdo yi sde snod gsungs /
NK129(to)003:1050: phyi dro 'phags pa 'od srungs kyis mngon pa'i sde snod gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:1051: de'i tshe yang dag tu gsungs shing mi brjed pa'i
NK129(to)003:1052: gzungs su bcangs pa las yi ger ma btab bo
NK129(to)003:1053: // dus der dgra bcom pa rnams kyis chos kyi
NK129(to)003:1054: 'khor lo dang po'i bshad pa bstan bcos bye brag
NK129(to)003:1055: tu bshad mdzod chen mo zhes bya ba shwa lo
NK129(to)003:1057: de'i rjes su dgra bcom pa bdun gyis mngon pa'i bstan bcos bdun mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:1060: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs chos kyi phung po /
NK129(to)003:1063: 'gro ba'i rnam grangs dang bdun mdzad ces grags so //
NK129(to)003:1064: bka'i bsdu ba gnyis pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1065: ston pa 'das nas lo gnyis brgya nas /
NK129(to)003:1066: rgyal po d+har+m+aah a shwa ka zhes bya ba byon nas sbyin bdag mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:1067: rgya gar kun dga' ra bar dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus te /
NK129(to)003:1068: de'i tshe yang dag tu zhib tshags su bsdus pa las yi ger ni ma btab bo //
NK129(to)003:1069: 'di'i dus so so skye bo rnams kyi 'ga' re brjed /
NK129(to)003:1070: 'phags pa rnams kyis ma brjed do //
NK129(to)003:1071: bka' bsdu ba gsum pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1072: ston pa 'das nas lo gsum brgya nas /
NK129(to)003:1073: rgyal po ka ni ka zhes bya ba byon pa'i sku ring la /
NK129(to)003:1075: kha che'i yul kun dga' ra ba zhes bya ba'i
NK129(to)003:1076: dgon pa dza la n+d+ha ra zhes bya ba ru
NK129(to)003:1077: / dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang /
NK129(to)003:1078: ba su mi tra la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' lnga brgya dang /
NK129(to)003:1079: so so'i skye bo sgra don la mkhas pa gnyis brgya lnga bcus bsdus pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1080: 'di'i dus su so so skye bo de rnams kyis phal cher brjed /
NK129(to)003:1081: 'phags pa rnams kyis ni mi rjed pa'i gzungs thob ste /
NK129(to)003:1082: so so skye bo mi rjed pa'i gzungs ma thob pa rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:1083: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa mtha' brtsan par bya ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1084: ma 'ongs 'gro ba rnams kyi rten du /
NK129(to)003:1087: a gro ka'i shun pa rnams la legs par gtan la phab ste /
NK129(to)003:1088: yi ge la dus der btab bo //
NK129(to)003:1089: bla na med pa sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1090: phal cher ni gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rjes gsungs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1091: ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:1093: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su yang dag pa'i rgyud gsungs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1094: skal ba dang ldan pa'i sems can rnams la sus bshad par 'gyur /
NK129(to)003:1097: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad pa dbyer med par 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:1099: rdzogs pa chen po la sogs pa rnying mar grags pa 'ga' zhig ni /
NK129(to)003:1100: sprul pa po dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK129(to)003:1102: lha yi rig 'dzin kun dga' snying po /
NK129(to)003:1103: sprul pa thub pa drug dang /
NK129(to)003:1104: purna nye bar zhi ba la sogs pa'i mkha' 'gro
NK129(to)003:1105: ma dpag tu med pa rnams kyis bsdus par rgyud
NK129(to)003:1106: rang rang gi skabs na gsal lo //
NK129(to)003:1107: de dag ni rgyud kyi bsdu ba mdo tsam rnam par bzhag pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1108: rgyas par yi ges 'jigs pas bka'i 'khor lo gsum pa'i skabs su 'du bas shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:1109: don gsum pa ji ltar bsdus pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1110: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong ji rnyed cig bka' stsal pa rnams don bzhir bsdus te /
NK129(to)003:1111: gnyan po la dgongs te rgyas par bka' stsal pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1112: dbye ba la dgongs te 'bring du bka' stsal pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1113: bsdus pa la dgongs te bsdus nas bka' stsal pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1114: gang zag gi dbang po la dgongs te theg pa rim par bka' stsal pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1115: dang po gnyan po la dgongs te bka' stsal pa yang /
NK129(to)003:1116: 'dod chags kyi gnyan por 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong /
NK129(to)003:1117: zhe sdang gi gnyan por mdo sde nyi khri chig stong /
NK129(to)003:1118: gti mug gi gnyan por mngon pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK129(to)003:1119: dug gsum cha mnyam gyi gnyan por gsang sngags nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK129(to)003:1120: lar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong du gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:1121: gnyis pa dbye ba'i don la dgongs te /
NK129(to)003:1123: bstan pa mtha' dag gsung rabs yan lag bcu gnyis su phye ste /
NK129(to)003:1125: dbyangs su bsnyad pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1126: tshigs su bcad pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1127: ched du brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1128: lung du bstan pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1129: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1130: rmad du byung ba'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1132: rtogs pa brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1133: da ltar byung ba'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1134: skyes pa rabs kyi sde dang /
NK129(to)003:1135: gtan la phab pa'i sde dang bcu gnyis so //
NK129(to)003:1136: gsum pa bsdus pa'i don la dgongs te bsdus par bka' stsal pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1137: bka' thams cad sde snod gsum du bstan pa 'am /
NK129(to)003:1138: theg pa che chung gnyis su bsdus pa'am /
NK129(to)003:1139: yang na sngags mtshan nyid gnyis su bsdus pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1140: bzhi pa gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs te theg pa'i rim par bka' stsal pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1141: yang dag par na theg pa la rims pa med kyang /
NK129(to)003:1142: gang zag dbang po'i rim pas theg par phyes te /
NK129(to)003:1148: yang na shes rab kyi snying po ji ltar zhe na /
NK129(to)003:1150: theg pa'i rang bzhin shes rab snying po ste //
NK129(to)003:1152: nges tshig ni theg pa che ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1153: 'degs par byed pas na theg pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1157: dbye na cig dang du ma dang cig dang du ma med pa gang rung yang rigs te /
NK129(to)003:1159: thegs pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK129(to)003:1160: theg pa cig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK129(to)003:1163: gsang ba'i snying po nges pas na //
NK129(to)003:1164: theg pa'i sgo yang cig las med //
NK129(to)003:1168: che chung rims pa'i blo yod phyir //
NK129(to)003:1169: theg pa'i rim pa ji bzhin te //
NK129(to)003:1170: bsdus pas che chung gnyis kyis so //
NK129(to)003:1173: gdul bya'i dbang gis lha mi'i theg pa dang //
NK129(to)003:1174: nyan thos rang rgyal theg pa dang //
NK129(to)003:1175: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang //
NK129(to)003:1176: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang //
NK129(to)003:1178: gcig dang du ma gang du yang nges pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1180: theg pa'i sgo ni srog med de //
NK129(to)003:1181: cig dang du ma cha shas dang //
NK129(to)003:1182: spyod pa kun las bral ba'o //
NK129(to)003:1184: de dag gi ni ji ltar bsdus pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1185: bsdus pa'i don rnams kyang rgya cher gtan la phab pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1186: spyi don bzhi pa lha dang mi'i yul du ji ltar grags pa'i tshul ni gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:1189: mtshan nyid kyi bka' rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1190: bsdu ba byas nas dge 'dun gyi bsro khang du phyogs cig tu bzhugs pa'am /
NK129(to)003:1191: theg pa'i 'dod pa ltar bgo bsha' bya bar 'dod na'ang /
NK129(to)003:1192: de dag gis long med par mi dang mi ma
NK129(to)003:1193: yin pa rnams kyis thob sha byas nas khyer ro
NK129(to)003:1194: // dus phyis mi yi gnas na bzhugs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1195: 'phags pa dang grub thob rnams kyis rim par bsdus nas dar ba yin cing /
NK129(to)003:1196: mdo rnams tho gar yul du 'thor ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1197: nyi khri sde brgyad yul du 'thor ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1198: 'bum klu'i yul du bzhugs pa la sogs pa du
NK129(to)003:1199: ma zhig slob dpon 'phags pa la sogs pa rnams
NK129(to)003:1201: shas cher rgyus yod phyir mang du ma smros so //
NK129(to)003:1203: rgya gar na gsar rnying du grags pa don gyi med na'ang /
NK129(to)003:1205: 'gyur ba'i khungs kyi gsar rnying du grags pa las /
NK129(to)003:1206: rnying ma ru grags pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK129(to)003:1209: rang snang stug po bkod pa'i gnas dang /
NK129(to)003:1211: 'tsho byed kyi gnas su gsungs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1212: gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rje'am /
NK129(to)003:1213: rdo rje chos sam rdo rje snying po'am /
NK129(to)003:1214: rdo rje thod pa rtsal du gsol ba de nyid kyis /
NK129(to)003:1215: gser gyis glegs bam la beed+aur+ya zhun mas bris te /
NK129(to)003:1216: rin chen sna lnga'i sgrom dang /
NK129(to)003:1217: rin po che sna dgu'i sgrom la sogs par rgya rang nan du btab ste /
NK129(to)003:1218: mchod rten chen po bde byed brtsegs dang /
NK129(to)003:1220: dur khrod brgyad kyi mchod rten dang /
NK129(to)003:1221: o ta na g+hon+d+ha la o rgyan gyi gtsug lag gsum dang /
NK129(to)003:1223: dgongs pa'i rtsal gyis mdun gyi nam mkha' la sbas
NK129(to)003:1224: pa la sogs pa dpag tu med pa sbas pa
NK129(to)003:1225: rnams / grub thob rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po rnams kyis dngos grub so sor brnyed nas /
NK129(to)003:1228: byang chub shing drung du sbas pa du ma zhig /
NK129(to)003:1229: rig 'dzin chen po dga' rab rdo rjes dngos grub du brnyes pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1230: mchod rten bde byed brtsegs su bzhugs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1231: rgya gar gyi rig 'dzin chen po brgyad kyis dngos
NK129(to)003:1232: grub brnyes pa la sogs pa dpag tu med pa'i
NK129(to)003:1234: yi ge 'jigs pas don du dril bas shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:1235: khyad par dgongs pa'i rtsal gyis nam mkha' la sbas zhes pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1240: rgyal po in+d+ra b+ho d+hi la /
NK129(to)003:1241: lag na rdo rjes ri ma la ya gnas lcags
NK129(to)003:1242: 'bar ba'i rtser bka' po ti glegs bam char du
NK129(to)003:1245: chos gdul bya'i dgongs pa la brten nas /
NK129(to)003:1247: kri ya w+aa r+aa na s+aiir babs te /
NK129(to)003:1249: ba dmar po'i 'o ma yod pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1250: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar ba la phab pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1251: ri de lhun cing brjid che bas yo ga'i lha dang mthun pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1252: ma h+aa yo ga rnams rgyal po dza'i khang thog tu babs te /
NK129(to)003:1253: de na longs spyod che bas ma h+aa yo ga'i tshogs grub sla ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1254: a nu yo ga rnams gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse la babs te /
NK129(to)003:1255: de na drag po'i rdzas gnam lcags yod pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1256: a ti yo ga rnams o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling du babs te /
NK129(to)003:1257: gling de ni sa khod snyoms shing mkha' 'gro rtag
NK129(to)003:1258: tu 'du ba'i gnas yin pas rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK129(to)003:1259: rnal 'byor pa spyod pa skyong ba la dgongs pa'o
NK129(to)003:1260: // gzhan yang sna tshogs pa rgyud sde'i rgyud sde brgyad kyi gnas na yod pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1261: gnod sbyin gyi gnas nas phyag na rdo rjes gdan drangs pa rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:1262: gshin rje'i gnas nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis gdan drangs pa rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:1263: srin po'i gnas na yod pa slob dpon pad mas gdan drangs pa rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:1264: gzhan yang mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod na yod pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1265: grub thob rnams kyis mang du gdan drangs te 'dir yi ge 'jigs shing rgyud kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK129(to)003:1268: dar tshul dang bcas pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1269: rgyas par ni kho bo'i gter 'byung chen por shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:1270: rgyud gzhan 'ga' zhig ni da dung mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod na mang du bzhugs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1271: 'ga' zhig ni sngon sdud pa po rnams kyis bsdu bar ma nus te /
NK129(to)003:1272: sgra rang yal la song ba yang yod ces grags so //
NK129(to)003:1273: sngon gsungs pa la don med snyam na /
NK129(to)003:1274: shin tu yod de sngon byung gi 'khor gtogs pa
NK129(to)003:1275: chen po la gnas pa rnams kyi sgro 'dogs bcad
NK129(to)003:1276: pa yin no // de yang rgyud rnams 'ga' zhig ni shin tu dar rgyas che /
NK129(to)003:1277: 'ga' zhig ni 'gro don bag re byas nas nub /
NK129(to)003:1278: 'ga' zhig ni mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod na da dung
NK129(to)003:1279: 'byon te dar rgyas su 'gyur bar lung gi bstan
NK129(to)003:1280: pa kho na ltar yin no //
NK129(to)003:1281: yang deng sang gi rtog ge ba la sogs bod kyi slob dpon kha gcig /
NK129(to)003:1282: de lta bu'i babs dong gtan tshig la nges pa med do zer na /
NK129(to)003:1283: lo ts+aa ba zur ga rdor gyis dpal na len
NK129(to)003:1284: sh+ri len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na po ti'i char babs
NK129(to)003:1285: pa'i rgyus rnams gyang ris lha khang la ri mo
NK129(to)003:1287: sngon byung bstan pa grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:1288: sa la gnas pa'i pan+di ta dang /
NK129(to)003:1290: byang chub sems dpa'i yon bdag rnams bzhugs pa'i dus
NK129(to)003:1291: su gtan la phab pa'i gna' gtam lo rgyus yin
NK129(to)003:1292: pas shin tu yid ches par shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:1293: yang gsang sngags gsar ma'i dbang du byas na /
NK129(to)003:1294: 'di la mi mthun pa'i 'dod 'ga' re snang ste /
NK129(to)003:1296: bcom ldan 'das grong khyer mnyan yod na bzhugs pa'i dus /
NK129(to)003:1297: de nas nub phyogs su dpag tshad sum brgya na o rgyan gyi yul yod de /
NK129(to)003:1298: de na rgyal po in+d+ra b+ho d+he bzhugs pa la /
NK129(to)003:1299: snga dro'i dus cig gi tshe dge slong gi gzugs gcig nam mkha' la 'gro ba mthong nas /
NK129(to)003:1300: de dag ci yin zhes dris pa la /
NK129(to)003:1301: 'di nas shar phyogs su dpag tshad sum brgya na mnyan yod ces bya ba'i grong khyer na /
NK129(to)003:1302: rgyal po zas gtsang gi sras sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya ba'i slob ma yin no //
NK129(to)003:1304: de skad thos pas rgyal po rab tu dad de /
NK129(to)003:1305: rgyal pos de phyogs su phyag 'tshal thal mo sbyar bas /
NK129(to)003:1306: mnyan yod na bcom ldan 'das dge 'dun gyi 'khor stong gnyis brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK129(to)003:1307: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor dpag tu med pa dang bcas pa bzhugs pa mthong ngo //
NK129(to)003:1308: der mos pa chen po'i dbang gis /
NK129(to)003:1309: bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa /
NK129(to)003:1310: thugs rje dang rdzu 'phrul gyi zhabs mnga' ba /
NK129(to)003:1311: sang bdag nyid gdugs tshod la bab pas gshegs par zhu /
NK129(to)003:1313: sang gdugs tshod la bcom ldan 'das 'khor dpag tu med pa dang bcas pa /
NK129(to)003:1314: bya'i rgyal po 'dab bzang ltar nam mkha' la byon te /
NK129(to)003:1315: pho brang gi yang thog tu babs te gdan bshams pa la bzhugs nas /
NK129(to)003:1316: gdugs tshod gsol ba'i rjes su /
NK129(to)003:1317: rgyal pos phyag 'tshal gus pa chen pos thal mo sbyar te mdun du 'dug nas /
NK129(to)003:1318: ston pa thabs mkhas thugs rje dang ldan pas bdag
NK129(to)003:1319: cag srid pa'i sdug bsngal las thar bar mdzad du
NK129(to)003:1322: kyee rgyal po chen po khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung na thabs yod do //
NK129(to)003:1325: bdag cag ni 'dod don gyi gdungs pa che zhing /
NK129(to)003:1326: 'jig rten gyi longs spyod la shin tu sred pas /
NK129(to)003:1327: 'di ma spangs par 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i thabs cig zhu zhes zhus pas /
NK129(to)003:1329: gsang sngags kyi snod du gzigs nas /
NK129(to)003:1330: de'i tshe skye bo chags pa can rjes su bzung ba'i phyir rdo rje 'chang du bzhengs nas /
NK129(to)003:1331: rdo rje btsun mo'i ba ga la bzhugs te /
NK129(to)003:1332: rgyal po btsun mo lnga brgya dang bcas pa'i 'khor rnams la dbang bskur /
NK129(to)003:1333: smin cing grol bar mdzad nas /
NK129(to)003:1334: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde dpag tu med pa gsungs
NK129(to)003:1335: pa phyag na rdo rjes bsdus te mkha' 'gro ma
NK129(to)003:1336: la gtad / 'ga' zhig ni dbus 'gyur tshal 'od ma'i gtsug lag khang du yang sbas te /
NK129(to)003:1337: dus phyis gru thob rnams kyis rims par blangs nas dar bar byas pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1340: bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyal po la min /
NK129(to)003:1341: lag na rdo rjes rgyal po smin par lung bstan te /
NK129(to)003:1342: mya ngan las 'da' khar 'jam dpal gyis zhus pa las /
NK129(to)003:1344: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK129(to)003:1345: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK129(to)003:1346: mi la skal ldan mchog gyur pa //
NK129(to)003:1347: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK129(to)003:1348: thugs rje ldan pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK129(to)003:1349: lag na rdo rjes ston par 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:1351: phyag na rdo rjes rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la gtad /
NK129(to)003:1352: de dag gis bsgrubs pas dngos grub rim par thob par gyur te /
NK129(to)003:1353: der rgyal po sras btsun mo mnga' ris 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad /
NK129(to)003:1354: lus ma spang nas lhag med du gshegs nas /
NK129(to)003:1355: dus de'i skabs su nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul mtha' zhig stongs par gyur skad /
NK129(to)003:1356: de klu'i bdag byas te mtsho chen po zhig tu gyur /
NK129(to)003:1357: der gsang ba'i bdag pos rgyud rnams klu rnams la byin cing lam du bcug pas /
NK129(to)003:1358: klu rnams kyang rims kyi mir gyur nas /
NK129(to)003:1359: mtsho de yang rim gyi sa'i gling chen por gyur te /
NK129(to)003:1360: de la grong 'chas nas mi rnams kyis nyams su blangs pas phal cher gyis ni grub pa thob /
NK129(to)003:1361: ma thob pa rnams kyang pho thams cad dpa' bo /
NK129(to)003:1362: mo thams cad dpa' mor gyur nas /
NK129(to)003:1363: o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling zhes su grags zer ba'i 'dod pa yang yod do //
NK129(to)003:1364: mdor na rgyud rnams nas gsungs pa'i gnas ni ma
NK129(to)003:1365: nges so sor gsungs kyang rgyud rnams kyi bdag po
NK129(to)003:1367: o rgyan mkha' 'gro ma'i gling yin pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:1368: rgyud thams cad ni phal cher o rgyan mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang mdzod na yod pas /
NK129(to)003:1369: grub thob rnams kyis thabs du ma'i sgo nas gdan drangs pa yod do //
NK129(to)003:1370: rgyal po ba su skal pas gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1372: klu sgrub kyis glan par bardzusa nas kyee rdor gdan drangs /
NK129(to)003:1373: ku ku ri pas ma h+aa ma ya gdan drangs /
NK129(to)003:1374: ma ti badz+ra gyis 'jigs byed la sogs pa gdan drangs pa'i lo rgyus du ma yod do //
NK129(to)003:1375: 'o na de ltar lo rgyus mi mthun pa gnyis su byung ba ci yin snyam na /
NK129(to)003:1376: spyir gang zag gis thos dus dang /
NK129(to)003:1377: gnas skabs kyi dus snga phyis kyang byung ba yin la /
NK129(to)003:1378: mkhas pa chen po rog gi ban+de shes rab 'od kyis lung bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:1379: dus phyis rgya gar yul du bstan pa'i grwa nyams shing /
NK129(to)003:1380: rgyud sde chen po rnams rim gyis nub rgya dpe
NK129(to)003:1381: rnams kyang gnyer chis ci lta ba bzhin ma byung
NK129(to)003:1382: ba dang / rgya gar rlan dang tsha rlan che bas mang po rul /
NK129(to)003:1383: grub thob kha yar gyis kyang /
NK129(to)003:1384: mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang mdzod nas blangs shing bshad pas /
NK129(to)003:1385: byung tshul ji lta ba khong du ma chud pa yin /
NK129(to)003:1386: dus phyis bod kyi bstan pa phyi dar du grags pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:1387: rgya gar pan+di ta gser 'dod can rnams kyis bod
NK129(to)003:1388: na chos gang la rtsis che dris nas bcos ma
NK129(to)003:1389: mang po byed / lo ts+aa ba mkhas 'dod can rnams kyis dbyar mon yul du sdod /
NK129(to)003:1391: sngon gyi lo phan sprul pa'i sku byang chub sems
NK129(to)003:1392: dpa' rnams kyis bsgyur ba'i chos la rang bzo'i 'gyur
NK129(to)003:1394: rtsa rlung thig le la sogs pa phyi rol dang
NK129(to)003:1395: thun mong gi chos la ngo mtshar ba'i gnas su
NK129(to)003:1396: byas nas rgya gar gyi khungs bzang po drangs /
NK129(to)003:1397: bdag rkyen bzang pos gser chos byas pas bstan pa nyams smad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1398: zhes gsungs pa 'di yang shin tu nas dag pas
NK129(to)003:1399: phyogs ris med pa'i mkhas pa rnams kyis legs par
NK129(to)003:1400: dgongs pa thong zhig thong zhig /
NK129(to)003:1401: da ni bka' 'khor lo de dag gi rjes su
NK129(to)003:1402: 'jug cing bstan pa rgyas par byed pa bstan bcos
NK129(to)003:1403: yin pas / de dag gi brjod pa cung zhig bsnyad par bya ste /
NK129(to)003:1411: dang po ngo bo ni sems can gyi nyon mongs pa spang shing ngan 'gro las skyob pa ste /
NK129(to)003:1413: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'joms pa dang //
NK129(to)003:1414: ngan 'gro srid la skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK129(to)003:1415: chos spyod yon tan che na bstan bcos te //
NK129(to)003:1416: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK129(to)003:1419: bka'i don ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa mi gsal ba rnams gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1424: don med pa ni bya rog gi bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:1425: don log pa ni mu stegs pa'i bstan bcos rnams so //
NK129(to)003:1426: don dang ldan pa ni nang pa'i bstan bcos te /
NK129(to)003:1427: de la yang rtsod pa lhur len pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1430: ngag gi 'grel pa sgra'i bstan bcos dang /
NK129(to)003:1431: brjod byed tshig gi 'grel pa tshad ma'i bstan bcos so //
NK129(to)003:1432: bsgrub pa lhur len pa la yang gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:1433: lung bsdus pa'i bstan bcos dang /
NK129(to)003:1436: sangs rgyas kyi bka' rgya che /
NK129(to)003:1438: de dag sems can gyi so sor bsdu mi nus pas /
NK129(to)003:1439: de'i don 'phags pa rnams kyis bstan bcos mang du mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:1440: de ma rtogs pa rtogs par byed pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1441: bsgribs pa gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1442: zab mo'i dgongs pa gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i dgos pa yod cing /
NK129(to)003:1445: sangs rgyas kyi bka' rdo rje'i tshigs su gnas pas /
NK129(to)003:1446: skye bo phal pas de'i don rtogs pa'i gnas med pas /
NK129(to)003:1447: 'phags pa dang gang zag dam pa rnams kyis bka'i bshad 'grel chen mo rnams mdzad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1449: bka' thams cad sde snod gsum du 'dus pas bstan bcos kyang sde snod gsum du 'du ba'o //
NK129(to)003:1450: dang po bstan bcos la snga ba ni /
NK129(to)003:1451: mngon pa sde bdun yin te /
NK129(to)003:1452: kha cig thub pa ma 'das pa'i gong du brtsams par yang 'dod la /
NK129(to)003:1454: bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo snga ste /
NK129(to)003:1455: bka' bsdu ba mdzad pa'i thog ma la mdzad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1456: chos kyi 'khor lo rims pa gsum dang bstun nas bstan bcos kyang gsum du 'byung ba las /
NK129(to)003:1458: bka'i 'khor lo dang po'i dgongs 'grel bye brag bshad
NK129(to)003:1459: mdzod chen mo sho lo ka 'bum yod pa mdzad
NK129(to)003:1460: / mngon pa sde bdun 'dul ba mdo rtsa la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1461: bka' 'khor lo bar pa grol bar byed pa la /
NK129(to)003:1462: don gyis 'grel pa dbu ma rig pa'i tshogs drug dang sher gsum mdzod /
NK129(to)003:1465: rig pa drug cu pa stong nyid bdun bcu pa /
NK129(to)003:1468: gang la 'jigs med la sogs pa rnams so //
NK129(to)003:1469: rjes dpag gi rgyan gnyis las /
NK129(to)003:1472: de rnams la yang gsal byed kyi 'grel pa /
NK129(to)003:1473: rtsa she'i 'grel pa sangs rgyas dbyangs kyis mdzad /
NK129(to)003:1474: de'i 'grel pa b+ha byi pas mdzad /
NK129(to)003:1475: de'i 'grel pa spyan ras gzigs kyis brtul zhugs pas mdzad //
NK129(to)003:1476: bka' 'khor lo gsum pa'i bstan bcos byams pa mgon po'i gzhung lugs te chos lnga mdzad pa las /
NK129(to)003:1477: mdo sde spyi'i 'grel pa mdo sde rgyan bye brag
NK129(to)003:1478: tu phye ba pha rol tu phyin pa'i 'grel pa
