NK129(to)003:1479: mngon rtogs rgyan / gzungs kyi dbang phyug gi 'grel pa'i rgyud bla ma /
NK129(to)003:1480: dbus mtha' chos dang chos min rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1482: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i sa sde lnga dang /
NK129(to)003:1484: don gsal ba la sogs pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:1485: de gnyis ka'i thun mong rgyud bla ma la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1486: mdor na re re la'ang theg pa che chung gnyis gnyis tshang ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1487: gsum gsum du don gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1488: da ni sngags kyi don gtan la 'bebs pa la lnga ste /
NK129(to)003:1496: shes pa skyob par byed pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1497: yang na ni ngo bo'i rang bzhin nyid de /
NK129(to)003:1499: da ni yid ces bya ba ste /
NK129(to)003:1500: ra ni skyob par byed pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1502: 'o na pha rol tu phyin pas kyang yid ches skyob na /
NK129(to)003:1503: sngags dang khyad par ci yod zhe na /
NK129(to)003:1505: myur bar skyob pas khyad par che ste /
NK129(to)003:1507: dka' thub dka' spyad 'dir mi bya //
NK129(to)003:1508: khrims dang sdom pa 'dir mi dgos //
NK129(to)003:1510: don zab pas dbang po rab tshe 'dir sangs rgyas /
NK129(to)003:1512: tha ma srid pa bar do /
NK129(to)003:1513: yang tha yang skye ba bdun tshun la sangs rgyas te /
NK129(to)003:1515: 'di yis bcom ldan bdag nyid zhes //
NK129(to)003:1516: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba'i //
NK129(to)003:1517: ye shes rgya mtshos rnam par brgyan //
NK129(to)003:1520: don du dril bas sngags kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)003:1521: stong nyid snying rje'i bdag nyid la bya ste /
NK129(to)003:1523: stong pa nyid dang snying rje ni //
NK129(to)003:1524: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK129(to)003:1525: gsang sngags zhes ni de la bya //
NK129(to)003:1529: snod ldan la basngagasa pas na gsang sngags te /
NK129(to)003:1531: gsang sngags gsang zhes bya ba ni //
NK129(to)003:1532: chos la skyon yod ma yin te //
NK129(to)003:1533: snod min sems can blo chung la //
NK129(to)003:1534: thugs rje'i thabs kyi rab tu gsang //
NK129(to)003:1537: gsang sngags rig sngags gzungs sngags so //
NK129(to)003:1540: ma rig rnams la gsang ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)003:1541: gsang sngags zhes su grags pa yin //
NK129(to)003:1542: de don phyin ci ma log pas //
NK129(to)003:1543: rig sngags zhes su btags pa yin //
NK129(to)003:1544: stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK129(to)003:1545: gzungs sngags zhes su btags pa yin //
NK129(to)003:1548: lha yab yum zung 'brel du yod pa gsang sngags /
NK129(to)003:1549: pho shas che ba rig sngags /
NK129(to)003:1550: mo shas che ba gzungs sngags so zer /
NK129(to)003:1553: tad+ya th+aa las drangs pa rig sngags /
NK129(to)003:1554: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya las drangs pa gzungs sngags so zhes zer te /
NK129(to)003:1555: re re la'ang kun yod de phyogs cig gis nges pa med pa 'dra snyam mo //
NK129(to)003:1557: mi 'gyur ba sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi ngo bo nyid de /
NK129(to)003:1559: chos kyi snying po sgrub byed cing //
NK129(to)003:1560: chos kyi dbyings dang yang dag ldan //
NK129(to)003:1561: gsang sngags mtshan nyid yin par gsungs //
NK129(to)003:1563: rnam grangs la 'dod bzhed mang ste /
NK129(to)003:1564: o rgyan chen po'i bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)003:1565: spyir ni mtha' dang ma lus bgrang bar mi nus shing /
NK129(to)003:1571: grangs ni mtha' dang mu med de //
NK129(to)003:1572: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'jug /
NK129(to)003:1573: brjod pa'i tshig rnams mtha' zad pas //
NK129(to)003:1574: yang dag don gyi snying por 'du //
NK129(to)003:1577: gang la gnyis med ye shes snang bar 'du ba yin /
NK129(to)003:1579: kun dga' snying po'i bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)003:1581: ston pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo'i 'khor lo yin la /
NK129(to)003:1582: rjod byed kyi sgra spyi'i rnam pa yi ger snang ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:1585: rgyud kyi ngo bo thabs shes gnyis med yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1587: thabs dang shes rab bdag nyid rgyud //
NK129(to)003:1588: 'di ni bdag gis bshad kyi nyon //
NK129(to)003:1592: nges pa'i tshig ni drug yin te //
NK129(to)003:1593: phun sum tshogs lngas ni che phyir dang //
NK129(to)003:1594: 'brel dang ma tshangs med phyir dang //
NK129(to)003:1595: dkrugs pa'i phyir na rag las phyir //
NK129(to)003:1596: gsang sngags bzlas pa ston phyir ro //
NK129(to)003:1600: rgyud kyi dbye ba gnyis yin te //
NK129(to)003:1601: brjod bya don gyi rgyud dang ni //
NK129(to)003:1602: rjod byed tshig gi rgyud gnyis so //
NK129(to)003:1605: byang chub sems dpa'i lung las /
NK129(to)003:1606: sku lnga ye shes lnga yi bdag /
NK129(to)003:1607: lam gyi rgyud la nyer sbyor zhing //
NK129(to)003:1608: 'khrul pa med pa rdo rje'i tshig /'bras bu yang dag lam du ni //
NK129(to)003:1613: rtsa ba bshad dang man ngag dang //
NK129(to)003:1614: phyi ma dang ni snying po'i rgyud //
NK129(to)003:1615: kha bskang dang ni sngags kyi rgyud //
NK129(to)003:1616: 'byed par byed pa lde mig tu //
NK129(to)003:1617: mtha' drug tshul bzhi rnam par phye //
NK129(to)003:1619: de ltar lha dang mi'i yul du grags tshul /
NK129(to)003:1620: bka' dang bstan bcos kyi rnam dbye /
NK129(to)003:1621: ngo bo dang nges tshig la sogs pa mtshan nyid dang rnam grangs bcas pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1622: da ni spyi don lnga pa'i tha ma chos 'di dag thams cad dgongs don /
NK129(to)003:1623: rgya bod kyi 'brel tshul la brten nas rang gi 'dod phyogs dang /
NK129(to)003:1624: rnam par bzhag pa ston pa la bdun te /
NK129(to)003:1627: gsar rnying du grags pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK129(to)003:1628: de gnyis kyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)003:1629: tha snyad mkhan gyis rtsod pa bzlog pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1630: chos spyi'i rnam bzhag mdor bsdus te bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1631: ji ltar brtsams pas bstan pa'i rnam gzhag smon lam bkra shis dang bcas pa'o //
NK129(to)003:1632: de la dang po rnying ma'i rgyud rnams rgya gar du ji ltar babs pa'i tshul ni /
NK129(to)003:1633: rgyas par ni gong du bshad pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:1634: khyad par du 'dir yang yid ches pa'i don du ston te /
NK129(to)003:1635: de yang gsar rnying gnyis ni /
NK129(to)003:1636: rgya gar rang du snga phyi ni khyad par che ste /
NK129(to)003:1637: rnying ma'i gru thob rnams ni ston pa 'das nas ring por ma lon par byung zhing /
NK129(to)003:1638: gsar ma'i rgyud la dbang ba'i slob dpon rnams ni dus phyi ma las ma byung /
NK129(to)003:1639: de yang rnying ma'i slob dpon rnams ni rgyud dang
NK129(to)003:1640: dbang gis chu klung chen po bzhi babs pas na
NK129(to)003:1641: bka' shin tu dam pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1642: bka' rgyud kyang nyung bar byon no //
NK129(to)003:1643: gsar ma'i slob dpon rnams ni rgyud gang rnyed nas
NK129(to)003:1644: brtsam grangs mang zhing bka' rgyud mang ba yin no
NK129(to)003:1645: // de yang rnying ma rnams dang po ji ltar snga na /
NK129(to)003:1646: o rgyan chen po de ni ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK129(to)003:1647: lo bcu gnyis nas byon pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1648: dbus 'gyur tshal lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK129(to)003:1649: rtag lta sun 'byin nga ni mya ngan 'da' //
NK129(to)003:1650: chad lta bsal phyir bzhi gsum bcu gnyis na //
NK129(to)003:1651: ko sha'i mtsho gling dri med pad+ma las //
NK129(to)003:1652: rgyal po'i thug dgyes sras kyi dam par 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:1653: bla med snying po don gyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK129(to)003:1655: rnam thar chen mo nas ston pa'i nye gnas kun dga' bo las rab tu byung bar bshad do //
NK129(to)003:1656: de nas dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK129(to)003:1660: ston pa 'das nas sum brgya tshun chod la thams cad byon pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1661: 'di rnams kyang shas cher kha che dang /
NK129(to)003:1663: dbus 'gyur tshal phan du byon pa shas che ba kho na yin no //
NK129(to)003:1664: de'i tshe dbang gi chos rnams kyang /
NK129(to)003:1665: rdo rje sems dpa' dngos dang /
NK129(to)003:1667: mkha' 'gro ma las kyi dbang mo che dang /
NK129(to)003:1668: de rnams kyi mngon sum du mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang
NK129(to)003:1669: mdzod rin po che'i ga'u rnams phyes nas dbang bskur
NK129(to)003:1670: lung bstan / rgyud smin cing grol bar byas pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1671: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta gzhan rnams dang mi mnyam pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1672: de yang o rgyan chen po la ni /
NK129(to)003:1673: khungs med pa'i sde brgyad kyi gnas la sogs pa'i rgyud sde mtha' med pa rnams kyang /
NK129(to)003:1674: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis mngon sum du gtad nas /
NK129(to)003:1675: phyis bsam yas su rgya dpe thams cad kyang slebs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1676: dus phyis jo bo a ti sha bod du bsam yas su byon pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:1677: khri snyan gyi pags pa gdan bting nas mar me
NK129(to)003:1678: bshams te rgya dpe rnams nyin mtshan du gzigs pa
NK129(to)003:1679: mdzad / de'i dus su jo bos gsungs nas /
NK129(to)003:1680: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas de ni mkha' 'gro ma rnams bran du khol /
NK129(to)003:1681: snang srid la dbang thob pas sde brgyad la sogs
NK129(to)003:1682: mkha' 'gro'i gnas na yod pa rnams kyang gdan drangs
NK129(to)003:1684: lan cig bdag la yang rgya gar mkha' 'gro ma
NK129(to)003:1685: rnams kyis rgyud kyi gsang mdzod phyes nas bstan pa
NK129(to)003:1686: yin te / rgya gar na med pa'i rgyud kyang
NK129(to)003:1687: 'di na mang du bzhugs 'dug pa ngo mtshar ro
NK129(to)003:1688: yin te / // ces pa'i thugs dgyes chen po
NK129(to)003:1689: mdzad pa yang jo bo'i rnam thar chen po lta
NK129(to)003:1690: yin te / // bar gsal lo // khyad par
NK129(to)003:1691: rdzogs pa chen po 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i
NK129(to)003:1692: rgyud gdams pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK129(to)003:1693: dga' rab rdo rje nas bdag cag gi bla ma
NK129(to)003:1694: o rgyan chen po dang b+ai ma la'i bar du
NK129(to)003:1696: bla ma gong ma de dag kyang phung po lhag med du 'grub pa sha stag yin no //
NK129(to)003:1697: des na gu ru dang b+ai ma la gnyis bod du byon dus cig rgyud yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1698: rgya dpe rnams ma lus pa bod du gdan drangs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1699: rgya gar du bka' dam pas ma dar bas ma spel ba'i don gyis /
NK129(to)003:1700: dus phyis rnyed pa'i yul med pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1701: dang po lag na rdo rjes gsungs pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1702: gser gyi shog gu la beed+aur+ya zhun mas bris pa'i rang byung gi rgyud rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:1703: bstan pa'i btsas su bzhag pa sku gsung thugs kyi rten rnams /
NK129(to)003:1704: rdo rje gdan gyi steng gi nam mkha' la rin
NK129(to)003:1705: po che'i 'od kyi gzhal yas khang na bzhugs te
NK129(to)003:1706: / mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis rtag tu mchod pa 'bul ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:1707: nam zhig na ston pa re 'jig rten du byon pa'i dus /
NK129(to)003:1708: rang bzhin gyi babs pa ma gtogs pa /
NK129(to)003:1709: gang zag su gang gis spyod yul du ma gyur pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1710: 'di dag kyang bka'i bab chen mo las bshad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1711: de ma yin pa'i bka' brgyad spyi yi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:1712: bye brag gi so so'i rgyud gdams pa dang bcas pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1713: gu ru dang b+ai ma la gnyis la /
NK129(to)003:1714: rgya gar du rig 'dzin brgyad kyis rgyud gdams pa
NK129(to)003:1715: dang bcas pa ma lus par phul nas thams cad
NK129(to)003:1716: bod du gdan drangs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1717: spel bar 'os pa rnams ka ma la ru spel /
NK129(to)003:1718: ma 'ongs pa'i don du gter du brtsal /
NK129(to)003:1719: de'i phyir lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis khungs chod pa'i don med pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1720: gzhan sems smad bco brgyad dang /
NK129(to)003:1721: klong sde'i skor la brgya dang brgyad /
NK129(to)003:1722: rgyud bu chung sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK129(to)003:1723: lung ye shes mar me'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:1724: man ngag snying dgongs la sogs pa /
NK129(to)003:1725: rang rgyud so so'i skor la lnga brgya dang drug bcu /
NK129(to)003:1726: 'di dag ni lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis sgras bsgyur te /
NK129(to)003:1727: rgya dpe rnams kyang phal cher bsam yas rang na bzhugs pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1728: de nas chos 'khor chen po bstan pa snga dar ba'i dus /
NK129(to)003:1729: sprul pa'i rgyal blon rnams kyis sbyin bdag mdzad nas /
NK129(to)003:1730: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis bsgyur bas snga 'gyur yin pas rnying mar grags pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:1731: gzhan yang rnying ma'i rgyud sde rnams kyi babs so 'ga' zhig ni /
NK129(to)003:1732: rdo rje gdan gyi shar lho mtshams za hor gyi yul yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1733: de dus pan+di ta rnams kyang za hor du rig pa sbyangs pa'i /
NK129(to)003:1734: bod du spyan drangs pa'i pan+di ta /
NK129(to)003:1736: rgya gar shar phyogs pa'i pan+di ta d+ha na sh+ai la dang /
NK129(to)003:1738: su ran tra pa la sogs pa rnams kyi /
NK129(to)003:1739: gong gi rgyud rnams za hor gyi yi ger yod pas /
NK129(to)003:1740: yul dbus kyi pan+di ta rnams kyis mi klog pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1741: gzhan yang za hor gyi yul du /
NK129(to)003:1742: mtha' yi rgyal pos dmag drangs nas chos bsnubs /
NK129(to)003:1743: dus phyis khungs med du'ang 'ga' song zer ba'ang yod de /
NK129(to)003:1745: ka ba bum pa can gyi 'og na /
NK129(to)003:1746: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud mang du bzhugs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:1747: gong du sh+ri sing ha dang /
NK129(to)003:1749: gu ru dang b+ai ma la la gtad de /
NK129(to)003:1750: da rung lhag ma mang du yod pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1751: lo ts+aa ba ka cog rma gsum gyis mkhas pa b+ai ma la spyan drangs pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:1752: rgya gar gyi pan+di tas phrag dog byas nas /
NK129(to)003:1753: phra ma'i dbang gis b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs pa'i snying nad dang /
NK129(to)003:1754: b+ai ma la mkhas grags pas /
NK129(to)003:1755: rgyal po mi la ku tra dang /
NK129(to)003:1757: bsam yas rgyal po'i bka' ma chog pa skad zer yang /
NK129(to)003:1758: pan+di ta rnams kyis bod du song na dga' byas pas de'i zhe nad du /
NK129(to)003:1759: b+ai ma la dpon g.yog gi rgyal po dang /
NK129(to)003:1760: pan+di ta la zhu ba phul ba /
NK129(to)003:1762: sngon chad ma grags pa'i chos rdzong dgos par zhus pas /
NK129(to)003:1763: pan+di ta rnams na re rdo rje gdan gyi 'og
NK129(to)003:1764: na rdzogs pa chen po'i chos dpag tu med pa
NK129(to)003:1765: yod de / 'o skol rgya gar ba la dus
NK129(to)003:1766: la ma bab bar du bshad pa dbang med kyang
NK129(to)003:1767: yod de / / khyod bod du 'gro ba yus che ba yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1768: ci tsam rig pa thon la khyer cig zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:1769: b+ai ma la dpon g.yog gis zhe nad yod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1770: b+ai ma la yang dus phyis rgya gar du mi ldog par dgongs nas /
NK129(to)003:1771: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos rnams ma lus par gdan
NK129(to)003:1772: drangs nas rgya dpe thams cad rtsad bcad pa yin
NK129(to)003:1773: no // de la dus phyis bod kyi lo ts+aa ba kha cig na re /
NK129(to)003:1775: rgya gar na rgya dpe mi 'dug zer ba'i brjod bya 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:1776: blo gzu bor bzhag nas bden rdzun gyi khungs btsun par byed na ni /
NK129(to)003:1777: gong gi de rnams la yid ches par bya zhing /
NK129(to)003:1778: de ltar ma yin na ni su dang su'i chos la yang nges tig gi gnas med do //
NK129(to)003:1779: de ma yin pa yang sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba rnams sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1780: rgya gar gyi ske tshangs bcu gsum du /
NK129(to)003:1781: dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga dang mjal nus pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1782: nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul thams cad chu bzhin rgyug nus pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1783: rkang mgyogs kyi rdzu 'phrul thob pas rgya gar dbus
NK129(to)003:1784: 'gyur tshal nas nyin cig la bod du bsgrod nus
NK129(to)003:1785: pa la sogs pa b+aee ro tsa na'i rnam thar
NK129(to)003:1786: na gsal zhing / dus phyis rnams ni so so'i skye bo'i lo ts+aa ba yin pas /
NK129(to)003:1787: mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod ni 'byed pa'i skabs med /
NK129(to)003:1788: nub phyogs o rgyan du ni mi rdol /
NK129(to)003:1789: rgya gar shar phyogs dang bal po'i yul la skyog
NK129(to)003:1790: bdar byas pa'i lo rgyus rnams 'og nas bstan no
NK129(to)003:1791: // de yang lo pan chen po snga dar ba'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:1792: bka' dang bstan bcos ci tsam 'gyur ba ni /
NK129(to)003:1793: zhib tu ni dpag par mi lang zhing /
NK129(to)003:1794: che long tsam zhig 'dir yang bkod par bya ste /
NK129(to)003:1795: phyi mdo dang nang sngags gnyis las /
NK129(to)003:1796: dang po phyi mdo'i sde la /
NK129(to)003:1797: mdo sde legs nyes bstan pa /
NK129(to)003:1802: gang pos rtogs pa brjod pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:1808: ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:1811: tshul khrims ngan pa tshar gcod /
NK129(to)003:1812: de dag drang don spyi'i mdo bcu'o //
NK129(to)003:1813: 'dul ba lung ma tshang ba med pa /
NK129(to)003:1814: dkon mchog brtsegs pa ma tshang ba med pa /
NK129(to)003:1816: byang chub sems dpa'i mdo bcu /
NK129(to)003:1817: rgyas 'bring rnam gsum la sogs nges don bstan pa'i mdo bcu bdun /
NK129(to)003:1818: drang nges gnyis ka bstan pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:1821: 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan gyi mdo /
NK129(to)003:1829: rnam dag dri med kyi mdo /
NK129(to)003:1831: bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:1833: gtsug gtor dri med lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:1834: dge slong lnga brgya lung bstan gyi mdo /
NK129(to)003:1842: bde gshegs bdun gyi smon lam /
NK129(to)003:1844: grwa lnga la sogs pa de dag ni rang gzhung
NK129(to)003:1845: tshugs pa'i mdo che lang du smos pa yin cing
NK129(to)003:1846: / de la mdo zhib tu ni bri bar mi lang ste /
NK129(to)003:1847: bsam gyis mi khyab ste bsam yas rgyal po rang
NK129(to)003:1848: gi bka' chem las kyang rgya gar na ma lus
NK129(to)003:1849: pa tsam cig bsgyur zhes pa yang bka' chem chen
NK129(to)003:1851: bka' de dag dang mthun pa'i bstan bcos bsgyur tshul yang /
NK129(to)003:1852: thog mar snga ba ni bstan bcos mngon pa sde bdun /
NK129(to)003:1853: pra ka ra sde brgyad bsgyur te /
NK129(to)003:1854: mngon pa sde bdun ston pa zhal bzhugs dus 'khor rnams kyis brtsams pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1855: dus phyis bka' bsdu ba mdzad pa'i dus brtsams pa la ni gang zag cung mi mthun na'ang /
NK129(to)003:1856: gong du rgyas par bstan mdzod cing /
NK129(to)003:1857: ston pa bzhugs dus kyi dbang du byas na /
NK129(to)003:1859: chos kyi phung po sh+aa ri'i bus //
NK129(to)003:1860: gdags pa'i bstan bcos mo 'gal bus //
NK129(to)003:1861: khams kyi tshogs ni gang po ste //
NK129(to)003:1862: rnam par shes pa lha skyabs kyis //
NK129(to)003:1863: grol ba'i rnam grangs gsus po ches //
NK129(to)003:1864: ye shes 'jug pa ka ta yas //
NK129(to)003:1866: gzhan yang phung po lnga'i rab tu 'byed pa /
NK129(to)003:1867: nyi shu pa'i rab tu 'byed pa /
NK129(to)003:1868: sum cu pa'i rab tu 'byed pa /
NK129(to)003:1869: las rnams bsgrub pa'i rig pa /
NK129(to)003:1870: rab tu rnam par 'byed pa'i rig pa lnga po 'di ni rang rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1871: sems tsam gyi phyogs su 'gro ba yin cing /
NK129(to)003:1875: rten 'brel chen mo'i 'grel pa dang gsum po 'di ni kun gyi gzhung 'grel du 'gro ba'o //
NK129(to)003:1879: mnyam nyid bye brag gi bstan bcos la sogs pa gzhan par pa'i 'grel par bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:1880: theg pa chen po dang mthun pa'i bstan bcos la /
NK129(to)003:1881: slob dpon 'phags pa'i dbu ma rig pa'i tshogs drug /
NK129(to)003:1883: +aar+ya d+he ba'i dbu ma bzhi brgya pa /
NK129(to)003:1884: slob dpon b+ha bya'i dbu ma snying po /
NK129(to)003:1885: mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho'i dbu ma rgyan /
NK129(to)003:1886: ka ma la shi la'i dbu ma snang ba /
NK129(to)003:1887: rta dbyangs kyis skyes rabs snyan ngag /
NK129(to)003:1888: phyogs glang gis rab byed brgya rtsa /
NK129(to)003:1890: dbang po sde'i rab byed gtan tshig /
NK129(to)003:1891: zhi ba lha'i spyod 'jug dang bsla btus /
NK129(to)003:1893: dbyig gnyen sku mched kyis sde lnga dang sdom gnyis /
NK129(to)003:1894: pha rol tu phyin pa seng ge bzang po'i 'grel pa /
NK129(to)003:1897: de dag la sogs pa bka' dang bstan bcos kyi 'grel pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:1898: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta slob dpon pad+ma /
NK129(to)003:1900: kha che dz+ny+aa na su tra /
NK129(to)003:1902: d+ha na sh+ri la sngon ma /
NK129(to)003:1905: de rnams kyi zhal snga nas /
NK129(to)003:1906: chos 'di 'dis bsgyur gyi lo ts+aa ba thams cad yi ge 'jigs pas /
NK129(to)003:1910: zhang ban de ye shes sde la sogs pa rnams kyis bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:1911: de yang sde snod gsum po'i chos 'di dag phal cher /
NK129(to)003:1913: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta mkhas pa dang mnyam pas /
NK129(to)003:1914: 'phral gyi phrin bsgyur ma mdzad par /
NK129(to)003:1915: rtsa ba'i zhu dag mdzad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1917: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK129(to)003:1920: 'di gsum gyis 'gyur gyi rtsa bdag mdzad /
NK129(to)003:1921: lo ts+aa ba chung ba gsum gyis rgyab brten mdzad pa lta bu yin no //
NK129(to)003:1925: zhang ban de ye shes sde dang gsum gyis pan+di ta rnams kyis 'phral bsgyur mdzad pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:1926: bka' bstan bcos rnams kyi gsham du yang lo ts+aa ba 'di rnams kyi ming bcug pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:1927: dus phyis bod kyi slob dpon kha cig gis bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:1928: lo ts+aa ba chung ba gsum gyi 'gyur rang du brtsi ste /
NK129(to)003:1929: cung ma dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:1930: b+ai ma la'i gser phreng las /
NK129(to)003:1931: lo ts+aa ba ni brgya rtsa brgyad rang rang 'gyur la /
NK129(to)003:1932: rngo thogs kyi che ba gsum gyis dpang po mdzad /
NK129(to)003:1933: 'bring po gsum gyis rgyab skyor te /
NK129(to)003:1934: chung ba gsum gyis mjug ma sbyar /
NK129(to)003:1936: rgyud la sogs shin tu 'gyur ba rtogs par dka'
NK129(to)003:1937: ba rnams su gong ma rnams kyi 'gyur byang yod
NK129(to)003:1938: la / gzhan ma rnams su lo ts+aa ba chung ba rnams gtso bor byas pa snang na'ang /
NK129(to)003:1939: gtso bo rnams ni gong ma rnams shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:1940: gnyis pa nang gsang sngags kyi 'gyur tshul mdo tsam
NK129(to)003:1941: bstan pa ni sngags kyi cher 'thun pa gzungs kyi
NK129(to)003:1942: skor la / za ma tog bkod pa che chung gi skor sum cu dang /
NK129(to)003:1943: tshig d+ha ma ni rtog bral lnga pa dang /
NK129(to)003:1944: gzungs brgya drug cu pa la sogs pa bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:1948: gsung a mo g+ha p+aa shi'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1949: thugs rig pa mchog gi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1950: mdor bsdus pa kri ya dpung bzang gi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1953: kri ya rtsa ba'i rgyud sde drug bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:1955: bye brag cho ga zhib mo'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1956: phyag na rdo rje'i rgyud la /
NK129(to)003:1957: sku'i rgyud gzungs ring bsam gtan /
NK129(to)003:1959: thugs kyi rgyud rig pa mchog /
NK129(to)003:1960: phyi ma legs grub kyi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1961: bshad rgyud dpung bzang chen po /
NK129(to)003:1962: rdo rje rnam 'joms kyi rgyud gsum /
NK129(to)003:1963: yan lag gsang ba dkyil 'khor gyi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1964: dbang bskur ba rtogs pa rgyal po'i rgyud rnams bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:1968: thugs 'jam dpal le'u drug gis rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1969: phyi ma 'jam dpal gsang ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1970: bshad pa'i rgyud rdo rje bkod pa las rgya mtsho'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1971: bskal pa 'gro drug gi rgyud rnams bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:1972: spyan ras gzigs kyi rgyud la /
NK129(to)003:1973: sku rig 'dzin sde snod kyi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1979: kri ya'i spyi rgyud bzhi la /
NK129(to)003:1980: gzi ldan sgrol ma 'bar ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:1984: de dag dang 'thun pa'i bstan bcos la /
NK129(to)003:1987: tsan+t+ra ko ma'i rigs gsum bsgrub pa /
NK129(to)003:1988: gos sngon can gyi sgrub thabs /
NK129(to)003:1989: rdo rje gtum po'i sgrub thabs /
NK129(to)003:1990: mtshan brjod kyi 'grel pa rin chen phreng ba dang bcas pa rnams bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:1992: rnal 'byor yo ga'i chos lnga la /
NK129(to)003:1993: rtsa rgyud ta tha sam kra /
NK129(to)003:1994: bshad rgyud rdo rje rtse mo /
NK129(to)003:1995: byin rlabs kyi rgyud ngan song sbyong ba /
NK129(to)003:1996: kha bskang ba dpal mchog dang po /
NK129(to)003:1998: khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba /
NK129(to)003:2000: kun 'dus pa sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang bcas pa rnams bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:2002: rtsa ba rnam snang mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2003: bshad rgyud nyi ma gzi brjid /
NK129(to)003:2005: rgyud phyi ma khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK129(to)003:2006: mtshan brjod le'u khri drug stong pa /
NK129(to)003:2008: phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2009: rnam par mi rtog pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2010: de rnams sgrub thabs 'grel pa dang bcas pa bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:2011: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud kyi skor la /
NK129(to)003:2013: sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK129(to)003:2014: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK129(to)003:2015: thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK129(to)003:2016: yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK129(to)003:2017: phrin las kyi rgyud pad phreng dkar po dang lnga'o //
NK129(to)003:2018: sgrubs pa lag len gyi rgyud la /
NK129(to)003:2019: sku'i rgyud la he ru ka gal po /
NK129(to)003:2020: gsung gi rgyud rta mchog rol pa /
NK129(to)003:2021: thugs kyi rgyud he ru ka gal po /
NK129(to)003:2022: yon tan gyi rgyud bdud rtsi rol pa bam po brgyad /
NK129(to)003:2023: phrin las kyi rgyud byi to ta ma la /
NK129(to)003:2024: ki la ya bcu gnyis kyi rgyud dang lnga'o //
NK129(to)003:2026: gzhi dam tshig gi gzung ba /
NK129(to)003:2027: dam tshig bkod pa rgyal po'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2030: phu thag lta bas bcad pa /
NK129(to)003:2032: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs pa /
NK129(to)003:2035: rngam pa glog gi rgyud dang lnga'o //
NK129(to)003:2037: dngos grub 'byung ba'i cho ga thabs kyi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2038: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+ma phreng ba dkyil 'khor thams cad la 'jug pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2041: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba stong phrag brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK129(to)003:2042: de dag thams cad bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba yang /
NK129(to)003:2044: ka cog rnam gnyis dang gsum mo //
NK129(to)003:2045: de dag gi rjes su 'gro ba'i bstan bcos la /
NK129(to)003:2046: rta dbyangs kyi bla ma lnga bcu pa /
NK129(to)003:2051: sgrub thabs dang bcas pa bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:2053: ye shes phyag rgya rol pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:2058: rdo rje ma kol pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:2060: de dag ni rtsa ba'i mdo bdun /
NK129(to)003:2061: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:2065: dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:2066: he ru ka gal po'i mdo /
NK129(to)003:2067: 'jig rten 'das pa'i mdo ste lung gi mdo bdun no //
NK129(to)003:2068: sku'i rgyud bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba /
NK129(to)003:2071: yon tan lha mo ma gos pa /
NK129(to)003:2072: phrin las ma ti drug gi rgyud rnams bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:2073: a ti yo ga'i skor la /
NK129(to)003:2074: spyi rgyud stong gis brgyan pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2075: ma mo srid pa'i bam chen mo /
NK129(to)003:2077: khro bo ya man+ta ka'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2079: spyi rgyud dang sna tshogs rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2083: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2084: ma rgyud thabs kyi zhags pa /
NK129(to)003:2093: b+aee ro tsa na'i snga 'gyur lnga /
NK129(to)003:2094: b+ai ma la yi phyi 'gyur bcu gsum /
NK129(to)003:2095: kha 'thor gyi rgyud brgya dang brgyad do //
NK129(to)003:2096: khyad par 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i skor la /
NK129(to)003:2097: snying po'i gsang rgyud bcu bdun /
NK129(to)003:2098: klong gsal 'bar ma nyi ma'i rgyud la che 'bring chung gsum /
NK129(to)003:2099: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgyud la rgyud sde lnga /
NK129(to)003:2100: bde gshegs sgrub pa bka' brgyad kyi rgyud la /
NK129(to)003:2101: bde gshegs 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2102: zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2104: che mchog 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2105: gshin rje 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2106: dbang chen 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2107: phur ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2108: ma mo 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2110: dregs pa 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2111: drag sngags 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2112: ma tshang ba kha bskangs pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2113: 'byed par byed pa lde mig rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2114: phyi ma nges par 'byung ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2115: phyi ma'i phyi ma sngags kyi rgyud rnams bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:2116: gzhan yang bka' brgyad bye brag dum bu'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2119: rta 'grin la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK129(to)003:2120: gzhan yang las tshogs kha bskang ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2121: srid pa lha rgyud dang 'dre rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2124: srid pa spyi blugs kyi rgyud che 'bring chung gsum /
NK129(to)003:2125: dregs pa'i sde dpon sum cu la sgos rgyud re /
NK129(to)003:2126: dregs pa sde brgyad la spyi rgyud re re /
NK129(to)003:2127: pho mo dang klu gsum la sgos rgyud re re /
NK129(to)003:2128: thams cad 'dus pa ma ning dregs pa'i spyi rgyud
NK129(to)003:2129: ma ning dregs pa'i srog rgyud nag po la sogs
NK129(to)003:2130: te / re re nas ni brir ga la lang ste /
NK129(to)003:2131: mdor na dpag tu med pa cig dus der 'gyur te /
NK129(to)003:2132: chos 'khor sprul pa'i rgyal blon mnga' thang rgyas /
NK129(to)003:2133: gru thob pan+di ta rnams sprin ltar gtibs /
NK129(to)003:2134: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba rnams glog ltar 'khyug /
NK129(to)003:2135: mnga' thang grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su 'gyur ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2136: dus phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba rang che 'byin pa rnams dang mi 'dra ste /
NK129(to)003:2138: sprul pa'i sbyin bdag rgyal blon rnams la gzigs /
NK129(to)003:2139: rgya gar gyi grub thob pan+di ta rnams la gzigs /
NK129(to)003:2140: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba rnams la gzigs /
NK129(to)003:2141: bod kyi gang zag mkhas shing blo gzu bor gnas pa rnams kyis legs par brtags 'tshal lo //
NK129(to)003:2142: gzhan yang gsar rnying gnyis kyis mtshams dang /
NK129(to)003:2143: gong gi lo rgyus de dag shes che ba ni /
NK129(to)003:2144: khams pa yang me seng+ge zhes grags pa de'i mdo
NK129(to)003:2145: khams smad kyi chos 'byung dang smri ti dz+ny+aa na
NK129(to)003:2146: g+hirti la / rgya gar gyi dri ba the tshom
NK129(to)003:2147: bcad pa'i lo rgyus chen mo las ji ltar brjod
NK129(to)003:2149: 'di dag ni rnying ma las ji ltar grags pa'i 'gyur tshul bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2150: gnyis pa gsar mar ji ltar grags pa'i 'gyur dang lo rgyus ni /
NK129(to)003:2151: bod kyi slob dpon gzhan gyis byas pa'i chos 'byung na mang du yod cing /
NK129(to)003:2152: 'dir yi ge 'jigs pas ma spros la /
NK129(to)003:2153: lo rgyus rnam gzhag mdo tsam zhig ni bshad par bya ste /
NK129(to)003:2155: lnga drug la sogs pa yod na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2156: don ni rgyud sde chen po bzhi ru bsdu ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2160: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)003:2161: de dag gi gtan tshig ni /
NK129(to)003:2163: go rims nges par bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2166: dang po grangs rkyang pa la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)003:2167: dus bzhi la dgongs te rgyud sde bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)003:2168: dpal phreng dam pa'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:2169: gsang sngags 'byung tshul rnam bzhi ste /
NK129(to)003:2170: bskal pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan gnyis /
NK129(to)003:2171: rtsod dus rgyud dang rim bzhin du /
NK129(to)003:2172: gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba yin /
NK129(to)003:2173: gnyis pa skye gnas bzhi la dgongs te /
NK129(to)003:2176: sgong skyes mngal las skyes pa'am //
NK129(to)003:2177: drod skyes la sogs bardzusa skyes sam //
NK129(to)003:2178: de phyir rgyud ni bzhi ru nges //
NK129(to)003:2180: gsum pa mi rigs bzhi la dgongs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2181: rdo rje sa 'og gi rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:2182: rgyal rigs rje'u rigs bram ze dang //
NK129(to)003:2183: rmongs rigs gdol pa 'dul don du //
NK129(to)003:2184: rgyud sde so sor bstan pa yin //
NK129(to)003:2186: bzhi pa 'dod khams kyi lha'i chags spyod la brten nas kyang bzhir bstan /
NK129(to)003:2188: gnyis gnyis 'khyud dang lag bcangs dang /
NK129(to)003:2190: srin bu yis ni tshul gyis su //
NK129(to)003:2191: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhi ru gsungs //
NK129(to)003:2193: gnyis pa go rims nges pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2194: sems can gyi dbang po'i rim pa dang bstun nas kyang rgyud bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)003:2196: sems can rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK129(to)003:2197: de lhag rnams la spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK129(to)003:2198: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK129(to)003:2199: de lhag rnams la bla med rgyud //
NK129(to)003:2201: rgyud sde bzhi po de dag gi chos kyi rnam grangs kyi tshad ni /
NK129(to)003:2202: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa las /
NK129(to)003:2203: rtogs pa'i rgyud ni stong phrag bzhi /
NK129(to)003:2204: bya ba'i rgyud ni stong phrag bzhi /
NK129(to)003:2205: spyod pa'i rgyud ni stong phrag brgyad //
NK129(to)003:2206: gnyis ka'i rgyud ni stong phrag drug /
NK129(to)003:2207: rnal 'byor stong phrag bcu gnyis so //
NK129(to)003:2208: rgyas par bshad na tshad med do //
NK129(to)003:2209: zhes lngar phyes nas tshad du byas so //
NK129(to)003:2210: de dag las bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor gsum gyis ngos bzung nas /
NK129(to)003:2212: bka' rnying 'gyur dus phyis kyi phyi thub pa'i rgyud sde gsum dang mthun te /
NK129(to)003:2213: rnying ma la ma ltos pa'i rgyud med do //
NK129(to)003:2214: rgyud gsar rnying du 'byed pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2215: gsar rnying gnyis ka bla na med pa'i rgyud las phye ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:2216: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud la gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:2219: gnyis su med pa snying po'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)003:2220: pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis kyi khyad par yang gdul bya'i khyad par te /
NK129(to)003:2222: skyes pa rnams ni 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)003:2223: rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud du bshad //
NK129(to)003:2224: bud med rnams ni 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)003:2225: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud du bshad //
NK129(to)003:2227: yang rdzogs rim gyi gnas skabs su /
NK129(to)003:2228: rtsa gtso bor ston pa ma rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2229: rlung gtso bor ston pa pha rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2231: gnas de rnams su dpa' bo ni //
NK129(to)003:2232: rlung gis khams dang yang dag ldan //
NK129(to)003:2234: yang bskyed rim gyi skabs su /
NK129(to)003:2235: lha pho shas che ba pha rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2236: mo shas che ba ni ma rgyud do //
NK129(to)003:2237: gnyis su med pa snying po don gyi rgyud ni /
NK129(to)003:2238: thabs shes cha snyoms pas kun las khyad par bton pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:2240: gnyis su med dang gnyis med ston //
NK129(to)003:2242: de la rgyud sde ngos bzung na /
NK129(to)003:2249: ma h+aa ma ya la sogs pa'i skor rnams so //
NK129(to)003:2250: gnyis su med pa snying po don gyi rgyud rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:2251: rtsa ba'i rgyud rab tu mi gnas pa /
NK129(to)003:2252: bshad pa'i rgyud bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK129(to)003:2253: gnyis ka'i rgyud rnyogs pa med pa /
NK129(to)003:2254: rgyab rten gyi rgyud he ru bzang po /
NK129(to)003:2255: phan par byed pa'i rgyud ye shes snying po /
NK129(to)003:2256: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i rgyud 'jam dpal sgyu
NK129(to)003:2257: 'phrul dra ba khri drug stong la sogs pa ste
NK129(to)003:2258: / de dag ni rgyud spyi'i rnam grangs mdo tsam bstan pa yin /
NK129(to)003:2259: rgyud sde re re la'ang 'dod pa'i bye brag tu phye na /
NK129(to)003:2260: rgyud rgyas pa la yan lag bdun ldan du 'dod
NK129(to)003:2261: pa dang rtsa rgyud bshad rgyud gnyis su 'dod pa'i
NK129(to)003:2262: lugs so // yan lag bdun ldan ni /
NK129(to)003:2267: ma tshang ba kha bskang ba /
NK129(to)003:2268: bka' ma yongs su spyod pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2269: bskal pa dum bu'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)003:2270: de dag gi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)003:2271: thog mar ston pas gsungs pa /
NK129(to)003:2272: bskyed pa ma lta bu'i tshul ni rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2273: de'i rjes la gyes pa yal ga lta bu ni bshad pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2274: rtsa rgyud mngon du phyung ba phyi ma'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2275: phyi ma rnams mi gsal ba gsal bar byas pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2277: rtsa bshad gnyis su ma tshang ba logs su gsungs pa kha bskangs ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2278: rtsa ba'i bka' logs su bkrol ba yongs su spyod pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:2279: rtsa bshad nas gal che ba logs su bkrol ba bkol ba dum bu'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)003:2280: rtsa rgyud la mtshan nyid drug ste /
NK129(to)003:2285: rgyud kyi ldang tshad bshad pa /
NK129(to)003:2286: mthu drug gi don bsdu tshul bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2287: bshad rgyud la tshul drug ste /
NK129(to)003:2288: mi gsal ba gsal bar byed pa /
NK129(to)003:2289: ma tshang ba kha bskang ba /
NK129(to)003:2290: tshul mi 'dra ba so sor ston pa /
NK129(to)003:2292: mi mthun pa gzhi don cig tu ston pa /
NK129(to)003:2293: tshig dang don rnam par phye ste cig tu ston pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2294: spyir na rgyud ces bya ba la ldang tshad ni /
NK129(to)003:2295: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu tshang bar ston pa'am /
NK129(to)003:2297: gdams gtad dang bcas pa ston pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2298: de rnams tshang na rgyud yongs su rdzogs par bzhed do //
NK129(to)003:2299: de rnams ma tshang na rgyud 'thor ba zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)003:2300: de ltar du rnam bzhag mdo tsam bstan nas /
NK129(to)003:2301: dus phyis kyi 'gyur gsar mar grags pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:2302: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta dang /
NK129(to)003:2303: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis 'gyur rnams ni /
NK129(to)003:2304: pan+di ta smri ti snga shos yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2305: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang po /
NK129(to)003:2310: zhang lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis mgos byas /
NK129(to)003:2311: rngog shes rab blo ldan yar bcad do //
NK129(to)003:2312: phal cher bsgyur ba yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2313: de yang lo ts+aa ba gong ma rnams kyis gtso bor bsgyur ba las /
NK129(to)003:2314: bod so so skye bo'i blo can rnams la /
NK129(to)003:2315: 'gyur bzang ngan du grags pa'i chos dang /
NK129(to)003:2317: rang phyogs kyi 'dod pas bcos pa kho na yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2318: rgyud gzhung chen po'i 'gyur rnams las bcos byas pa las /
NK129(to)003:2319: dus phyis lo ts+aa ba rgya bal du rgya tshong pa ltar mang du rgyug pa byung ste /
NK129(to)003:2320: phyis rang gzhung tshugs pa'i rgyud cher 'gyur ba ni med /
NK129(to)003:2322: gzungs dang lha'i sgrub thabs la sogs pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:2323: dag ma dag gang yang rung ba mang po zhig 'gyur tshul 'dug go //
NK129(to)003:2324: de dag ni gsar ma'i chos 'byung 'ga' zhig tu bstan 'dug pas /
NK129(to)003:2325: 'dir re re bzhin gyi 'gyur byang ni yi ges 'jigs te brir ma lang ngo //
NK129(to)003:2326: de dag gis ni gtso bor gsar ma'i 'gyur tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:2327: bye brag tu gsar rnying gnyis kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK129(to)003:2328: 'gyur tshul mdor bstan pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2329: gsum pa gsar rnying du grags pa'i rgyud 'dzin /
NK129(to)003:2331: rgya gar na gsar rnying med /
NK129(to)003:2332: bod du grags pa yin zer yang /
NK129(to)003:2333: rgya gar du bstan pa'i bab tshul gyi gsar rnying dang /
NK129(to)003:2334: bod du 'gyur snga phyis gsar rnying du grags pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2335: rgya gar na bka' rgyud bab tshul gyi rim pa gong du yang bstan pa yin la /
NK129(to)003:2336: de'ang rgya gar na bstan pa'i babs tshul rnying ma
NK129(to)003:2337: la khyad par du 'phags pa ci yod ce na
NK129(to)003:2338: / bskal pa la grangs su bcad pa'i bstan pa bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:2339: de dag mthun pa'i gnas bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:2340: bstan pa'i bdag po ston pa bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:2341: de dag gi gsungs pa bstan pa'i chos bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)003:2342: 'di dag rim gyi bab so dang bcas nas 'byung ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2343: de dag gis babs so mdo tsam bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2344: de yang skye dgu rnams kyi tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:2345: bskal pa dang po dga' ldan brtsegs pa zhes bya bar /
NK129(to)003:2346: gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min lha'i gnas su
NK129(to)003:2347: me tog pad+ma'i sdong po 'dab ma stong dang ldan
NK129(to)003:2348: pa la / ston pa rdo rje 'chang nyid byis
NK129(to)003:2349: pa gzhon nu'i gzugs su 'khrungs pa'i tshul bstan pa'i
NK129(to)003:2350: g.yas g.yon du lha'i bu nyi ma rab tu snang
NK129(to)003:2351: pa la / byed dang / zla ba dri ma med pa gnyis bardzusa te skyes shing /
NK129(to)003:2352: 'dab ma stong la bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas
NK129(to)003:2353: stong khye'u gzhon nu sprul sku'i cha byad du sprul
NK129(to)003:2355: bskal pa bzang po 'di la sangs stong gis 'dul ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2356: de yang bstan pa 'di la longs sku'i bstan pas
NK129(to)003:2357: gdul bya yang rab rnams 'dul ba la dgongs nas
NK129(to)003:2358: / seng ge drang srong glang po gsum gyi bzhugs stangs gsum dang /
NK129(to)003:2359: sku gsum gyi gzigs stangs gsum gyis chos phun sum
NK129(to)003:2360: tshogs pa sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud la sogs
NK129(to)003:2361: pa mngon sum du snying tig gi bstan pa rnams
NK129(to)003:2362: dus phun sum tshogs pa bskal pa 'di'i thog ma
NK129(to)003:2363: la gsungs so // de nas skye dgu rnams kyi tshe lo bye ba thub pa na /
NK129(to)003:2364: thams cad 'byung bzhi 'dus pa 'od kyi sgo nga las skyes pa sha stag ste /
NK129(to)003:2365: de'i tshe gnas phun sum tshogs pa mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams 'od gsal lha'i khang par /
NK129(to)003:2366: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rdo rje 'chang chen
NK129(to)003:2367: po 'od lnga 'dus pa'i sgo nga las gzhon nu
NK129(to)003:2368: lo bcu drug gi tshod tsam du /
NK129(to)003:2369: khye'u 'od mi 'khrugs pa zhes bya bar byon te /
NK129(to)003:2370: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa yid snyung rdo rje ma la sogs pa la /
NK129(to)003:2371: chos phun sum tshogs pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud lnga /
NK129(to)003:2372: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo bye ba thub pa'i dus gsungs po //
NK129(to)003:2373: de nas tshe lo 'bum thub pa'i dus na /
NK129(to)003:2374: gnas phun sum tshogs pa drod gsher 'dus pa 'od kyi phung po spungs pa zhes bya bar /
NK129(to)003:2375: ston pa rdo rje 'chang nyid dpal 'jigs pa skyob pa zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2376: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' 'bum phrag drug la chos phun sum tshogs pa 'khor ba dong sprugs dang /
NK129(to)003:2378: dpal 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud rnams /
NK129(to)003:2379: dus phun sum tshogs pa'i tshe lo 'bum pa'i dus na gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2380: de nas tshe lo brgyad khri pa'i dus na /
NK129(to)003:2381: gnas chags 'byung mngal du snang bar /
NK129(to)003:2382: ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen po brtse bas rnam par rol pa zhes bya bas /
NK129(to)003:2383: 'khor gnod sbyin dang brag srin stong phrag cig la /
NK129(to)003:2384: chos phun sum tshogs pa sems sde rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga /
NK129(to)003:2385: yang dag gi rgyud drug ste bcu gcig /
NK129(to)003:2386: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo brgyad khri pa'i dus na gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2387: de nas tshe lo bdun khri pa'i dus na /
NK129(to)003:2388: gnas phun sum tshogs pa sum cu rtsa gsum du /
NK129(to)003:2389: ston pa rdo rje 'chang nyid spyir 'gro ba rigs drug na /
NK129(to)003:2390: thub pa drug gsang ba pha rol tu phyin pa drug la gzigs te /
NK129(to)003:2391: drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen por sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2392: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa nyid kyi rnam par rol pa las byung ba sangs rgyas rab bdun dang /
NK129(to)003:2394: chos phun sum tshogs pa gdung ba sel ba'i chos drug la /
NK129(to)003:2395: lung sbrags ma bac+wa brgyad dang /
NK129(to)003:2396: phyag na rdo rjes me lce phreng ba'i rgyud le'u dgu pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2397: spyan ras gzigs seng ge sgra'i rgyud le'u dgu pa /
NK129(to)003:2398: 'jam dpal ye shes rgyan gyi le'u bdun pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2400: ye shes kun tu gsal ba'i rgyud le'u bcu bdun pa la sogs pa /
NK129(to)003:2401: rdzogs pa chen po bya ba dang bral ba'i rgyud rnams /
NK129(to)003:2402: dus tshe lo bdun khri pa'i dus su gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2403: de nas tshe lo drug khri pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:2404: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ri rab kyi byang shar dur khrod me ri 'bar ba zhes bya bar /
NK129(to)003:2405: ston pa rdo rje 'chang gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2406: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa gong gi thub pa drug /
NK129(to)003:2407: gnod sbyin gyi bu legs spyod dang bdun la /
NK129(to)003:2408: chos phun sum tshogs pa pha rgyud bye ba dgu /
NK129(to)003:2410: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud rigs pa rang shar le'u
NK129(to)003:2411: brgyad cu rtsa drug pa la sogs pa 'bum phrag
NK129(to)003:2413: dus tshe lo drug khri pa'i dus su gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2414: de nas 'dzam bu gling gi nub phyogs rgya mtsho'i gling zhes bya ba'i gnas su /
NK129(to)003:2415: ston pa rdo rje 'chang drang srong khros pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2416: 'khor srin po bye ba cig la /
NK129(to)003:2417: chos rig pa 'dus pa'i rgyud bcu la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:2418: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo nyi khri pa'i
NK129(to)003:2420: de nas gnas phun sum tshogs pa bya rgod phung por /
NK129(to)003:2421: ston pa rdo rje 'chang gser 'od dam par sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2422: 'khor nyan thos rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa dpag tu med pa la /
NK129(to)003:2423: chos phun sum tshogs pa 'dul ba khri phrag cig /
NK129(to)003:2424: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo lnga stong pa'i dus su gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2425: de nas gnas phun sum tshogs pa sog po g.yu yi smin ma can gyi yul du /
NK129(to)003:2426: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo stong gi tshe /
NK129(to)003:2427: ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen po brtse bas rnam
NK129(to)003:2428: par rol pa'i blo gros zhes bya bar sprul nas
NK129(to)003:2429: / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' mang po la /
NK129(to)003:2430: chos phun sum tshogs pa phra rgyud bdun pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2431: de nas gnas phun sum tshogs pa bya rgod phung po'i ri la /
NK129(to)003:2432: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo lnga brgya pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:2433: ston pa rdo rje 'chang 'od srungs bgres po zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2434: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa sh+aa ri'i bu skar ma
NK129(to)003:2435: 'od bzang po la sogs pa dgra bcom pa bdun
NK129(to)003:2436: dang / byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba la /
NK129(to)003:2437: chos phun sum tshogs pa mdo sde dang /
NK129(to)003:2438: kri ya dang a nu la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2439: de nas gnas phun sum tshogs pa rdo rje gdan byang chub kyi shing drung du /
NK129(to)003:2440: dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo sum brgya pa'i dus kyi tshe /
NK129(to)003:2441: ston pa rdo rje 'chang mngon rdzogs rgyal po zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK129(to)003:2442: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rig gsum mgon po la /
NK129(to)003:2443: chos phun sum tshogs pa snying po nges pa'i don gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2444: de nas dus phun sum tshogs pa tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na /
NK129(to)003:2445: gnas phun sum tshogs pa w+aa r+aa na s+ai dang /
NK129(to)003:2448: ston pa rdo rje 'chang nyid lha dang mi rnams
NK129(to)003:2449: kyi ston pa dpal rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa nyid
NK129(to)003:2450: du sprul nas / mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i tshul gyis /
NK129(to)003:2451: 'khor nyan thos dang byang chub sems dpa' lha dang klu la sogs pa la /
NK129(to)003:2452: chos phun sum tshogs pa theg pa gsum gyi chos
NK129(to)003:2453: kyi 'khor lo gdul bya'i rim pa dang sbyar nas
NK129(to)003:2454: gsungs so // de ltar ston pa bcu gnyis po de dag kyang /
NK129(to)003:2456: gdul byed kyi 'khor babs la brten nas thog ma'i ston pa kun tu bzang po /
NK129(to)003:2457: gdod ma'i rgyab pa de nyid mtshan rdzogs rdo rje 'chang gi tshul du byon pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2458: de la bskal pa dang 'tsham pa'i gdul bya 'dul byed gnyan po la dgongs te /
NK129(to)003:2459: ston pa'i 'khrungs tshul zhi khro cha lugs mi 'dra ba du mar sprul te /
NK129(to)003:2460: gong ltar bka'i 'khor lo rnams rim par gsungs pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2461: bstan pa 'di nyid kyi dbang du ston pa thub pa'i dbang po 'di nyid /
NK129(to)003:2462: phyi ltar na sh+aakya thub pa /
NK129(to)003:2463: nang ltar kun rig rnam par snang mdzad /
NK129(to)003:2465: yang gsang ltar na rang bzhin gdod ma'i rgyal ba
NK129(to)003:2466: kun tu bzang po zhes don la mtshan du gsol
NK129(to)003:2467: ba yin te / de'i gsungs pa'i rgyud sde rnams kyang /
NK129(to)003:2468: spyir ni 'og min la sogs pa dag pa'i gnas dang /
NK129(to)003:2471: sde rgyad la sogs pa du mar gsung na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2472: khyad par rdzogs pa chen po la /
NK129(to)003:2473: rgyud sde 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi yod pa rnams dang /
NK129(to)003:2474: spyir yang rnying ma'i chos kyi babs so thams cad
NK129(to)003:2475: phal cher nub o rgyan gyi yul du byung ba
NK129(to)003:2476: yin te / bod du rgyal blon mnga' thang dar ba'i dus tshun chod kyi lo ts+aa ba ni /
NK129(to)003:2477: dus phyis nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul du rtol ba med /
NK129(to)003:2478: rtol kyang so so skye bo'i lo ts+aa bas mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod /
NK129(to)003:2479: rang byung gi mchod rten rnams 'byed par mi nus /
NK129(to)003:2480: gong du bstan pa ltar rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK129(to)003:2481: ston pas gsungs pa'i chos theg pa rim pa dgur 'dus pa las /
NK129(to)003:2482: de thams cad kyi yang rtse dbang po yang rab kyi chos yin te /
NK129(to)003:2483: kun gyi thun mong ma yin pa /
NK129(to)003:2484: rgya gar gyi brgyud pa rnams kyang 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i skor /
NK129(to)003:2485: dbang gi chu klung bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbang gi tshig rgyud du byon pa bdun nas /
NK129(to)003:2487: b+ai ma la gnyis kyis bod du lhag ma ma lus par gdan drangs pas /
NK129(to)003:2488: rgya gar du dus phyis khungs med pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2491: bka' brgyad bye brag so so la sogs pa rnams ni rgya gar gyi rig 'dzin brgyad dang /
NK129(to)003:2492: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba rnams kyis rim par bsgyur ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2493: rgyud 'ga' re ni da dung yang /
NK129(to)003:2494: o rgyan rang byung gi gtsug lag khang du bzhugs par bshad do //
NK129(to)003:2495: de la gong gi chu klung bzhi'i babs so gang yin na /
NK129(to)003:2496: bla ma brgyud pa las byung ba'i byin rlabs bka' bab kyi dbang lung /
NK129(to)003:2497: yi dam lha'i gnang ba thob pa dbang lung gi babs so //
NK129(to)003:2498: mkhas pa pan+di ta'i dbang lung las byung ba rang grol gyi dbang lung /
NK129(to)003:2499: bka' po ti glegs bam gyi dbang theg pa'i babs so //
NK129(to)003:2500: rig pa ye shes kyi rtsal dbang thob pa 'khor 'das la dbang bsgyur ba /
NK129(to)003:2501: gong gi bla ma brgyud pa de rnams la yod pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2502: khyad par du dbang bzhi'i chu klung yongs su rdzogs par babs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2503: rgya gar na yang gu ru pad ma 'byung gnas tsam las med ces grags so //
NK129(to)003:2504: des na 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i yang rtse 'di ni /
NK129(to)003:2505: rgya bod kun tu dkon cing /
NK129(to)003:2506: blo chung mos par yang dka' ste /
NK129(to)003:2507: b+ai ma la'i gser phreng las /
NK129(to)003:2508: bla med theg pa'i yang rtse 'di ni /
NK129(to)003:2509: skal ldan gyis skyes bu bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol nas tshogs gnyis bsags pa /
NK129(to)003:2510: sangs rgyas mang po la bsnyen cing bkur ba /
NK129(to)003:2511: las kyi sgrib pa mthar zad pa /
NK129(to)003:2512: srid pa tha ma'i byang chub sems dpa' 'ga' dang 'ag'i spyod yul yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2513: gang rung rung gi spyod yul ni ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:2517: yul dus sa dang lam la ltos pa'i gang zag rnams dang ni phrad par mi 'gyur /
NK129(to)003:2520: chos 'di ni rgya gar na yang dkon pa'i gnas su gyur pa ste /
NK129(to)003:2521: gang rung rung gi spyod yul ni ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:2522: zhes pa don go sla ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:2523: des da rgya gar na yang chos kyi ngo bo la gsar rnying med kyang /
NK129(to)003:2524: bka' rgyud babs so'i gsar rnying gi gu ru dang b+ai ma la phan gyi dga' rab rdo rje /
NK129(to)003:2527: dz+ny+aa na su tra dang bcas pa 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:2537: go ma de byi dang bcas pa 'di rnams phan chad ni /
NK129(to)003:2538: rnying ma'i bka' rgyud babs so //
NK129(to)003:2539: yang rgya gar gyi ske tshang gsum na bzhugs pa'i
NK129(to)003:2540: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa cig tu gsal ba'i b+aee
NK129(to)003:2541: ro tsa na'i bla mar grags pa 'di rnams thams
NK129(to)003:2542: cad ni / dus snga bas rgya gar du yang rnying ma'i bka' rgyud kyi babs so //
NK129(to)003:2543: 'di dag la brgyud pa'i chos rnams bod du 'gyur ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2544: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan /
NK129(to)003:2545: bstan pa snga dar ba'i dus su lo ts+aa ba che gsum /
NK129(to)003:2548: mkhas par grags pa bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi /
NK129(to)003:2549: yongs grags kyi lo ts+aa ba brgya rtsa brgyad la
NK129(to)003:2550: sogs pa rnams kyis rgya gar mkhas pa'i yul du
NK129(to)003:2551: lhag ma ma lus par bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)003:2552: ces pa ni rgyal po'i bka' chems rtsis kyi yi
NK129(to)003:2553: ge chen mo rnams las ji ltar byung ba yin
NK129(to)003:2554: te / 'di rnams ni rgyal blon snga dar ba'i
NK129(to)003:2555: dus kyi 'gyur tshul te rnying ma'i 'gyur zhes bya'o
NK129(to)003:2556: te / // de yang mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan la sras gsum yod pa la /
NK129(to)003:2557: che ba mu ne btsad po /
NK129(to)003:2559: chung ba mu rub btsad po dang gsum las /
NK129(to)003:2560: che ba mu ne btsad pos yum dang blon po'i phyogs la brten nas dug gis bgrongs /
NK129(to)003:2561: mu rug btsan po la 'dod lugs gsum du gleng /
NK129(to)003:2562: phag tu blon pos bgrongs pa /
NK129(to)003:2563: mthar spyugs par yang bzhed de /
NK129(to)003:2564: chibs kyis brdabs nas gshegs zer ba'ang yod /
NK129(to)003:2566: gang ltar na'ang lha lung dpal gyi rdo rje skye ba 'phos pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2569: de la mes ag tshom yang zer /
NK129(to)003:2573: khri gtsang ma dang gsum byung ba las /
NK129(to)003:2574: mnga' bdag khri ral pa can gyi ring la /
NK129(to)003:2575: 'od 'jangs rdo'i gtsug lag khang la bya 'dab dgu brtsegs su yod pa bzhengs /
NK129(to)003:2577: mkhas pa dzi na mi tra phyi ma /
NK129(to)003:2582: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i slob ma kha che rad na mi tra la sogs pa /
NK129(to)003:2583: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta mkhas pa lnga bcu rtsa lnga gdan drangs /
NK129(to)003:2584: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba mnga' bdag khri srong gi
NK129(to)003:2585: dus kyi lo ts+aa 'ga' zhig bzhugs pa yin te
NK129(to)003:2587: o rgyan chen po'i dngos slob tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes pas /
NK129(to)003:2588: dgung lo gnyis bargya'am phyed dang gnyis brgya tsam shas che ba bzhugs pa yin /
NK129(to)003:2590: glang dar mas bstan pa bsnubs pa'i dus na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2591: gu ru'i dngos slob gnubs nam mkha'i snying po /
NK129(to)003:2592: btsun pa rgyal ba mchog dbyangs /
NK129(to)003:2595: lha lung dpal gyi rdo rje /
NK129(to)003:2597: la sum rgyal ba byang chub /
NK129(to)003:2598: lo ts+aa ba ka cog rnam gnyis la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:2599: 'di rnams la gsod pa'i mi thung ba btang pas
NK129(to)003:2600: / rdzu 'phrul gyis nam mkha' la byon te /
NK129(to)003:2602: h'u dang ru lu'i sgra sgrogs pa /
NK129(to)003:2603: glang dar ma bcom nas bsdus pa la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:2604: mdzad pa'i bar du rtsod pa ma nus pa'i gtam
NK129(to)003:2605: rgyud ni / bod kyi slob dpon rnams kyis mdzad
NK129(to)003:2606: pa'i chos 'byung mang por bltas pas shes par bya'o
NK129(to)003:2607: rgyud ni / // yang rnying ma rang gi chos kyi 'gyur lugs na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2608: rma rin chen mchog 'das nas med zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:2609: shud pu dpal gyi seng ge rgya bod kyi mtshams
NK129(to)003:2610: su klu bdud kyis bar du bcad zer ba'ang 'dug
NK129(to)003:2611: ste / kho bo'i 'dod kyi de kun yang mi dag ste /
NK129(to)003:2612: mchims phu dang dbu rtse rim gsum du /
NK129(to)003:2613: o rgyan chen pos rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga la /
NK129(to)003:2614: bde gshegs 'dus pa gsang ba yongs rdzogs rdo rje
NK129(to)003:2615: dbyings la sogs pa'i dbang chen mo rnams bskur ba'i
NK129(to)003:2616: dus na'ang / 'di rnams gtso bor bzhugs pa las /
NK129(to)003:2617: bar chad du ma song ste shin+tu bzhugs pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2618: de ltar mnga' bdag khri ral pa can gyis yab
NK129(to)003:2619: mes kyi ring la bsgyur ba'i chos rnams dag par
NK129(to)003:2620: bya ba dang / ma dag pa zhu dag byas pa'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:2621: dus phyis bod blo mang gis 'gyur la bcos mi bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK129(to)003:2622: rgya bod kyi lo pan rnams gung mnyam par 'dzom pa yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:2623: sprul pa'i rgyal po nyid kyi bka' btsan par gtan la phab pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:2624: skad gsar bcad kyis bcom nas gtan la phab pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2625: ces bka'i rtsis chen mo las 'dir phab pa'o //
NK129(to)003:2626: gzhan yang lha mo dri ma med pa'i mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:2627: gdong char can lung bstan pa'i mdo dang /
NK129(to)003:2628: bram ze gzungs kyis snye ma /
NK129(to)003:2631: kri ya'i sgrub thabs mang po zhig kyang 'di'i dus su bsgyur te /
NK129(to)003:2632: rgyal po 'di ni gsang ba'i bdag po'i sprul pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:2633: sku tshe la bar chad du 'gyur kyang thug dgongs mthar rdzogs par bzhed do //
NK129(to)003:2635: phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa min /
NK129(to)003:2636: de yin na cung po glang dar mas bar chad brtsam par mi rig zer na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2637: de yang dus la ma bab pa'i bar chad ni ma nges te /
NK129(to)003:2638: ston pa zhal bzhugs pa'i dus na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2639: lha sbyin gyis kyang bar chad mang po brtsam par yin cing /
NK129(to)003:2640: log pa'i bdud kyis smon lam log par btab na /
NK129(to)003:2642: glang dar ma yang log pa'i smon lam gyis nus pa byung ba'o //
NK129(to)003:2643: rgyal po de nyid phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa yin par yid ches pa'i lo rgyus ni /
NK129(to)003:2644: rgyal pos khrims bar pa bcas pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:2645: rgya gru gu'i yul la dmag mdzad nas /
NK129(to)003:2646: lho phyogs kyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po la spreng yig mdzad nas /
NK129(to)003:2647: nga ni dmag rog la shog cig gsungs pa la /
NK129(to)003:2648: rgya nag po'i byang phyogs smin ma can gyi yul du rgyal po'i dmag sleb pa'i dus /
NK129(to)003:2649: lung pa de thams cad mi'i lus la byi la'i
NK129(to)003:2650: mgo bo can gyis rta pa sha stag gis gang
NK129(to)003:2651: 'dug ste / der rgyal po'i thugs dgongs la yang /
NK129(to)003:2652: a ba pha ki ci yin bsam nas thugs 'tshab pa la /
NK129(to)003:2653: de dag thams cad rta las babs phyag 'tshal rgyal po la gus pa las /
NK129(to)003:2654: rgyal pos khyed cag su yin zhes dris pas /
NK129(to)003:2656: nged cag ni rgyal po khyod kyis bka' lung bas /
NK129(to)003:2657: lho phyogs kyi rgyal po 'phags skyes pa'i grub bum gyi dmag yin no //
NK129(to)003:2659: de'i dus na rgyal po phyag na rdo rje'i sprul par thag bcad /
NK129(to)003:2660: de nas g.yu'i smin ma can gyi yul du rgyal po phyag theg dus /
NK129(to)003:2661: gru gu'i yul na bgas kyis sleb ste /
NK129(to)003:2662: g.yu'i thub pa 'jig rten sgron ma zhes bya bas mgos byas /
NK129(to)003:2663: gser bre khal cig phyag rten du btang zhes grags so //
NK129(to)003:2664: rten de ni da lta bsam yas bzhugs pa de yin no //
NK129(to)003:2665: rgyal pos khrims gsum pa bcas pa'i dus /
NK129(to)003:2666: hor dang hor ser gnyis bka'i 'bangs su bcad /
NK129(to)003:2667: smad hor la dmag mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:2668: khams kyi dbyar mo thang du sleb /
NK129(to)003:2669: dgun gyi zla ba gsum la hor yul du thog lan bco brgyad phab /
NK129(to)003:2670: de'i dus su hor bab mis sleb /
NK129(to)003:2671: rdzu 'phrul la dbang thob pas rgyal po phyag na rdo rje'i sprul par stang bcad /
NK129(to)003:2672: gser sku chu ris can dang /
NK129(to)003:2673: sdud pa ba so can dang /
NK129(to)003:2674: dngul skyogs sha ba can dang gsum /
NK129(to)003:2676: de nas khams gsum pa'i yul du phebs dus /
NK129(to)003:2677: byang phyogs nas rgyal po rnam thos sras nam mkha' la byon te /
NK129(to)003:2678: mnga' bdag la phyag 'tshal zhabs la gtugs te /
NK129(to)003:2679: yul 'di ni las sgo'i longs spyod bco brgyad dang ldan pas nga'i yul yin pas /
NK129(to)003:2680: 'di la bka' bkyon mi gnang ba'i zhu ba phul bas /
NK129(to)003:2681: khams gsum pa'i yul zhes su grags /
NK129(to)003:2683: rgyal po phyag na rdo rje'i sprul par grags so //
NK129(to)003:2684: rgyal po 'di'i sku drin la bod du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dbu btsan /
NK129(to)003:2685: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dge 'dun pa'i bstan pa mtha' btsan pa'i phyag len mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:2686: rgyal po de'i dbu skra la /
NK129(to)003:2688: kun dga' ra ba'i them pa la btad de thams cad spyi bor khur ba dang /
NK129(to)003:2689: zhabs 'og gi rde'u blangs te dbu yi gtsug tu bzhag ste bla na /
NK129(to)003:2690: gnyen par khur ba la sogs te /
NK129(to)003:2691: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhabs tog su gang
NK129(to)003:2692: gi che ba'i thugs khur kho na mdzad pa ste
NK129(to)003:2694: bka' rnams gtan la phab pa ste /
NK129(to)003:2695: bstan pa bar dar du bzhed cing /
NK129(to)003:2696: yang bod kyi slob dpon kha cig gis chos 'byung dang bzhed pas /
NK129(to)003:2697: khri ral pa can mched gsum po 'di /
NK129(to)003:2698: rgyal po khri srong gi tsha bo yin par yang bzhed pa'ang 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:2700: khri srong gi sras mu tig btsad po /
NK129(to)003:2701: de'i sras rgyal po sad na legs /
NK129(to)003:2702: de'i sras rgyal po ral pa can mched gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:2704: o rgyan chen po'i bka' ma 'ongs lung bstan chen mo las /
NK129(to)003:2705: khri srong nyid la lung bstan mang po na //
NK129(to)003:2706: rgyal po khyod kyi yang dbon dus //
NK129(to)003:2707: rgyal po bdud kyi sprul pa 'byung //
NK129(to)003:2708: zhes gsungs pas khungs btsun pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2709: rgyal po che ba mnga' bdag khri ral 'bring po
NK129(to)003:2710: glang dar ma chung ba khri gtsang ma gsum las
NK129(to)003:2711: / khri ral pa can bdud kyis bgrongs /
NK129(to)003:2712: chung ba khri gtsang ma mon pa gror spyugs te /
NK129(to)003:2713: chos kyi kha bzungs bas skyon phab pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2714: glang dar ma rang yang chos kyis dbu yog gis lha lung dpal gyi rdo rjes bgrongs /
NK129(to)003:2715: 'di dag gis skabs su gleng brjod mang po cig yod na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2716: yig dron che bas ma bris te gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:2717: gnas skabs 'di'i dus su bstan pa bar dar zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)003:2718: da ni bstan pa phyi dar du grags pa'i lo rgyus rnams mdo tsam zhig bstan par bya ste /
NK129(to)003:2719: de yang rgyal po'i bka' chems las /
NK129(to)003:2720: rnying ma'i 'gyur mjug tsan+d+ra kirtisa bcad //
NK129(to)003:2721: gsar ma'i 'gyur mgo jo bo smri tis btsugs //
NK129(to)003:2723: tsan+t+ra kirti ni slob dpon h'u mdzad rdo rje'i slob ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:2724: lo ts+aa ba 'brog mi'i yang dag gi las tshogs /
NK129(to)003:2725: dbang phyug ma'i zor mdos bsgyur ba phan ni rnying ma'i 'gyur phyi shos yin no //
NK129(to)003:2726: de man chad du smri ti dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK129(to)003:2727: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang pos mgos byas /
NK129(to)003:2728: lha bla ma byang chub 'od yan chad du bsgyur ba mang zhig dang /
NK129(to)003:2729: btsad po lha bla ma ye shes 'od kyi dgongs pa ma grub pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK129(to)003:2730: cung po byang chub 'od kyi ring la lo ts+aa ba mang po bardzongasa pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2731: nag tsho bardzangasa nas jo bo di pam ka ra
NK129(to)003:2732: gdan drangs te ka gdams kyi sde btsugs pa dang
NK129(to)003:2733: / dus phyis grags che ba rngog blo ldan shes rab yar bcad du /
NK129(to)003:2734: sngar ma 'gyur ba'i rgyud gzhung lugs rgya cher 'gyur ba med na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2735: rgyud sgrub thabs man ngag dang bcas pa bod go sla ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:2736: skad la 'gyur bcos byas pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2741: dag phyogs su drangs mang ngo gzhan yang lo ts+aa bar grags pa du ma zhig gis /
NK129(to)003:2742: rang rang gi gzhung la rgya gar gyi khungs nga bzang /
NK129(to)003:2744: rang phyogs du ma'i che ba dang /
NK129(to)003:2745: snyan brjod brjod pa mang po zhig byung ba 'di rnams la gsar 'gyur du grags pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2746: bzhi pa de gnyis kyi khyad par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:2747: rnying ma la che ba'i yon tan du ma dang ldan zhing /
NK129(to)003:2748: mi mnyam pa'i don dang khungs btsun par bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2749: gsar ma la lo ts+aa ba rang che 'dod pa'i
NK129(to)003:2750: skyon gyis bcos bslad rang bzo mang po yod pa'i
NK129(to)003:2751: skyon bstan pa'o // de yang mkhas pa chen po rog gi ban d+he shes rab 'od na re /
NK129(to)003:2752: sngon dang po'i rgyal blon snga dar ba'i dus kyi
NK129(to)003:2753: lo ts+aa ba rnams rang rgyud pa ma yin te
NK129(to)003:2754: / sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba kho na yin te /
NK129(to)003:2755: 'gyur rnams cig thog tu cig yong bas 'dra min ye mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:2756: slar rgya gar du bsgyur dang zhu dag btub pa yin /
NK129(to)003:2757: gsar ma'i 'gyur rnams dus phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba rnams ni so so skye bo'i 'gyur yin pas /
NK129(to)003:2758: rang gi 'dod pa dang bstun nas de go bar
NK129(to)003:2759: bya ba'i phyir 'gyur mi 'dra ba mang du yod
NK129(to)003:2761: rnying ma la mi mnyam pa'i che ba gang yin zhe na /
NK129(to)003:2762: rong zom chos kyi bzang po zhes bya ba de /
NK129(to)003:2763: skye ba bdun du pan di ta'i lus brtsegs mar bzhes pa /
NK129(to)003:2765: sgra dang bstan bcos la mkhas pa /
NK129(to)003:2766: bstan pa phyi dar gyi me ro bslong ba la drin du che ba /
NK129(to)003:2767: mdo sngags gnyis ka'i pan+di ta chen po de'i zhal nas /
NK129(to)003:2769: gsar ma las khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba drug yod gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:2770: nyi 'og bod kyi rgyal khams na /
NK129(to)003:2771: 'gran zla dang bral ba'i chos 'khor gtsug lag rnam lnga dang /
NK129(to)003:2772: sprul pa'i lo pan rnams gdan 'dren pa'i yon bdag gi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)003:2773: rnying ma'i yon bdag rnams mnga' bdag mes dbon rnam
NK129(to)003:2774: gsum 'phags pa rigs gsum mgon po'i sprul pa rnams
NK129(to)003:2775: kyis gdan drangs pa yin la /
NK129(to)003:2776: da ltar gang zag sde chung dang dgon chung gi
NK129(to)003:2777: yon bdag skye bo re res byas pa'i chos dang
NK129(to)003:2778: mi 'dra gsung / phyag bzhes gtsug lag khang gi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)003:2779: sngon dpal gyi bsam yas dang /
NK129(to)003:2780: chos 'khor stod smad du gdan phab nas gsungs pa yin la /
NK129(to)003:2781: da lta'i sde gnas dang dgon chung cag cog dang mi 'dra gsung /
NK129(to)003:2782: 'gyur byed lo ts+aa ba'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)003:2783: sngon ba gor b+aee ro tsa na rma rin chen mchog /
NK129(to)003:2784: gnyag dz+ny+aa na ye shes gzhon nu ku ma ra /
NK129(to)003:2785: ka cog rnam gnyis la sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bas bsgyur ba'i chos yin /
NK129(to)003:2786: da lta lo ts+aa ba dgun bal yul du bsdad /
NK129(to)003:2787: dbyar tshad pas 'jigs bred nas mang yul du thon /
NK129(to)003:2788: sngon gyi mkhas pa'i 'gyur la rang bzo bcos ma byas pa dang mi 'dra gsung /
NK129(to)003:2789: mkhas pa dang pan+di ta'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)003:2794: sangs rgyas gsang ba la sogs pa'i rig 'dzin sa
NK129(to)003:2795: la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis gdan
NK129(to)003:2797: da lta'i pan+di ta lto ma phyid bod du gser
NK129(to)003:2798: 'tshol du yong ba'i bzang sprang ba kha cig mi
NK129(to)003:2799: 'dra gsung / zhu rten me tog gi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)003:2800: sngon gser phye bre la 'jal nas phul /
NK129(to)003:2801: g.yu sha ba'i slud pu bkang nas phul /
NK129(to)003:2802: gser gyi tong rtse bdun brtsegs su brtsegs nas phul /
NK129(to)003:2803: gser dngul dang dar zab rta khal dang dril du bkal nas phul ba'i chos yin la /
NK129(to)003:2804: da lta gser zho re re gnyis gnyis mchan nas
NK129(to)003:2805: nyug nyug byas nas zhus pa dang mi 'dra gsung
NK129(to)003:2806: / brjod bya chos kyi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)003:2807: sngon sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:2808: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bas bka' ma 'gyur ba med par gtan la phab nas /
NK129(to)003:2809: shes bya'i dngos po 'dug tshul gtan la 'bebs shing /
NK129(to)003:2810: de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs du mas brgyan pa'i chos dang /
NK129(to)003:2811: dus da lta'i lo ts+aa ba rdzun po ches sngon gyi 'gyur la bcos ma sna tshogs byas nas /
NK129(to)003:2812: 'gyur nga bzang khungs nga btsun zer zhing /
NK129(to)003:2813: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang bla ma'i gsung la ra chod byas nas /
NK129(to)003:2816: ma deb la bu ston mi btub pa'i chos dang mi 'dra ste /
NK129(to)003:2817: khyad par shin tu che gsung skad /
NK129(to)003:2818: mdor na bod du dam pa'i chos kyi dbu brnyes srol btod /
NK129(to)003:2819: dar zhing rgyas par mdzad kyang o rgyan chen po kho na'i rnam par 'phrul pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:2820: gu ru chos kyi dbang phyug gi gnam skas can
NK129(to)003:2821: gyi them byang chen mo nas sangs rgyas kun 'grub
NK129(to)003:2822: rdo rje 'chang dang bgros gsang bdag dngos dang mkha'
NK129(to)003:2823: 'gros gtad rgya bkrol rgyud lung man ngag kun gyi
NK129(to)003:2824: dngas ma bsdus rdo rje gdan du mnyam par bzhag
NK129(to)003:2825: pa'i tshe spyan ras gzigs kyis rab bskul bod mchis
NK129(to)003:2826: kyang bon gyis dbang bsgyur dam chos dus ma bab
NK129(to)003:2827: lha bshen tho kar zhes byar sku sprul nas bod
NK129(to)003:2828: rgyal tho tho ri la bka' rtags btsal slar log
NK129(to)003:2829: ri bo ta lar yong nas ni ma ra ki
NK129(to)003:2830: tar tan+t+ra bco brgyad kyi don bkrol de tshe sprul
NK129(to)003:2831: pa brgyad bkyes na o rgyan rgya gar shar nub
NK129(to)003:2832: dar rgyas byas de tshe bod rnams rgyu 'bras chos
NK129(to)003:2833: go tsam gdul byar gzigs nas srong btsan sprul par
NK129(to)003:2834: bkyes dge bcu'i khrims bcas dam chos srol chen btod
NK129(to)003:2835: mtha' dbus gtsug lag brgya dang rtsa brgyad bzhengs de
NK129(to)003:2836: nas gdung lnga song tshe chos skyong rgyal khri srong
NK129(to)003:2837: lde btsan nyid 'khrungs las sad nas o rgyan bdag
NK129(to)003:2838: sprul bod khams dkar por btang zhes so //
NK129(to)003:2839: des na rnying ma'i slob dpon lo ts+aa ba rgyal
NK129(to)003:2840: blon dang bcas pa 'di rnams ni 'phags pa spyan
NK129(to)003:2841: ras gzigs kyi rnam par 'phrul pa kho na sha
NK129(to)003:2842: stag yin te / bod gangs can gyi rgyal khams
NK129(to)003:2843: 'di nyid ston pa'i zhabs kyis ma bcag kyang ston
NK129(to)003:2844: pa'i dam chos bod du dar ba la dgongs nas
NK129(to)003:2845: stag yin te / / bod du bstan pa 'dzin skyong bsrung zhing dar bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:2846: bsam zhing 'gro ba'i don du rgyal blon lo pan rnams kyi tshul du byon pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:2847: dus phyis kyi rgyal blon lo pan du grags pa
NK129(to)003:2848: rnams kyi ba spu cig gis char yang mi nye
NK129(to)003:2849: ba yin te / de la bod kyi slob dpon kha cig gis /
NK129(to)003:2850: rnying ma la mi 'gro ba'i rtsod gnas mi bya ste blo gzu bor bzhag par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:2851: khungs btsun pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK129(to)003:2852: gong du bshad pa rnams kyang shes par bya zhing /
NK129(to)003:2853: de yang sbyin bdag chos rgyal chen po de nyid
NK129(to)003:2854: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang mtshungs pa yin
NK129(to)003:2855: pas / sngon dus lo ts+aa ba rnams la gser
NK129(to)003:2856: phye dpag tu med pa bskur nas rgya gar du
NK129(to)003:2857: pas / bardzongasa pa dang / rjes la o rgyan
NK129(to)003:2858: rgya gar shar nub kha che bal po la sogs
NK129(to)003:2859: kyi pan+di ta mkhas pa thams cad bod du spyan
NK129(to)003:2860: pas / bardzongasa pa dang / drangs / gser khri dang g.yu khri dngul khri gsum la /
NK129(to)003:2861: po pan dang rgyal po nyid bzhugs te /
NK129(to)003:2862: cig dpang cig gis mdzad de /
NK129(to)003:2863: bsgyur pa bsam yas su byas pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2864: dus phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba gar phyin dang su phrad kyi khungs med la /
NK129(to)003:2865: bal por khyi bzhin 'khyams nas rang bzo dang bcos ma'i chos la /
NK129(to)003:2866: 'ur rgyang 'don pa dang mi 'dra ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:2867: gnyis pa gsar ma la ma dag pa ci ltar yod ces pa ni /
NK129(to)003:2868: de yang gsar ma thams cad la ma dag pa'i skyon yod ces smra ba ni ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:2869: rin chen bzang po'i dus dang /
NK129(to)003:2872: rje mar pa lo ts+aa la sogs pa'i 'gyur dag pa yang mang po yod cing /
NK129(to)003:2873: dus phyis cig nas da lta khams pa bod du kha lud pa ltar /
NK129(to)003:2874: bod rnams rgya bal du thag bran pa ltar du byung bas /
NK129(to)003:2875: de'i dus su lo ts+aa ba rnams kyang khyung 'grol nas /
NK129(to)003:2876: rang rang gis che ba ni 'dod /
NK129(to)003:2877: rgya gar shar nub kyi chos rnams ni lo ts+aa ba snga ma rnams kyis bsgyur zin /
NK129(to)003:2878: nub phyogs o rgyan du ni ma slebs /
NK129(to)003:2879: mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod 'byed pa'i skal ba ni med /
NK129(to)003:2880: der rang bzo dang 'dod bcos mang po byas pas /
NK129(to)003:2881: 'phral khungs btsun nan zab zab 'dra yang /
NK129(to)003:2882: gting ma dag pa'i bshad skyon chen po yod de /
NK129(to)003:2883: o rgyan chen po'i zhal gdams gsal ba'i sgron me
NK129(to)003:2884: las de yang mnga' bdag khri srong gi gdung rgyud
NK129(to)003:2885: drug bdun nas mar la song dus bod rnams lo
NK129(to)003:2886: ts+aa bar grags te mi phyed rgya gar du thag
NK129(to)003:2887: 'bren thams cad rang rang gis che ba ni 'dod
NK129(to)003:2888: chags sdang dang 'gran sems ni rlung ltar 'tshubs rgya
NK129(to)003:2889: gar gyi pan+di ta gser 'dod rnams kyang bod la
NK129(to)003:2890: gang dar ba'i chos la 'dod bcos 'chos de yang
NK129(to)003:2891: rgya gar gyi sde snod gsum la sogs pa sngags
NK129(to)003:2892: mtshan nyid du grags pa thams cad ni da ltar
NK129(to)003:2893: 'gyur zin rgyud dang man ngag ma grags pa rnams
NK129(to)003:2894: ni o rgyan la sogs mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod rnams
NK129(to)003:2895: na yod de rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug gru thob
NK129(to)003:2896: min pas mi thon de dus kyi bod rnams o
NK129(to)003:2897: rgyan gyi yul du ni mi rdol dbus 'gyur rdo
NK129(to)003:2898: rje gdan du ni tshad pas yud de las ma
NK129(to)003:2899: tshugs rgya gar shar phyogs kha che bal yul rnams
NK129(to)003:2900: la chu ltar rgyug lo ts+aar grags pa rnams rang
NK129(to)003:2901: che dang mkhas 'dod pas gcig skyon la cig 'gel
NK129(to)003:2902: sngar 'gyur zin pa rnams la rgyud khungs dang bcos
NK129(to)003:2903: chung re byas nas nga'i 'gyur bzang po zer da
NK129(to)003:2904: lta'i sprul pa'i lo pan rnams mi bzang na ma
NK129(to)003:2905: 'ongs bod phrug so so skye bo byis pa rnams
NK129(to)003:2906: mi mkhas gsung der bod phrug lo ts+aar grags pa
NK129(to)003:2907: rnams ru 'khrol nas man ngag cung zad re la
NK129(to)003:2908: bcos cung dang gab sbas dang 'dra min mang po
NK129(to)003:2909: 'chos rgya gar gyi khungs dang brgyud pa gang legs
NK129(to)003:2910: nas 'dren bod rnams gsar ngas ni che rgyud 'dzin
NK129(to)003:2911: ma rig par / rang rang lo ts+aa ba'i kha
NK129(to)003:2912: 'dzin chos srid dang phyogs dred byed lo ts+aa ba
NK129(to)003:2913: kha cig sngar ma grags pa'i chos ni ma rnyed
NK129(to)003:2914: der sngags la sgra bcos byed lha dpa' bo cig
NK129(to)003:2915: pa la yum 'chos zhal phyag mang po la lhan
NK129(to)003:2916: skyes 'chos lhan skyes la zhag phyag mang po 'chos
NK129(to)003:2917: sku mdog la rigs lnga mang po byed dkyil 'khor
NK129(to)003:2918: la 'dod bzhed kyis dkrugs mdor na gzhan dang mi
NK129(to)003:2919: 'dra ba zhig la gtso bor 'don mkhas pa de
NK129(to)003:2920: 'dra'i rigs 'ong bar nges gsungs nas bzhad do ces
NK129(to)003:2921: gsungs pa ltar yin cing rnying ma'i chos zab pa
NK129(to)003:2922: man ngag bkol du btub pa rnams la rnying ma
NK129(to)003:2923: rtsod pa can gyi chos su bzhag nas /
NK129(to)003:2924: de dag la brten nas bzo bcos dang /
NK129(to)003:2925: ming dang rgya gar gyi khungs drang nas rang gi
NK129(to)003:2926: che ba gcig 'dod nas ma tshugs pa yin yin
NK129(to)003:2927: 'dra ba kha cig byas nas med pa tsug ston
NK129(to)003:2929: gzhan las khyad par lhag lhag po che ba 'dod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2930: rjes su 'jug pa'i bod kyi mkhan slob su grags pa rnams /
NK129(to)003:2931: gzhan yang ban de'i rigs gyur rnams kyi ni mngon shes ni med /
NK129(to)003:2933: kha bdag bzang po'i rjes su 'brangs nas rang gi lo ts+aa ba'i phyogs su bzhengs rus drangs nas /
NK129(to)003:2934: theg pa'i rigs mang po zhig yod par mngon no //
NK129(to)003:2935: de yang snga dar gyi dus kyi lo ts+aa ba
NK129(to)003:2936: chen po b+aee ro tsa na la sogs pa rnams
NK129(to)003:2937: kyis ni / sgra 'jug pa'i sgo k+aa la pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2938: sgyur byed kyis dag yig tu tsan+t+ra pa dang /
NK129(to)003:2939: rjes su 'jug pa 'byung ba'i sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2940: 'gyur bya sems can gyi skad bsgyur ba'i sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2941: don bsgyur ba mthun sbyor gyi sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2942: 'byed pa dag byed sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2943: ka li 'jug pa thabs kyi sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2944: a li bsgyur ba shes rab kyi sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2945: sgra dag byed dgos don gyi sgra dang /
NK129(to)003:2946: rang bzhin go ba sha stag la brten pa'i sgra la sogs te /
NK129(to)003:2947: 'gyur ba'i rtsa ba yang sam skri ta la brten
NK129(to)003:2948: nas yul gyi sgra la sogs te sgra skad nyi
NK129(to)003:2949: shu rtsa lnga dang sgra skad brgya rtsa brgyad b+aee
NK129(to)003:2951: rgya 'gyur dang bod 'gyur phan tshun zung 'jug mnyam du bsgyur yang /
NK129(to)003:2952: rang 'gyur du bsgyur ba yin yang /
NK129(to)003:2953: rgya gar ba la ltos mi dgos te pan+di ta phal pa las mkhas pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2954: b+ai ma la bod du byon pa'i dus lta bu'i pan+di ta dang /
NK129(to)003:2955: b+aee ro tsa na lta bu'i lo ts+aa ba yod pa /
NK129(to)003:2956: mdo sngags gnyis ka'i bstan pa bod du nyi ma shar ba 'dra ba byed gsungs /
NK129(to)003:2957: b+aee ro tsa na tsha ba rong du spyugs zhus pas /
NK129(to)003:2958: 'o na kho bo bod du yong nas ci byed /
NK129(to)003:2959: b+aee ro tsa na lta bu bod kyi lo ts+aa ba min /
NK129(to)003:2960: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta las kyang mkhas gsung /
NK129(to)003:2961: rngog blo ldan shes rab ni /
NK129(to)003:2962: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dus phyis kyi mkhas shos su grags pa yin na'ang /
NK129(to)003:2964: b+aee ro tsa na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam /
NK129(to)003:2965: ka cog rnam gnyis nyi zla zung cig 'dra //
NK129(to)003:2966: rin chen bzang po tho rang skar chen tsam //
NK129(to)003:2967: kho bo dag ni srin bu me khyer tsam //
NK129(to)003:2968: zhes pas gsar rnying gnyis la 'gyur dang khungs kyi
NK129(to)003:2969: khyad par ni de lta bu yod pa kun gyi
NK129(to)003:2970: mthun snang du grub pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:2971: gzhan yang rnying 'gyur gyi chos la gsar ma'i bdag rkyen byas pa yang mang du yod de /
NK129(to)003:2972: rdor dbyings yang snga 'gyur rnying ma'i chos skor yin /
NK129(to)003:2973: yo ga rnams kyang rnying ma'i chos skor yin /
NK129(to)003:2974: kun rig kyang rnying ma'i chos skor yin /
NK129(to)003:2976: gu ru chos dbang gi bzhed pas rgya dum pa zhang khrmo kyis /
NK129(to)003:2977: gshin rje'i skor shog ser rdza zom gang byung ba rnams la /
NK129(to)003:2978: khong rang gi tshe bdag snying 'byin skor la sogs pa phyed tsam las ma bshus pas /
NK129(to)003:2979: gzhan 'jigs byed la sogs gshin rje'i skor mang po
NK129(to)003:2980: gcig ra lo ts+aa ba'i phyag tu babs pa las
NK129(to)003:2981: rgya gar gyi khungs dang 'gyur bcos pa la /
NK129(to)003:2982: ra lugs rnams gter ma yin gsung /
NK129(to)003:2983: gzhan yang mon bum thang gter shog mang po cig ra lo ts+aa la babs te /
NK129(to)003:2988: tshogs bdag la sogs pa mang po zhig kyang gter ma la gsar ma bcos pa yin gsungs /
NK129(to)003:2989: de rnams kyi don yang rnying ma la rtsod pa can gyis chos su byas /
NK129(to)003:2990: ma dag pa la dag par bardzusa pa'i rig pa mang po zhig yod ces /
NK129(to)003:2991: ri khrod kyi mkhas pa brtson seng dang /
NK129(to)003:2992: sman lung ba mi spyod rdo rje la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:2993: rnams kyis yang gsung sgros brjod bya mang po zhig
NK129(to)003:2994: snang ngo // des ni gsar rnying gi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)003:2995: gsar ma la yang deng sang gi slob dpon rnams kyi bdag rkyen ji ltar bzang yang /
NK129(to)003:2996: legs par brtags shing dpyad na /
NK129(to)003:2997: ma dag pa'i skyon 'gyur yod par bstan pa 'di yang /
NK129(to)003:2998: rang 'dod 'gran sems zhe sdang gis kun nas bslang ba'i gtam ma yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:2999: mkhas pa gong ma rnams kyis gsung dang gtan tshig dang /
NK129(to)003:3000: lo rgyus las ji ltar byung ba rnams blo gzu bor bzhag ste /
NK129(to)003:3001: legs par bltas pa'i gtan tshig yin no //
NK129(to)003:3002: don lnga pa tha snyad mkhan gyis rtsod pa bzlog pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3003: dus phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3004: bod kyi slob dpon rtog ge ba tha snyad mkhan la sogs 'ga' zhig na re /
NK129(to)003:3005: rnying ma mi dag lta log yin zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3006: hwa shang gi lta ba yod pas /
NK129(to)003:3008: de rnams ni shin tu ma go ba'i gnas te /
NK129(to)003:3009: hwa shang gi chos kyis bsre bslad ni /
NK129(to)003:3010: rdzogs pa chen po snga 'gyur phyi 'gyur bka' gter gang la'ang yod pa'i don med de /
NK129(to)003:3011: bod du byon pa'i pan+di ta /
NK129(to)003:3013: b+ai ma la mi tra gnyis kyis slob dpon hwa shang min /
