NK129(to)003:3014: hwa shang ni rgya nag rtsis la mkhas pas /
NK129(to)003:3015: mnga' bdag rgyal pos bsam yas kyi rtsis la bos pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:3016: rtsis kyi 'gyur ni mang po 'gyur bar snang /
NK129(to)003:3017: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos bka' gter gang na yang /
NK129(to)003:3018: hwa shang la zhus hwa shang gis gnang bya ba'i chos yi ge ni cig kyang med /
NK129(to)003:3020: ka cog la sogs pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK129(to)003:3021: chos rgya gar du phyin nas bsgyur zer ba la /
NK129(to)003:3022: hwa shang la zhus so bya ba tshig cig kyang mthong ma myong /
NK129(to)003:3023: rdzogs chen gyi rgyud re re tsam nas /
NK129(to)003:3024: dag byed kyi tshig gtan la 'bebs pa la so so'i sgra ni 'di skad de /
NK129(to)003:3025: rang rang gis sgra don gtan la 'bebs pa la
NK129(to)003:3026: 'adi'o zhes ston pa'i phyir rgya gar gyi skad du
NK129(to)003:3028: d+ha na ko sha gling pa'i skad du /
NK129(to)003:3033: tho gar yul gyi skad du /
NK129(to)003:3034: za hor gyi skad du 'di skad ces bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3035: ces rgyud kyi spyi bzhag bshad nas /
NK129(to)003:3036: khungs btsun pa rang phyogs su bstan pa las /
NK129(to)003:3038: rgya gar sam skri ta'i skad du /
NK129(to)003:3042: rgyud gnyis tsam na 'dug pa la rtsod pa'i khungs drangs pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3043: de ma yin par ha shang gis 'di gsung /
NK129(to)003:3044: bod kyi lo ts+aa bas 'dir bsgyur dbang bskur rgyud lung man ngag dang bcas pa 'di gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:3046: khungs su la'ang yod mi srid de /
NK129(to)003:3047: deng sang kha cig gis smra ba ni lug chu 'bog gam /
NK129(to)003:3048: khyi phyogs za'i gtan tshigs su shes par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3049: yang rdzogs pa chen po la lta ba la skyon yod de zhes zer na /
NK129(to)003:3050: lta ba la skyon ji ltar yod /
NK129(to)003:3051: nged rdzogs pa chen po la /
NK129(to)003:3055: theg pa rim pa dang phye ba'i lta sgom lam gyi rim pa ni yod mod kyi /
NK129(to)003:3057: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba gang yin na /
NK129(to)003:3059: rang byung ye shes kyi snying po /
NK129(to)003:3060: khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po /
NK129(to)003:3061: gnas lugs gnyug ma'i don 'di nyid mu bzhi'i mthar ma lhung bar /
NK129(to)003:3062: rtag chad gnyis kyi mtha' las grol ba /
NK129(to)003:3064: rang byung lhun grub ye gdod ma nas rang bzhin rnam dag tu rdzogs pas /
NK129(to)003:3065: 'dus ma byas chos nyid kyi rang bzhin ngo bo stong pa /
NK129(to)003:3067: thugs rje 'char ba'i sgo ma 'gag pa /
NK129(to)003:3069: 'di zhes mtshon pa'i tshig rtag brtan ther zug ma yin pa /
NK129(to)003:3070: kha len gdags bya dang bral ba cig 'dod pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3071: de la rdzogs pa chen po smad pa rnams la /
NK129(to)003:3072: lta ba de las lhag pa zhig tshig brjod bya dang /
NK129(to)003:3073: don go bas nyams su len pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3074: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa 'di la ni med /
NK129(to)003:3075: lta ba 'di ma yin pa zhig 'dod na ni /
NK129(to)003:3076: phyi ltar du sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3077: nang ltar du rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa'i chos thams cad ma yin par thal lo //
NK129(to)003:3078: yang gsar rnying gnyis kyi mi mthun no zer na /
NK129(to)003:3080: rnying mas kyang gzhi mi 'gyur ba /
NK129(to)003:3081: gnas lugs kyi don ma nor ba zhig gis gzhi 'dzin /
NK129(to)003:3082: lam ma nor ba lta sgom spyod gsum /
NK129(to)003:3084: rten cing 'brel pa 'byung ba las ma 'gal ba zhig nyams su len /
NK129(to)003:3085: 'bras bu sku lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid spangs
NK129(to)003:3086: thob med pa'i ngang du ye rdzogs lhun grub tu
NK129(to)003:3087: 'dod / lta ba stong nyid mtha' bral /
NK129(to)003:3089: spyod pa theg pa'i rim pa dang bstun pa'i 'jug sgo ma nor ba /
NK129(to)003:3091: tshogs gnyis bskyed rim bzlas brjod /
NK129(to)003:3093: stong nyid lta ba rnam dag /
NK129(to)003:3095: rjes su bsngo ba smon lam /
NK129(to)003:3096: mdor bsdus pa lam 'jug pa'i sgo 'dir 'dus pa
NK129(to)003:3097: cig /'di las gzhan pa'i chos kyi 'jug sgo ni
NK129(to)003:3098: gsar ma ba rnams la yang med las che /
NK129(to)003:3099: gzhan yang gsar rnying gnyis bskyed rdzogs lag len gyi skor la yang /
NK129(to)003:3100: ming mi mthun yang don mthun pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3102: bum dbang la brten nas rgyud smin par bya ba'i lha'i dbang dang /
NK129(to)003:3103: gsang dbang la brten nas ngag smin par bya ba byang sems thig le'i dbang dang /
NK129(to)003:3104: shes rab ye shes la brten nas bde ba lam
NK129(to)003:3105: du byed pa yul phyag rgya la brten te dga'
NK129(to)003:3106: bzhi'i 'gros nyams su len pa shes rab ye shes
NK129(to)003:3107: kyi dbang dang / rang rig ye shes kyi rtsal
NK129(to)003:3108: dbang rang thog tu ngo sprad nas sems nyid chos
NK129(to)003:3109: skur ngo sprod byed pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3112: gsar ma'i bsrung 'khor bsgom pa cig /
NK129(to)003:3114: gsar ma'i bdun rnam dag gcig /
NK129(to)003:3115: rnying ma'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3116: gsar ma'i ye shes kyi tshogs stong nyid du bsgom pa gcig /
NK129(to)003:3117: rnying ma'i kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3118: gsar ma'i tshad med pa bsgom pa cig rnying ma'i gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3119: gsar ma'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa cig /
NK129(to)003:3120: lha bsgom pa la cho ga drug gis bskyed pa /
NK129(to)003:3121: skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed pa /
NK129(to)003:3123: cho ga gsum gyi bskyed pa rnams ni gnyis ka la yod de mthun /
NK129(to)003:3126: rnying ma'i sman mchod don rnams bsgo ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3127: gsar ma'i bskyed rim bdud rtsi myong ba cig /
NK129(to)003:3132: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i mtha' rgyas dang bcas pa ming du mi cig na'ang /
NK129(to)003:3133: don du cig pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3134: yang lo ts+aa ba 'ga' zhig na re /
NK129(to)003:3135: rgya gar na rnying ma mi 'dug zer na'ang /
NK129(to)003:3136: de'i gnas lugs rnams gong du rgyas par bshad yod cing /
NK129(to)003:3137: grub chen o rgyan pa'i gsungs nas /
NK129(to)003:3138: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba kha cig rgya gar na rnying ma sgyur rgyu mi 'dug zer /
NK129(to)003:3139: de la chags lo ts+aa ba bdag rang gis dbang zhus kyi bla ma yin yang /
NK129(to)003:3140: rgya gar na rnying ma bsgyur rgyu mi 'dug zer /
NK129(to)003:3141: de 'dra khong rang gis blo chung gi gtam yin /
NK129(to)003:3142: lo ts+aa ba rgya gar shar phyogs su yug re
NK129(to)003:3143: las ma phyin pas rgya gar na gang yod kyi
NK129(to)003:3144: cha ci yod / des na bod la gang yod kyi mtha' yang mi chod /
NK129(to)003:3145: spyir yang rgya gar tshad chu che bas rgya gar gyis dpe rnams rul ba mang /
NK129(to)003:3146: sangs rgyas kyi bka' la tshad bzung med pa la /
NK129(to)003:3147: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba rkyang res khungs mi chod /
NK129(to)003:3148: nga nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul du phyin pa yin kyang mu dang mtha' ma chod /
NK129(to)003:3149: de yang dang po'i rgya dpe rnams dus phyis bal po na mang ba yin /
NK129(to)003:3150: de bas bal po b+he ha ra'i gtsug lag khang cig na /
NK129(to)003:3151: rnying ma'i rgyud kyi rnam grangs rang yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa bzhugs 'dug /
NK129(to)003:3152: ngas bod kyi rnying ma ba rnams la ngas rnying ma'i rgya dpe dang /
NK129(to)003:3153: pan+di ta tshur 'gugs khyed rang rnams mang yul gyi
NK129(to)003:3154: grong du 'gro na ngas lo ts+aa byas te bsgyur
NK129(to)003:3155: zer ba byas pas ma grub /
NK129(to)003:3156: de 'gyur na rnying ma'i 'gyur da rung bya rgyu yod pa la gsungs /
NK129(to)003:3157: yang bod kyi shes par 'dod pa 'ga' zhig na re /
NK129(to)003:3159: bod kyi sngags rgan tshos bcos pa yin mi dag zer /
NK129(to)003:3160: de 'dra yang 'os su mi 'gro ba'i gtam yin te /
NK129(to)003:3161: shes na de 'dra ba'i chos rang re tshos kyang chos dang /
NK129(to)003:3162: de las legs rgyu ni sangs rgyas kyi bka' la yang med gsungs so //
NK129(to)003:3163: yang dus 'phyis kyi bod kyi slob dpon rnams kyis /
NK129(to)003:3164: mnga' ris kyi lha byang chub 'od dang /
NK129(to)003:3165: mnga' bdag zhi ba 'od kyis mdzad pa'i sngags log sun 'byin du grags pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3166: lo ts+aa ba 'gos lha btsas kyis bcos zer ba'i sngags log sun 'byin yin zer ba 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:3167: btsad po lha gnyis kyis mdzad pa ni shin tu mi dag ste /
NK129(to)003:3170: btsad po zhal bdag bzang ba la skad kha g.yar ba yin mod /
NK129(to)003:3171: de'i rtsa ba gang la skyon bzung na /
NK129(to)003:3172: sbyor sgrol gnyis la 'thab pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3173: sbyor ba la brten nas khrims kyi sdom pa zhig /
NK129(to)003:3174: chos sde byi phrug gis bkangs zer te /
NK129(to)003:3175: 'o na dbang gsum pa'i skabs la brten nas /
NK129(to)003:3177: dga' bzhi'i lam la brten nas bde stong zung du 'jug pa /
NK129(to)003:3178: lam mtha' thug pa'i zab mo gsar ma rnams kyang mi 'dod dam /
NK129(to)003:3179: rnying ma rnams kyang gsang sngags lam du 'gro zhing
NK129(to)003:3180: lam du slongs pa zhig sgom phyag len yin cing
NK129(to)003:3181: / pho mo spyad tshad sangs rgya'o zhes ni ma bshad /
NK129(to)003:3182: gsar ma ba yin pa tsam gyi lam du slangs pa'i khyab byed gang na yod /
NK129(to)003:3183: lam du ma bslangs na ni gsar ma'i byas pa'i byi phrug bcos pa mang /
NK129(to)003:3185: sngags sde gnyis ka'i khrod na gsar ma ba dpung che bas so //
NK129(to)003:3186: 'o na blo gzu bor ji ltar 'jog ce na /
NK129(to)003:3187: lam nyams su blang na ni /
NK129(to)003:3188: rnying ma sangs rgyas pa'i lam yin la /
NK129(to)003:3189: lam nyams su blangs na ni gsar ma yang ltung ba'i gnas su mi 'gyur ram /
NK129(to)003:3190: yang rnying ma ba la sgrol ba bya ba yod /
NK129(to)003:3191: srog chags dngos su bsgral bas las kyi dmyal bar skye /
NK129(to)003:3192: bam bsgrubs pas dur khrod kyi ro chad /
NK129(to)003:3195: bya ba la sogs pa ma rabs ya po'i gtam 'dra ba 'ga' 'dug na'ang /
NK129(to)003:3196: rgyud kyi dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3198: phur pa bi to'i rgyud las bsad pa nyid kyis
NK129(to)003:3199: bsad pa'i mchog bdag nyid rtogs pa mngon gyur nas
NK129(to)003:3200: thugs rje'i thabs kyis sgrol ba rnams dmigs med chos
NK129(to)003:3201: kyi dbyings su bsgral ces pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3202: dregs pa'i spyi rgyud las dang po rtogs pas bdag
NK129(to)003:3203: nyid bsgral de nas gnyis med blo yis ni blo
NK129(to)003:3204: ngan sems can snying rje bas thugs rje'i thabs kyis
NK129(to)003:3206: phur pa rtsa thung gi rgyud las snying rjes bsgral
NK129(to)003:3207: ba'i dam tshig ni bsad cing gnan pa ma yin
NK129(to)003:3208: te phung po rdo rjer gtam byas nas rnam par
NK129(to)003:3211: he ru ka gal po'i rgyud las //
NK129(to)003:3212: thabs dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK129(to)003:3213: bdag nyid chos kyi dbyings su bsgral //
NK129(to)003:3214: thabs la mkhas pa'i snying rje yis //
NK129(to)003:3215: ma dag ru tra bsgral bar bya //
NK129(to)003:3216: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su spar //
NK129(to)003:3218: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud las yang dag don rtogs blo yis ni //
NK129(to)003:3219: ma rtogs sems can gnas su bsgral //
NK129(to)003:3220: dus gsum bde gshegs de la mnyes //
NK129(to)003:3221: mchog gi mchod pa chen por bzhes //
NK129(to)003:3222: zhes pa la sogs pa dgongs don mang po cig gsungs pas /
NK129(to)003:3223: rtogs dgongs dang ldan pa'i tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pa phul du phyin pa /
NK129(to)003:3224: yul snying rje ba'i rnam par shes pa bde bar spar la dgongs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3225: dper na bla ma zhang gis dbyar gyi dus su
NK129(to)003:3226: sems can mang po la rdo dang shing drud nas
NK129(to)003:3227: mthong tshod gsod / las ngan tsho bsad pa dum
NK129(to)003:3228: pa nyung ngu 'gro yong gsungs pa dang mthun no
NK129(to)003:3229: mthong tshod gsod / // gzhan yang zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las bzhi ni /
NK129(to)003:3230: gsar ma na'ang khyad med du yod de la sgos
NK129(to)003:3231: su rnying ma la skyon 'gel bas mi 'ong ste
NK129(to)003:3232: / sngon nas da lta'i bar du rnying ma'i bla ma tshad ldan gyis /
NK129(to)003:3233: sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i lam ma nor ba yin zer nas /
NK129(to)003:3234: ga na su gsod pa mthong /
NK129(to)003:3235: las ngan log pa'i blo can gyis spyod pa ngan pa sna tshogs cig byed pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3236: rnying ma las mi nyung ba cig gsar ma la yang 'dra /
NK129(to)003:3237: yang bam bsgrub ces pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3238: mkha' 'gro dgyes par byed pa'i dam rdzas yin pas /
NK129(to)003:3239: shi ba'i ro de yang gson dus nad gcong med pa /
NK129(to)003:3240: nad ngan dang dug mtshon la sogs glo bur rkyen ngan gyis ma shi ba /
NK129(to)003:3241: rang bzhin gyi nad kyis shi ba'i ro na gzhon gtsang ma zhig dgos par bshad de /
NK129(to)003:3242: rnying ma na mi btsan thabs su bsad la /
NK129(to)003:3243: bam bsgrub zhes bya bar dper mi srid pa'i chos nyid yin no //
NK129(to)003:3244: spyir yang rgyud dngos grub 'byung ba'i dgongs par bshad pa las /
NK129(to)003:3245: rnying ma bas ro'am bam bsgrub byed cing 'dug zer ba /
NK129(to)003:3246: thos mthong su la'ang med pas /
NK129(to)003:3247: sgro skur du 'gro ba'i skabs med do //
NK129(to)003:3248: sman sgrub pa ni da lta'i bar du'ang phyag len shin tu yod de /
NK129(to)003:3249: rgyud lung man ngag la sogs pa /
NK129(to)003:3250: mkhas pa chen po bye ma la'i gzhung lugs shin tu mang ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3251: o rgyan chen po'i phyag bzhes lung yang bka' gter gnyis ka na mang ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:3254: rgyal ba mnyes pa'i dam rdzas /
NK129(to)003:3257: mchod rdzas thams cad kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa yin pas /
NK129(to)003:3258: shin tu gsang ba'i dam rdzas zhes kyang bya /
NK129(to)003:3259: a mri ta zhes kyang bya /
NK129(to)003:3260: ra sa ya na zhes kyang bya ste /
NK129(to)003:3261: rnying ma ba la phyag len kyang ma chad par yod /
NK129(to)003:3263: b+ai ma las bsgrubs pa'i phab kyang gter nas byon /
NK129(to)003:3264: sman dpyad nas kyang chos sman zer /
NK129(to)003:3265: 'di'i sgrub thabs dang yon tan ni /
NK129(to)003:3266: gsar ma nas kyang 'thor bu ba 'ga' yod pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3267: kho bo rat+na gling pas kyang lo sum cu rtsa gnyis nas lnga cu rtsa drug gi bar du /
NK129(to)003:3268: phyogs bzhi mtha' dbus thams cad du sman sgrub lan nyi shu rtsa cig song ste /
NK129(to)003:3269: bkra shis pa'i sgo du ma nas bstan pa la phan btags par 'dod pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3270: 'gos lhas btsas kyis sngags log sun 'byin na ni /
NK129(to)003:3271: mi rims na ba'i kha 'chal dang 'dra ba 'di 'dra 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:3272: rdzogs pa chen po snga 'gyur lnga bya ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3273: phyi 'gyur bcu gsum bya ba 'di rnams ni chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3274: yang phur pa bi to'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:3275: phur pa rtsa thung gi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:3276: phur pa man ngag gi rgyud bya ba la sogs pa'i lo ts+aa ba b+aee ro dang /
NK129(to)003:3277: nam mkha'i snying pos bsgyur zer ba 'di rnams chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3278: yang bdud rtsi 'byung rgyud dang bdud rtsi ye shes 'khor lo dang /
NK129(to)003:3279: bdud rtsi ye shes bla ma dang /
NK129(to)003:3280: bdud rtsi lung bal po brgyad b+ai ma la dang
NK129(to)003:3281: gnyags dz+ny+aa nas bsgyur zer ba 'di rnams chos log
NK129(to)003:3283: gzhan yang rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:3285: rta mgrin yang gsang gi rgyud /
NK129(to)003:3286: drag po lha bzhi'i rgyud la sogs pa rnams ni chos log go //
NK129(to)003:3287: gzhan yang gsang ba snying po'i rgyud /
NK129(to)003:3289: yang dag gal po'i rgyud la sogs pa gnyags dz+ny+aa nas bsgyur zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3290: gnubs nam mkha'i snying pos bsgyur zer ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3291: ka cog gis bsgyur zer ba 'di rnams ni chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3292: gzhan yang 'jam dpal gshin rje'i skor dang /
NK129(to)003:3294: ma mo srid pa'i bem chen mo la sogs pa
NK129(to)003:3295: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis bsgyur zer ba 'di
NK129(to)003:3296: rnams log chos dri ma yin no //
NK129(to)003:3297: zhes zer ba'i 'di 'dra ba'i grangs bgrangs kyi mi lang ste /
NK129(to)003:3298: bod kyi yul du rnying ma'i chos su gtogs so cog /
NK129(to)003:3299: de dang 'thun pa'i lo ts+aa ba /
NK129(to)003:3300: mdor na khong rang gis rna bas thos tshad chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3301: zer ba'i phyogs 'then glen gtam kho na 'ba' zhig ste /
NK129(to)003:3302: bden pa'i gnas ni gang yang med de /
NK129(to)003:3303: khos rgya gar gyi khungs 'tshol nas /
NK129(to)003:3304: bstan pa sngar dar ba'i dus su bsgyur ba la khos ci'i phyir khungs chod /
NK129(to)003:3305: 'o na kho dus phyis grub thob cig yin na /
NK129(to)003:3306: rgya gar gyi dur khrod dang mkha' 'gro'i gsang mdzod gar slebs /
NK129(to)003:3308: kho bstan pa snga phyi bar gsum du rgyus yod pa'i tshe'i rig 'dzin thob pa cig yin nam /
NK129(to)003:3309: yang na ji lta ba ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas yin nam /
NK129(to)003:3310: yang na dus gsum ma bsgrib par gsal ba'i mngon shes mnga' 'am /
NK129(to)003:3311: yang na nub phyogs o rgyan nas bal po phan
NK129(to)003:3312: chad na kho la rgyus med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK129(to)003:3313: bka' med dam / 'o na rnying ma la chos
NK129(to)003:3314: min pa'i rgyu mtshan thub pa'i bstan pa la rgya
NK129(to)003:3315: gar du byung ba ni med /
NK129(to)003:3316: rgyal blon sngar dar ba'i dus su bod du chos bsgyur ba yang med /
NK129(to)003:3317: lta ba'i sa na log pa 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3318: sgom pa spyod pa'i sa na lam nor pa 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3319: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i skabs na bka' lung mi mthun pa 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3320: chos thams cad kyi sngon 'gro'i skabs na 'gal ba 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3322: rjes kyi skabs na 'gal ba 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3323: lo ts+aa ba tshad mas ma bsgyur ba'i sgra ma dag pa 'di yod /
NK129(to)003:3324: ces pa'i gtan tshig khungs dang bcas pa'am /
NK129(to)003:3325: brjod bya tshig cig med par lug chu 'bog gi yod zam /
NK129(to)003:3326: rnying ma'i chos thos tshad dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3327: zer ba 'di gtan tshig dang brjod bya srid pa lam du 'gro ba e yod /
NK129(to)003:3328: dper na rnying ma'i bla ma cig gis /
NK129(to)003:3329: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang po dang /
NK129(to)003:3330: mar pa lo ts+aas bsgyur zer ba'i /
NK129(to)003:3334: rdo rje gdan bzhi la sogs pa 'di rnams chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3335: gur rtag gnyis la sogs pa rin chen bzang pos
NK129(to)003:3336: bsgyur zer ba 'di dag kyang chos log dri ma
NK129(to)003:3337: can yin no // yang ras chung bas bsgyur zer
NK129(to)003:3338: ba'i rdo ha'i skor rnams kyang chos log dri ma
NK129(to)003:3339: can yin no // can yin no // lo ts+aa
NK129(to)003:3340: ba 'brog mis bsgyur zer ba'i lam 'bras bu dang
NK129(to)003:3341: bcas pa 'di dag kyang chos log dri ma can
NK129(to)003:3342: can yin no // can yin no // yin no // zer ba lta bu /
NK129(to)003:3343: dper na gsar ma'i 'gyur du grags so cog /
NK129(to)003:3344: de'i 'gyur byed kyi lo ts+aa ba dang bcas la /
NK129(to)003:3345: 'di chos log dri ma can yin no //
NK129(to)003:3346: zer ba kho na'i rnam grangs su phyes na mkhas pa'i rnam bzhag su e 'gro /
NK129(to)003:3349: 'di 'dra ba'i brjod byas rnying ma'i chos 'di bsnub
NK129(to)003:3350: pa zhig byung na bsam pa'i las mtha' log pa'i
NK129(to)003:3351: dbang gis zhe sdang gis kun nas bslang ba'i tshig
NK129(to)003:3352: la / blo gzu bor bzhag nas /
NK129(to)003:3353: gsar rnying gnyis ka'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa su gang gis brtag kyang /
NK129(to)003:3354: bden pa dang 'os shing 'thad pa'i gnas su 'gro ba ni ma srid de /
NK129(to)003:3356: smyo ba'am rnam shes gdon gyis bsgyur ba yin na ni ma nges kyi /
NK129(to)003:3357: dran shes bzhin du byas pa yin na ni /
NK129(to)003:3358: rdo rje 'chang gis gsung pa'i rgyu 'bras dang /
NK129(to)003:3363: log pa brgyad la sogs pa'i chos spangs 'di rnams bden ni /
NK129(to)003:3364: kho dmyal ba'i gnas su yod par nges la /
NK129(to)003:3365: mi bden na ni chos gang la'ang nges 'jog gi gnas med par 'gyur bas /
NK129(to)003:3366: gang zag dam pa rnams kyis legs par dgongs shing dpyad par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3367: zhes pa 'di yang phyogs snga dang zhe sdang gis kun nas bslangs pa'i tshig yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3368: lung rigs rtogs dpyod drang por gtong ba'i rgyu mtshan
NK129(to)003:3369: e yin gang zag dam pa rnams kyis gzigs par
NK129(to)003:3370: 'tshal lo // yang khyung po rnal 'byor gyis kyang /
NK129(to)003:3371: rdzogs pa chen po 'di la lta ba rnam dag cig 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:3372: spyod pa gti mug pa cig 'dug zer ba snang ste /
NK129(to)003:3373: khyung po ni gang zag rtsod med yin mod kyi /
NK129(to)003:3374: gsung de ni rig shing 'os pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:3375: thams cad kyis zab pa'i khyad par gang gis 'byed pa yin na /
NK129(to)003:3376: lta ba rnam dag gis 'byed pa yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3377: nyan thos nas a ti'i bar du theg pa rim pa dgu po 'di dag kyang /
NK129(to)003:3378: lta ba kho nas khyad par phye ba yin mod /
NK129(to)003:3381: nam 'phang gcod pa la khyung dang bye'u khyad par gyis dpe dang mtshungs te /
NK129(to)003:3382: nyan thos 'og ma'i theg pa rnams la lta ba sgom pa spyod pa'i sa na /
NK129(to)003:3383: rim skyes dang dman pa dang blo chung ba'i lam
NK129(to)003:3384: las med pa kho nas bskal par sangs rgyas ma
NK129(to)003:3385: thob pa yin / dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK129(to)003:3386: rdzogs pa chen po lta ba'i rdzong //
NK129(to)003:3387: sa lam skad cig gcod pa yin //
NK129(to)003:3388: theg dman 'og ma'i do zla min //
NK129(to)003:3391: lta ba rnam dag de la lam du mdzad pas chog mod /
NK129(to)003:3392: lta ba rnam dag de nyams su len pa la
NK129(to)003:3393: spyod pa gti mug gang min cis kyang byed dgos
NK129(to)003:3394: zer ba'i bshad pa ni med do //
NK129(to)003:3396: rnying ma la bdag cag gis bla ma skad gnyis
NK129(to)003:3397: smra ba'i bla ma nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyis gsungs
NK129(to)003:3398: nas rnying ma ni bal po na yang rgya dpe
NK129(to)003:3399: 'dug pa dang / bsam yas na yang phur pa rtsa thung gi rgya dpe 'dug pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3401: bdag gi ni chos la smad pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3402: chos spangs kyi las lci bas gtang snyoms su bzhag go //
NK129(to)003:3403: ces pa'i tshig bcad bzhi pa zhig byas 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:3404: 'di yang gang zag mkhas pa'i gsung tshul ma yin /
NK129(to)003:3405: 'o na khyod kyi bla ma lo ts+aa ba de tshad ma ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)003:3406: bla ma'i chos btub rung khyod kyis dag pa ma byin pas so //
NK129(to)003:3407: gnyis pa bal po na yang lo ts+aa bas mthong ba'i rgyud 'dug /
NK129(to)003:3408: bsam yas na yang rgya dpe bzhugs 'dug bzhin du
NK129(to)003:3409: dag pa mi ster bar btang snyoms su bzhag zer
NK129(to)003:3410: na / bod du 'gyur ba'i gsar rnying gi chos thams cad la yid ches pa'i khungs dang /
NK129(to)003:3412: gang yang min pa'i btang snyoms su thams cad bzhag go //
NK129(to)003:3413: bod na khungs btsun pa'i chos med pa thag chod pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3414: yang bod kyi slob dpon kha cig gis /
NK129(to)003:3415: rang gis byas pa'i bstan bcos 'ga' zhig nas /
NK129(to)003:3416: zhi rdzogs bon gsum lta ba ngan pas bslad pa yin zer bas /
NK129(to)003:3417: bon la 'di smra don med kyi /
NK129(to)003:3418: zhi byed dang rdzogs chen chos min par khas blangs de ltar yin na /
NK129(to)003:3419: deng sang bod gangs can gyi rgyal khams na grub thob dang /
NK129(to)003:3422: zhi rdzogs kyi brgyud pa ci tsam 'dug /
NK129(to)003:3424: las su song ba'i gtam yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3425: dge slong legs pa'i skar ma dang 'dra bas /
NK129(to)003:3426: 'di skad smra mi de dag kyang /
NK129(to)003:3427: deng sang 'o brgyal ba'i gnas na lam ma log
NK129(to)003:3428: pa cig 'dug zer ba yang rna bas ma thos
NK129(to)003:3429: te / rgyu mtshan thams cad la yod par mngon /
NK129(to)003:3430: yang bod kyi slob dpon 'ga' zhig na re /
NK129(to)003:3431: rnying ma'i lhun grub 'od gsal gyi snang ba 'di /
NK129(to)003:3432: rtag lta yin no zer ba yang yod do //
NK129(to)003:3433: de ni chos de'i gnas lugs rang gis spu tsam yang ma go cha dang rgyus med par /
NK129(to)003:3434: mun nang la mda' 'phen yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3435: 'di ni rang rig ye shes kyi snang ba /
NK129(to)003:3436: sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid /
NK129(to)003:3437: 'dus ma byas rang byung lhun grub /
NK129(to)003:3439: stong pa'i yul du stong pa'i mdangs shar ba yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3440: rtag lta yin na ni rig pa gzhi dngos po'i 'dug tshul dang dbyer med de /
NK129(to)003:3448: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes /
NK129(to)003:3449: skye 'gag gnas gsum dang bral ba zhig yin te /
NK129(to)003:3450: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud du ma zhig nas 'di'i dgongs pa bshad pa bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK129(to)003:3451: thun mong gis bka' pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa las kyang /
NK129(to)003:3452: sems ni sems ma mchis te /
NK129(to)003:3453: sems kyi rang bzhin ni 'od gsal ba'o //
NK129(to)003:3456: ye shes snang ba lam me ba //
NK129(to)003:3457: 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron //
NK129(to)003:3460: nam mkha' ji ltar mthong zhes don de brtag par gyis //
NK129(to)003:3463: rang rig ye shes snying po can //
NK129(to)003:3464: nam mkha' dag tu rnam par gsal //
NK129(to)003:3466: sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK129(to)003:3468: ye shes lnga ni dbyings kyi rgyan du che'o //
NK129(to)003:3469: stong pa nyid ni stong pa nyid kyi ngang du 'od gsal lo //
NK129(to)003:3470: ces pa la sogs pa don gyis dgongs pa len shes na ni /
NK129(to)003:3471: theg pa chen po'i bka' mang po nas gsungs pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:3472: de'ang gzhi snang ye shes kyi snying po can zhes bya ste /
NK129(to)003:3473: rig pa ngo bo rang gsal dri ma med pa las /
NK129(to)003:3474: chos kyi dbyings la sogs pa ste /
NK129(to)003:3476: gser sa 'og na yod pa'i 'od gdang nam mkha' la gsal ba'am /
NK129(to)003:3477: nyi ma shar ba'i mdangs nub rir gsal ba ltar yin gyi /
NK129(to)003:3478: rgyu rkyen las grub pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3480: mtshan ma bzung yul du ma grub pas rtag lta zhes ci'i phyir du 'dog /
NK129(to)003:3481: rang snang ye shes kyi rang mdangs stong pa go
NK129(to)003:3482: ma 'gag pa'i 'char sgo 'di la rtag ltar 'gro
NK129(to)003:3483: na ni / sems zer ba'i gzhi'i 'dug tshul 'di yang rtag ltar 'gro dgos /
NK129(to)003:3485: 'dug tshul gyi dpe don rtags gsum ni gong du rgyas par bshad zin to //
NK129(to)003:3486: yang rdzogs pa chen po la gang zag snga phyi
NK129(to)003:3487: bar gsum dran cing rgyus yod pa'i lung gang la
NK129(to)003:3488: byed na / bod gangs can du bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' rab 'byams shes /
NK129(to)003:3489: dkyil 'khor brgya zhal phye shes zer ba /
NK129(to)003:3490: rtogs ldan grub thob zer ba mang bar byung ste /
NK129(to)003:3491: skye ba snga phyi la 'khrul pas bar du mi chod par /
NK129(to)003:3492: rang sems la dbang thob pa ste /
NK129(to)003:3493: bsam shing 'gro ba'i don du sprul pa mdzad pa kar+m+aa pa 'a di nyid yin te /
NK129(to)003:3495: rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam 'phrul dga' rab rdo rje la /
NK129(to)003:3496: rdzogs pa chen po klong chen rab 'byams la sogs pa nyan pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:3497: rang byung rdo rje bdag kyang rtog rtse rnal 'byor dbang phyug zhes bya bar gyur cing /
NK129(to)003:3498: rdzogs pa chen po'i sgra don thams cad rtogs pa yin gsungs /
NK129(to)003:3500: rgyal po dza'i rjes slob dpon pad+ma bod du ma byon pa'i snga rol tsam na /
NK129(to)003:3501: rgya gar na bdag kyang gsang sngags rnying ma ston
NK129(to)003:3502: shes pa'i gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa zhig tu
NK129(to)003:3503: gyur nas mtshan yang rdo rje ye shes 'bar zhes
NK129(to)003:3505: yang bod du gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyi slob ma /
NK129(to)003:3506: rdo rje dbang phyug ces bya ba bskyed rdzogs la
NK129(to)003:3507: dbang thob pa rdzogs pa chen po 'ba' zhig bsgom
NK129(to)003:3508: pa'i cog ro sgom pa zhes bya ba de kho
NK129(to)003:3509: bo yin / de'i don gyis da lta yang rdzogs
NK129(to)003:3510: chen gyi chos thams cad phyogs med du rtogs pa
NK129(to)003:3512: yang kar+m+aahpa mthong ba don ldan la bde chen bla ma bya bas /
NK129(to)003:3513: rdzogs pa chen po la rtsod pa mang po 'dug /
NK129(to)003:3515: ka dag chen po'i gnas lugs 'di //
NK129(to)003:3516: yang dag don gyi lta ba yin //
NK129(to)003:3517: rdzogs pa chen po chos kyi mchog /
NK129(to)003:3518: thog ma'i mgon po de la 'dud //
NK129(to)003:3520: 'di dag kyang gang zag tshig shes pas rgyud ma
NK129(to)003:3521: grol bar khengs pas khong sbos pa dang mi 'dra
NK129(to)003:3522: ste / sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po yin no //
NK129(to)003:3523: yang bod kyi slob dpon 'ga' zhig na re /
NK129(to)003:3524: gter ma rnams mi dag zhes zer na /
NK129(to)003:3525: sangs rgyas bka' bstan bcos lung man ngag rnams /
NK129(to)003:3526: rgya bod gnyis kar gter ma gtogs med pas /
NK129(to)003:3527: de'i khungs dang lo rgyus thams cad 'dir yi ge 'jigs pas /
NK129(to)003:3528: kho bo'i gter 'byung chen por blta bar bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3530: gter ma la dbang bka' dang snyan rgyud med /
NK129(to)003:3531: slob dpon pad mas sngon du gter sba thon pas bka' lung chad zer na /
NK129(to)003:3533: gu ru chen po nyid kyi dbang lung las /
NK129(to)003:3534: ma 'ongs rtog ge ba rnams kyi gter ma la bka' lung med zer na /
NK129(to)003:3536: ston pa sangs rgyas kyi bka' la yang /
NK129(to)003:3540: byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' dang bzhi ru 'du ste /
NK129(to)003:3541: de bzhin du nga'i gter la'ang de bzhi tshang ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:3542: ma 'ongs gter la spyod pa'i skyes bu rnams /
NK129(to)003:3543: da lta nga'i 'khor du yod pas /
NK129(to)003:3544: da ltar nga yi dgongs pa gtad cing byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' yang yin no //
NK129(to)003:3545: yang ma 'ongs pa na yul dang sa phyogs 'dir /
NK129(to)003:3547: lus kyi mtshan rtags yan chad bstan te /
NK129(to)003:3548: ma 'ongs chos 'di dang 'phrad par 'gyur ro zhes pas na lung du bstan pa'i bka' yang yin /
NK129(to)003:3549: ma 'ongs pa na las can cig dang 'phrad par shog ces pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3550: rang nyid nyams su 'di ltar long la gzhan la 'di ltar ston ces pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3551: rang gzhan gyi don 'di ltar 'byung zhes pa lung du bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3553: smon lam gyi brgyud pa yang tshang ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:3554: yang tshad dang ldan pa'i gter ston de la o rgyan bdag gis rab dngos /
NK129(to)003:3556: tha ma rmi lam du dbang bskur /
NK129(to)003:3558: sgrub phrin phyag bzhes dang bcas pa ston cing /
NK129(to)003:3559: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyis bka' gtad byed pas /
NK129(to)003:3560: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' yang shin tu dag pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3561: de la ma 'ongs rtogs ge ba la sogs kha cig gis /
NK129(to)003:3562: dbang dang bka' lung med do ces ci nas kyang
NK129(to)003:3563: ri dwags klung du babs pa ltar kus 'debs mi
NK129(to)003:3564: dgos / skal ldan gyi skyes bu rnams kyis sgrub rtags dang /
NK129(to)003:3565: byin rlabs khyad par gang myur legs par nyams su blangs pas gsal ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:3567: 'di yang bka' lung rig pa gsum gyis grub cing /
NK129(to)003:3568: de ltar min na rgya bod kyi gang zag dam pa rnams la /
NK129(to)003:3569: nyams dang rmi lam la sogs te dag pa'i snang bar /
NK129(to)003:3570: yi dam lhas bka' lung man ngag gdams pa'i rigs rnams gsungs shing bstan pa yang /
NK129(to)003:3571: tshad mar mi 'gro zhing mi dag par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:3572: don 'di dag mkhas pa gzu bor gnas pa rnams
NK129(to)003:3573: kyis brtags shing dpyad na mos pa'i gnas su 'gro
NK129(to)003:3574: ba yin no // yang gang zag 'jug pa'i sgos
NK129(to)003:3575: rnying ma ba'i bla ma rnams ni rang nyams su
NK129(to)003:3577: thams cad la'ang dag snang byed pa 'ba' zhig shas che ste /
NK129(to)003:3578: rtog ge ba rtsod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3579: gzhan 'geg pa kho na la ma zhugs pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3580: 'o na mkhas pa'i rig pas legs par brtags te /
NK129(to)003:3581: bka' gter gnyis ka la skyon gang la yod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3583: bka' ma las gter ma zab cing khyad par che ste /
NK129(to)003:3585: bka' ma rnams ni tshong dus kyi 'o ma dang 'dra ste bslad /
NK129(to)003:3586: 'o ma de yang dongs ba bdag gis bzhos ma thag lhad ma zhugs pas /
NK129(to)003:3587: mnan na zho 'chag dkrog na mar 'ong /
NK129(to)003:3588: 'thung na bcud yod pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3589: de yang tshong 'dus su rim par brgyud pas /
NK129(to)003:3590: cig gis 'o ma cung zad cig phris /
NK129(to)003:3592: yang de 'dra ba rim par byas pas /
NK129(to)003:3593: mthar 'o ma'i ming dang cho ma 'gyur yang /
NK129(to)003:3594: dgos pa'i byed las mi 'grub ste /
NK129(to)003:3599: bka' ma rnams la yang dang po ston pa'i bka' dang rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag /
NK129(to)003:3600: lo ts+aa bas bcos bslad med par bsgyur ba'i dus
NK129(to)003:3601: bzang po'i bka' rgyud gong ma'i dus su gdams pa
NK129(to)003:3603: byin rlabs kyi drod yod pas /
NK129(to)003:3608: bka' brgyud rnams cig bas cig bzang 'byon /
NK129(to)003:3609: phrin las rnams pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes pa byung ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:3610: de nas bod kyi bla ma rnams kyis rang bzos /
NK129(to)003:3611: sangs rgyas kyi bka' tshad ma rnams bslad /
NK129(to)003:3614: mchan dang 'grel pa mang po'i bcos bslad byas /
NK129(to)003:3616: de yang rang gi sgrub thabs mngon dkyil rnams la /
NK129(to)003:3617: rgya gar gyi bka' dri ma med pa rnams bslad nas /
NK129(to)003:3618: stod na yod pa smad na skyel /
NK129(to)003:3619: sman na yod pa stod na skyel /
NK129(to)003:3621: sul shes kyis dgongs pa byas nas bcos pa bslad mang bas /
NK129(to)003:3622: nas gseb tu phul ma btab /
NK129(to)003:3623: chos sde rnams dang ri dgon thams cad 'khrugs pa'i las byas pas /
NK129(to)003:3624: der thams cad dam tshig la khrag sha bko bo byas pas /
NK129(to)003:3625: der gong gi 'o ma bslad pa ltar /
NK129(to)003:3626: byin rlabs kyi babs so chad /
NK129(to)003:3629: rgyud la yon tan ma skyes pas rgyud dred por song /
NK129(to)003:3630: 'dod pa rang gzhan gyi don 'grub pa cig 'dod na'ang /
NK129(to)003:3631: bsod nams kyi lto gos ma phyid /
NK129(to)003:3632: chos skyong rgyab gyes pas mthu med kyi khar khas nyan 'babs /
NK129(to)003:3633: de la sogs kyi skyon du ma yod do //
NK129(to)003:3634: yang bka' la tshad ma'i gang zag med dam ces na /
NK129(to)003:3635: gang zag yon tan rtogs sgom khyad par can yang 'ga' zhig yod mod /
NK129(to)003:3636: 'o na brjod bya'i chos bslad tshul dang /
NK129(to)003:3637: yun du rnying pa'i na bab khyad par gyi yod tshul gyis bshad pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:3638: gzhan yang bod gsar 'grogs che ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3639: blo sna mang ba'i skyon gzhan yang yod de /
NK129(to)003:3641: bod kyi slob dpon rnams rgya gzhung bzang ba la nyams len dang phyag len byed mkhan med de /
NK129(to)003:3642: slob dpon res mngon dkyil sgrub thabs /
NK129(to)003:3643: rang rang gi bcos ma re kho na ma byas pa'i chos bod na med /
NK129(to)003:3644: bka' rgyud pa la sogs rdzogs rim la 'khrid pa rnams la yang /
NK129(to)003:3645: rgya gzhung sor bzhag med de /
NK129(to)003:3646: bla ma res khrid gzhung re /
NK129(to)003:3647: rang bcos du ma zhig yod pas /
NK129(to)003:3648: de rnams kyis brtsams pa tshad mar ma ldan pa
NK129(to)003:3649: rtsams pas rten 'brel gyis gnad 'chugs te grub pa
NK129(to)003:3650: thob pa nyung ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:3651: 'o na rtsom pa thams cad la mi btub bam
NK129(to)003:3652: zhe na brtsam pa po tshad dang ldan pas rtsom
NK129(to)003:3653: pa btub ste / tshad ldan gang yin zhe na /
NK129(to)003:3655: lung la 'dris shing tshad la mkhas //
NK129(to)003:3656: rang gi nyams myong man ngag ldan //
NK129(to)003:3657: yongs su shes bya'i dngos po la //
NK129(to)003:3658: tshad du phyin pas man ngag btsam //
NK129(to)003:3660: de ltar ldan na rung ba yin mod kyi /
NK129(to)003:3661: tshad de rnams dang mi ldan pa'i bod kyi slob
NK129(to)003:3662: dpon rnams rang rang gis che ba zhig kho na
NK129(to)003:3663: 'dod pa dang / gzhan dang khyad drag cig 'dod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3664: kho mkhas gdul bya kho che /
NK129(to)003:3667: zer ba zhig kho na 'dod pas /
NK129(to)003:3668: tshad dang ldan rung mi ldan rung /
NK129(to)003:3669: gzhan dang mi 'dra ba kho na zhig khyad 'don
NK129(to)003:3670: gyis bcos bslad du ma zhig byas pa 'di dag
NK129(to)003:3671: gi skyon yod pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3672: rgya gar mkhas pa'i skyes mchog rnams mi mkhas na /
NK129(to)003:3673: bod kyi blo chung rnams mi mkhas so //
NK129(to)003:3674: 'o na gter ma la zab pa'i khyad par ci yod ce na /
NK129(to)003:3675: o rgyan chen po ni sangs rgyas gnyis pa yin
NK129(to)003:3676: par lung du ma nas lung du bstan pa dang
NK129(to)003:3678: rdo rje 'chang dang dgongs pa mnyam par zhal gyis bzhes pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:3679: gsang ba 'dus pa'i spyi chings las /
NK129(to)003:3681: thos dang shes chung ma yin te //
NK129(to)003:3682: rdo rje 'chang dang dgongs pa mnyam //
NK129(to)003:3683: ces gsungs pas de lta bu'i slob dpon gyi mdzad pa yin pas na /
NK129(to)003:3684: sangs rgyas kyi bka' tshad ma /
NK129(to)003:3687: blo mang gis ma bslad pa /
NK129(to)003:3688: byin brlabs kyi rtags tshan dang ldan zhing /
NK129(to)003:3689: mkha' 'gro'i kha rlangs thu le ba /
NK129(to)003:3690: gter srung dregs pa can la gtad pas chos bdag
NK129(to)003:3691: ma yin pa gzhan gyis spyod pa'i gnas su mi
NK129(to)003:3692: 'gyur ba / las can gyi skyes bu ma yin
NK129(to)003:3693: pa la spyod pa'i dbang med de smon lam gyis
NK129(to)003:3694: 'gyur ba / 'tshams sbyar / gong gi tshong 'dus kyi 'o ma ma bslad pa ltar /
NK129(to)003:3697: phrin las rnam pa bzhi lag len la khel /
NK129(to)003:3700: chos skyong bran bzhin du nyan /
NK129(to)003:3705: de lta bu'i khyad par yod de /
NK129(to)003:3706: sgra dge bshes che yang nus pa sngags pas thon /
NK129(to)003:3707: nga rgyal rtog ge pa che yang /
NK129(to)003:3708: grub rtags sgom chen pas thon /
NK129(to)003:3710: ya gi sangs rgyas bsgrub pa nas /
NK129(to)003:3711: bstan pa'i ched du mthu gtad ser gsum rnams la lag len du khel zhing nus pa thon pa /
NK129(to)003:3713: nged gu ru pad+ma'i gter chos la spyod pa rnams gang zag nus pa gang gis thon kyang /
NK129(to)003:3714: gsar rnying gnyis ka la mos pa'i gang zag drang
NK129(to)003:3715: por gnas pa rnams kyis gzigs pas gsal ba yin
NK129(to)003:3716: no // yang gsar ma khas len pa'i mtshan nyid pa la sogs phyogs dregs can rnams na re /
NK129(to)003:3717: rnying ma ba zer ba'i sgom chen pa 'di tshogs sde snod kyi bshad pa mi shes /
NK129(to)003:3718: grub matha'i gshag ral mi phyed /
NK129(to)003:3719: ci yang mi shes pa'i rmongs pa gti mug pa cig yin no //
NK129(to)003:3720: zhes zer ba yang mi rigs te /
NK129(to)003:3721: gang zag dam pa sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i thabs la
NK129(to)003:3722: nyams su blangs pas nyams su grol ba zhig yin
NK129(to)003:3723: mod / bsgom pas 'khrul pa ma zhig na /
NK129(to)003:3724: tshig dang go bas sangs mi rgya ste /
NK129(to)003:3726: ba glang mig rjes chu dang rgya mtsho bzhin //
NK129(to)003:3727: yun ring byas dka' med par gang bsgrub pa //
NK129(to)003:3728: de ni nges par dpal chen bcom ldan 'das //
NK129(to)003:3729: de yii'i yang sprul 'di nas zas gtsang sras //
NK129(to)003:3730: sman pa bya ka'i yul du mngon par ston //
NK129(to)003:3731: phyogs bcu'i zhing gi rdul rnyed dge slong mchog /
NK129(to)003:3732: grangs med bskal par rab tu mchod pa bas //
NK129(to)003:3733: sngags mos cig tsam rab tu mchod byas pa //
NK129(to)003:3734: phul byung rdo rje theg pa nges pa nyid //
NK129(to)003:3737: tshigs gis khengs pa klu'i gdengs ka bzhin //
NK129(to)003:3738: 'chad dang nyan pa po dag mi grol te //
NK129(to)003:3739: slar yang nga rgyal dag gis rab gzir zhing //
NK129(to)003:3740: nges par ngu 'bod gnas su phyin pa nyid //
NK129(to)003:3741: zab mo'i don gang tshig gis mi rtogs te //
NK129(to)003:3742: rtogs su rung na mkhas pa khyod ji ltar //
NK129(to)003:3743: tshig bral don ni rtogs zhes gang smra ba //
NK129(to)003:3744: de dag rtog ge mthar zhen yun ring 'khor //
NK129(to)003:3747: theg pa'i bye brag shes na shes pa tsam mo bu //
NK129(to)003:3748: du ma ro gcig shes na mkhas pa yin no bu //
NK129(to)003:3750: chos la phyogs ris byas na nyan thos lam mo bu //
NK129(to)003:3753: bshad pa'i tshig rnams nam mkha'i mtha' dang 'dra //
NK129(to)003:3754: bshad pa'i don la phyogs mthar thug pa med //
NK129(to)003:3755: 'du shes ma zad rtog pa'i yo langs yin //
NK129(to)003:3756: shes pa'i nga rgyal 'khrul pa mi 'jigs shing //
NK129(to)003:3757: de bas gnas lugs nang du gang 'jog pa //
NK129(to)003:3758: 'di ni skyes chen thar pa'i lam du 'jug /
NK129(to)003:3761: shes pa'i tshig dang rtogs dpyod blos //
NK129(to)003:3762: kun rdzob lus kyi de nyid min //
NK129(to)003:3763: stong pa'i sems ni ji ltar rtogs //
NK129(to)003:3764: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi dgongs pa ltar /
NK129(to)003:3766: kun shes cig rdug gi rigs 'ong bas /
NK129(to)003:3767: dpe cha thog cig blor tshud /
NK129(to)003:3770: gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa ma dag na blo 'das kyi rtogs pa rgyud la mi skye bas /
NK129(to)003:3771: de tsam gyis rang mthong dang sbos pa mi 'tshal /
NK129(to)003:3772: sngon sbyangs gyi las sad pa'i skyes bu /
NK129(to)003:3775: nang gi dgongs pa mi rtogs /
NK129(to)003:3776: zas khyi phag gi lto ltar za /
NK129(to)003:3777: gos khyi thul dug po gyon /
NK129(to)003:3778: mdzad spyod smyon pa ltar byas nas /
NK129(to)003:3779: nam zhig lus sems bral ba'i tshe /
NK129(to)003:3781: 'ja' dang 'od du na re byung ba la grangs med /
NK129(to)003:3782: yang phyi tshul gzugs kyi dge bshes /
NK129(to)003:3784: nang sha mar dang jas brgyad /
NK129(to)003:3785: phyi tshul bag ma bas mkhas pa /
NK129(to)003:3786: khas thams cad mkhyen par khas blangs nas /
NK129(to)003:3787: nam zhig bems rig bral dus drod rtags 'byin re ba mang po yod /
NK129(to)003:3789: cig gis cig smad pa'i chos spang gis las dang /
NK129(to)003:3790: chags sdang phyogs dred rang rgyud ngan pa'i mngon rtags 'di mi 'thad pas /
NK129(to)003:3791: rang rang gi sngon gyi las kyi 'phro dang /
NK129(to)003:3792: bag chags kyis mtshams sbyor bas /
NK129(to)003:3794: rang gang mos kyi chos de tshul bzhin du nyams su blangs /
NK129(to)003:3795: dag snang phyogs med mi sbyong na yang chos spang dang log lta mi bya /
NK129(to)003:3796: thar pa bsgrub pa'i rang gzhung so so na zab /
NK129(to)003:3797: pho rgod po yod na tshe 'dir bstan pa dang sems can la phan thogs /
NK129(to)003:3798: phyi ma thar pa'i lam 'thob pa zhig bgyid 'tshal /
NK129(to)003:3799: rnying ma chos min kyang gsar ma bas mi khegs /
NK129(to)003:3800: gsar ma chos min kyang rnying ma bas mi khegs kyi /
NK129(to)003:3801: gzhan gyi chos la ma dag pa byed pa bas /
NK129(to)003:3802: rang gis dag par bsgom pa la 'bras bu thob pa re bgyid 'tshal /
NK129(to)003:3803: 'o na yang slob dpon kha cig gi yid la /
NK129(to)003:3804: gter ston rat+na gling pa de /
NK129(to)003:3805: gsar ma dang mtshan nyid pa la brnag pa zhig yin nam zer na /
NK129(to)003:3815: bod kyi khrod na rdzogs rim phal che ba zhig kho bos ma zhus pa yang med de /
NK129(to)003:3816: thad ka'i yon tan kyang rgyud la skyes pa yod /
NK129(to)003:3817: mtshan nyid kyi chos 'di dag kyang /
NK129(to)003:3818: ston pa'i bka' la brten nas /
NK129(to)003:3819: bstan bcos sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'dzin skyong /
NK129(to)003:3820: bstan pa yun du gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:3821: rgya bod kyi gang zag dam pa rnams kyis mdzad pa yin pa shin tu yang dgos la /
NK129(to)003:3822: phyi thos pa sgro 'dog gcod pa /
NK129(to)003:3823: nang bsgom pas rang rgyud grol ba /
NK129(to)003:3824: rang gzhan dang bstan pa la phan pa'i rgyur gyur pa zhig la /
NK129(to)003:3825: kho bo yang shin tu mos shing dad la /
NK129(to)003:3826: dag snang dang nges pa'i shes pa dang bcas pa yod do //
NK129(to)003:3827: de ltar rgyas par bshad nas /
NK129(to)003:3828: rtsod pa bzlog pa mdor bsdu na /
NK129(to)003:3829: rnying ma la ma dag zhes pa'i khas len mi btub pa'i gnad chen po yod de /
NK129(to)003:3831: rgyal blon snga dar ba'i dus su sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba b+aee ro tsa na dang /
NK129(to)003:3832: ka cog la sogs pa rnams kyis sde snod gsum
NK129(to)003:3833: la sogs pa'i bka' bstan bcos du ma cig bsgyur
NK129(to)003:3834: ba yin cing / de dag la rgya gar na khungs med /
NK129(to)003:3835: bsam yas su bsgyur ba mi dag zer ba'i rtsod pa ni med /
NK129(to)003:3836: des na sngags rnying ma'i rgyud man ngag rnams kyang dus der bsgyur ba yin pas /
NK129(to)003:3837: des na sde snod gsum la sogs pa 'di dag rnams dag na ni /
NK129(to)003:3838: rnying ma rnams kyang dag dgos la /
NK129(to)003:3839: rnying ma mi dag na ni sde snod gsum la sogs pa 'di rnams kyang mi dag par thal /
NK129(to)003:3843: zhang ban+de ye shes sde la sogs pa'i bsgyur mkhan gyis lo ts+aa ba rnams gcig pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)003:3844: yang b+aee ro tsa na la sogs pa sprul pa'i
NK129(to)003:3845: lo ts+aa ba rnams kyi sde snod gsum la sogs
NK129(to)003:3846: pa rnams dag par shes la /
NK129(to)003:3847: rnying ma'i rgyud rnam ma dag ngo ma shes zer ba'i lung rigs pa yang mi 'thad las che /
NK129(to)003:3848: mkhas pa rnams kyis ni dgongs pa 'dis kyang len par 'os so //
NK129(to)003:3849: lar yang gsar ma ba dang rnying ma ba gnyis kha bdag bzang ngan gyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)003:3850: chags sdang la rus 'don mi 'don dang /
NK129(to)003:3851: grangs dpung mang nyung gis kyang khyad par 'byed 'dra bar song ba yin /
NK129(to)003:3853: gsar rnying gnyis 'gyur snga phyi go log nas /
NK129(to)003:3854: rnying ma ba la ma dag pa'i 'brel mthar 'dzin rang byed pa'i tshod du yang snang /
NK129(to)003:3855: de gang yin na rnying ma 'di ma dag ces pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3856: slob dpon rnams kyis bcos pa yin no zer ba dag yod de /
NK129(to)003:3857: rnying ma rnams rgyal blon snga dar /
NK129(to)003:3858: bstan pa grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:3859: dpag bsam gyi shing sdong rtsa ba brtan zug /
NK129(to)003:3862: 'bras bu dus su smin pa yin cing /
NK129(to)003:3863: gsar ma'i brjod byas bod du gtam ma grags pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:3864: rig 'dzin gru thob nam mkha'i skar ma tsam byon te /
NK129(to)003:3865: yer pa'i grub thob 'od lus grub pa brgyad cu /
NK129(to)003:3866: mchim phu'i grub chen nyer lnga /
NK129(to)003:3867: bka' babs kyi rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK129(to)003:3868: thugs sras snying gi bu dgu /
NK129(to)003:3869: sa thob pa'i sngags pa phreng thog brgya /
NK129(to)003:3870: smon lam btab pa'i phyir mi ldog gi sbyin bdag
NK129(to)003:3871: brgya la sogs pa rgyal po bka'i tshom chen mo
NK129(to)003:3874: b+ai ma la mi tra dang /
NK129(to)003:3876: sangs rgyas gsang ba la sogs pa rnams kyi mngon
NK129(to)003:3877: slob kho na la yang grub thob de tsam zhig
NK129(to)003:3878: byon cing / gzhan yang grangs su ma smos pa'i
NK129(to)003:3879: gang zag dam pa nam mkha'i skar ma tsam zhig
NK129(to)003:3880: byon cing / byon te / chos kyi zab rgya gtan la phab /
NK129(to)003:3881: nyams len gyi grub rtags mtha' ru phyin /
NK129(to)003:3882: grub thob tsha tsha btab pa bzhin byung ba lags te /
NK129(to)003:3887: thos sar thob pa'i bka' rgyud dag lags pas /
NK129(to)003:3888: 'di la bkag par 'dod pa'i gnas su ci byas kyang /
NK129(to)003:3889: rtse mo bas rtsa ba snga ba dang /
NK129(to)003:3890: bu las pha rgan pa'i dpe ltar du /
NK129(to)003:3892: dregs pas kun nas bslangs pa'i glan gtam dang phyogs bzos 'gro ba'i skabs med cing /
NK129(to)003:3893: 'di la yang gtan tshig 'di bden pa'i gnas yin nam ma yin mkhas pas brtags par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3894: gal te 'di gnyis go log ste /
NK129(to)003:3895: gsar ma sngon du 'gyur ba zhig yin na ni /
NK129(to)003:3896: gsar ma rnams kyis ni nged gsar ma'i chos la brtsams gdan byas nas /
NK129(to)003:3897: bod kyi sngags sgom rnams kyis rang bzo dang sgra bcos byas pa yin /
NK129(to)003:3898: nged kyis gsar ma tsho 'gyur dus na sbyin bdag chos rgyal mes dbon rnam gsum /
NK129(to)003:3899: lo ts+aa ba b+aee ro dang ka cog gsum /
NK129(to)003:3900: rgya gar gyi slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK129(to)003:3904: rgya gar gyi rig 'dzin brgyad lta bu'i zhal nas bsgyur /
NK129(to)003:3905: phyag rten gser phye bre la 'jal te /
NK129(to)003:3906: bstan pa snga dar ba'i ring la bsgyur ba yin /
NK129(to)003:3907: zhes zer ba'i lab ni khong tsho la gtong rgyu med /
NK129(to)003:3908: gsar ma'i lo ts+aa ba bya ba rgya gar shar phyogs su phyin pa yang med /
NK129(to)003:3909: bal por yug re phyin nas /
NK129(to)003:3910: nged gsar ma'i chos la rang bzo dang 'dra chos
NK129(to)003:3911: byas pa yin no zhes kha bdag bzang pos 'geg
NK129(to)003:3912: par thag gcod nges par 'dug ste /
NK129(to)003:3913: smra rgyu ma rnyed pa'i brjod byas /
NK129(to)003:3914: lce ma zad na shag mi 'dzad ces zer ba'i dpe dang mtshungs par /
NK129(to)003:3915: rnying ma la skyon tshol ba'i thabs ma byung ba yin no //
NK129(to)003:3916: de bas na ma dag pas dag pa sun 'byin pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3917: pha wong gis ri phul pa'i dpe ltar /
NK129(to)003:3918: phyogs snga dang chos spang gi gang ma la yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)003:3919: rang gzhan la phan pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)003:3920: bstan pa'i zhabs tog tu mi 'gyur bas kun la dag snang bya /
NK129(to)003:3921: gang mos la nyams len rtse gcig tu dril /
NK129(to)003:3922: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gru bzhi ru btegs /
NK129(to)003:3923: chos shes na rang rgyud thul /
NK129(to)003:3924: mi lus lan gcig po 'di skyes pa don dang ldan par bya'o //
NK129(to)003:3925: spyi don drug pa chos spyi'i rnam bzhag mdor bsdus te bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3926: de yang ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK129(to)003:3927: rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i chos thams cad bzhir 'du ste
NK129(to)003:3932: zhal nas gsungs pa la gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:3933: ston pas rang shugs su gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3934: 'khor rnams kyis zhus te gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3936: ston pas rang shugs su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3937: 'phags pa sdud pa lta bu ste /
NK129(to)003:3938: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor bzhi po de
NK129(to)003:3939: dag yang dag par rab tu dga' bar mdzad pa'i
NK129(to)003:3940: phyir / yang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di ston cing /
NK129(to)003:3941: de'i tshe tshigs bcad pa 'di dag bka' stsal to //
NK129(to)003:3943: 'khor gyis zhus te gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3945: glur blangs gang lags bshad du gsol //
NK129(to)003:3947: skabs la gleng bslangs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3948: khye'u tshangs pa'i dpal lung bstan pa lta bu ste /
NK129(to)003:3949: rtsed mo byas te sa la ri mo bris pa'i khang pa bcon ldan 'das la phul te /
NK129(to)003:3950: bdag gis 'di tshogs rdzogs par mdzad du gsol zhes zhus pa la /
NK129(to)003:3951: ston pas sngon gyi gling bslangs te /
NK129(to)003:3952: khye'u'i skyes rabs mtha' rgyas su lung bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:3953: byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' la'ang gsum ste /
NK129(to)003:3954: skus byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3955: bcom ldan 'das kyis dpal rdo rje snying po'i spyi
NK129(to)003:3956: bor phyag glang po che'i sna lta bu bzhag nas
NK129(to)003:3957: byin gyis rlabs te chos gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:3958: gsung gis byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' ni /
NK129(to)003:3960: rab 'byor khyod shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spobs par byos shig /
NK129(to)003:3962: thugs kyis byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3963: bcom ldan 'das zab mo snang ba zhes bya ba'i
NK129(to)003:3964: ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs nas spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK129(to)003:3966: gang byin gyis rlabs na don gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:3967: sems kyi rgyud dang ma 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3968: sems kyi rgyud dang 'brel par byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:3969: dang po ni thub pa bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)003:3970: ston pa'i byin rlabs kyis bems po la yang chos kyi sgra 'byung ste /
NK129(to)003:3972: khams dang gzug ni dngas pa dang //
NK129(to)003:3973: nam mkha' la yang chos kyi sgra //
NK129(to)003:3976: ston pa dga' ldan gnas su ni /
NK129(to)003:3977: ri dang shing bu rde'u dang /
NK129(to)003:3978: rnga bo che dang pad+ma las /
NK129(to)003:3979: sgra byung ba ni bka' zhes brjod //
NK129(to)003:3981: sems kyi rgyud dang 'brel par byin gyis rlabs pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:3982: sems can gyi sems dang 'brel par byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:3983: 'phags pa'i thugs dang 'brel par byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:3984: dang po ni thub pa zhal bzhugs pa'i dus su
NK129(to)003:3985: ni dud 'gro la sogs sems can phal pas kyang
NK129(to)003:3987: za ma tog bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK129(to)003:3988: thub pa khyod kyi byin rlabs las /
NK129(to)003:3989: sems can rnams kyis chos sgra sgrog /
NK129(to)003:3991: 'phags pa'i thugs dang 'brel par byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)003:3993: rgyal ba'i nyan thos pa dag ji snyed chos ston dang //
NK129(to)003:3994: 'chad dang rig pa dag dang ldan par brjod pa dang //
NK129(to)003:3995: mchog 'phags bde ba byed dang de yi'i 'bras thob pa //
NK129(to)003:3996: de dag kun kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i skyes bu'i mthu //
NK129(to)003:3998: sangs rgyas mthus byed rang gi stobs kyi mthus ma yin //
NK129(to)003:4000: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' la gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:4001: gsung gcig pa rjes su gnang ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4002: bsdus gcig par rjes su gnang ba'o //
NK129(to)003:4003: dang po ni thub pas 'khor rnams la shod cig ces pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4004: mo'u mgal gyi bus sh+aakya'i gdung rabs bshad pa lta bu dang /
NK129(to)003:4005: ji ltar khyod kyi bstan pa de bzhin du shes
NK129(to)003:4006: rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa zab mo la
NK129(to)003:4007: bslab par bya'o // zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:4008: bsdu ba par rjes su gnang ba ni /
NK129(to)003:4009: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK129(to)003:4010: zhes pa chos thams cad kyi dbu ru byung /
NK129(to)003:4011: gsung pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK129(to)003:4012: ces pa chos thams cad kyi zhabs su gyis shig ces pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:4013: lung du bstan pa'i bka' la gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:4014: gnas skabs su bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4016: gnas skabs su lung bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)003:4017: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'di nas shar phyogs na sangs
NK129(to)003:4018: kyi zhing me tog bkram pa zhes bya ba na
NK129(to)003:4019: / byang chub sems dpa' 'di dang 'di zhes bya ba la /
NK129(to)003:4020: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje snying po zhes bya bas chos ston to //
NK129(to)003:4021: de'i 'khor de dag kyang myur du 'dir 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:4023: 'gro ba 'di dang 'di gnas 'phos te zhing 'dir skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:4024: zhes pa la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:4025: mtha' thug tu bstan pa la nye bar lung bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4026: dus ring por lung du bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4027: nye bar lung bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)003:4028: dge slong dag ston pa'i dam chos ni byang phyogs nas byang phyogs su rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:4031: 'phags pa'i rigs can dpag med kyis //
NK129(to)003:4032: ston pa'i bstan pa rgyas par byed //
NK129(to)003:4035: lo ni bzhi brgya lon pa na /
NK129(to)003:4036: ces slob dpon 'phags pa lung bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:4037: dus ring du lung bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)003:4038: sring mo gang g+aa'i lha mo 'di ma 'ongs pa na sangs rgyas 'di zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)003:4040: de ltar ston pa'i bka' rnams bsdu na bka' bzhi po der 'du ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:4041: de'ang bka' dang bstan bcos rnams kyi rnam par bzhag pa gang la bya na /
NK129(to)003:4043: ston pa mya ngan las ma 'das phan du gsungs pa thams cad ni bka'/
NK129(to)003:4044: mya ngan las 'das tshun chad ni bstan bcos yin zer /
NK129(to)003:4046: ston pas gsungs pa thams cad bka'/
NK129(to)003:4047: gang zag gis gsungs pa thams cad bstan bcos zer ba'ang yod /
NK129(to)003:4048: de dag kyang bka' la brten nas bstan bcos byung bas 'gal ba med cing /
NK129(to)003:4049: de bas kyang kho bo ni 'di ltar 'dod do //
NK129(to)003:4050: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi zhal nas gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4053: rjes su gnang ba'i chos sgrar snang ba /
NK129(to)003:4055: sgra don gyi 'brel pa'i brjod bya thams cad la bka' zhes bya /
NK129(to)003:4056: bka'i don la brten kyang rung /
NK129(to)003:4059: 'phags pa dang gang zag gis mdzad pa sgrar snang ba /
NK129(to)003:4061: sgra don gyi 'brel pa'i brjod bya thams cad la bstan bcos zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)003:4064: bka' dang bstan bcos lung rigs rnams sgra grags sgra'i
NK129(to)003:4065: don gyi 'brel pa gsum tshang ba bka' dang bstan
NK129(to)003:4067: de yang bstan pa'i chos la sde snod gnyis su bshad de /
NK129(to)003:4069: ma nor ba'i lam nyid dang /
NK129(to)003:4070: lam la slob pa de nyid de /
NK129(to)003:4071: lta ba phyi nang gnyis yin no //
NK129(to)003:4073: phyi pa mu stegs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4074: nang pa sangs rgyas pa gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:4075: phyi pa mu stegs pa'i chos la lta log sum
NK129(to)003:4076: brgya drug cu la sogs 'jigs tshogs kyi chos dbye
NK129(to)003:4077: na mang du yod de 'dir ma spros /
NK129(to)003:4078: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i chos la nye bar bsdu na gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK129(to)003:4089: ngo bo ni chos kyi bdag tu lta ba'i sgo nas rang gis zhi dul bsgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4092: nyan nyan thos shing thos thos grol //
NK129(to)003:4095: nyan thos sprul pa ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4099: sprul pa ni sh+aa ri'i bu dang /
NK129(to)003:4101: rab 'byor la sogs pa mchog brgyad po lta bu'o //
NK129(to)003:4102: 'di dag ni dngos su theg pa chen po la gnas kyang /
NK129(to)003:4103: nyan thos kyis tshul bzung nas nyan thos kyi don byed pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4105: theg pa chen po la dngas zhing skur pa 'debs pa /
NK129(to)003:4107: de las gyes pa'i sde pa bco brgyad pa rnams so //
NK129(to)003:4110: thams cad yod smra'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4112: mang pos bskur ba'i sde dang bzhi'o //
NK129(to)003:4113: de las gyes pa'i sde ni /
NK129(to)003:4114: shar gyi ri bo'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4115: nub kyi ri bo'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4117: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i smra ba'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4118: rtag par smra ba'i sde dang lngar gyes so //
NK129(to)003:4119: yod par smra ba'i sde la'ang /
NK129(to)003:4120: gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4121: de bzhin du 'od srungs sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4124: mang du thos pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4126: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde dang bdun no //
NK129(to)003:4127: gsum pa gnas brtan pa'i sde la yang /
NK129(to)003:4128: rgyal byed tshal gnas kyi sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4130: gtsug lang khang chen sde dang gsum du gyes so //
NK129(to)003:4131: bzhi pa ni mang pos bkur ba'i sde la yang /
NK129(to)003:4132: sa gro rig pa'i sde dang /
NK129(to)003:4134: gnas ma bu'i sde dang gsum du gyes so //
NK129(to)003:4136: 'gog pa la snyoms par zhugs pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4137: rten gyi gang zag 'phags pa'i dgag bya ni /
NK129(to)003:4138: rnam shes tshogs bdun 'khor bcas dgag pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4140: rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs 'byung dang lugs bzlog tu
NK129(to)003:4141: shes pas rang gis de nyid thob pa la sogs
NK129(to)003:4143: lta ba sgom pa spyod pa 'bras bu la sogs pa rang rang gi 'jug pa'i sgo /
NK129(to)003:4144: rtogs pa'i lta ba sgom pa'i nyams /
NK129(to)003:4145: mthar 'dod pa'i 'bras bu la sogs pa rim par phye na mang du yod de /
NK129(to)003:4146: yi ge 'jigs pas don mdor bsdus pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:4147: de yang dka' bas lam du 'jug pa la /
NK129(to)003:4148: phyi pa dang nang pa'i khyad par gang zhe na /
NK129(to)003:4149: rdo rje snying po'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:4150: bstan pa gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)003:4151: mu stegs rtag dang chad pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4152: rgyang 'phen dang ni mur thug go //
NK129(to)003:4153: stong dang snying rje mi phyed dang /
NK129(to)003:4156: mu stegs kyi ston pa la mtshan dang dpe byad rnams kyang med /
NK129(to)003:4157: nang pa'i ston pa la mtshan dang dpe byad brgyad cu la sogs pas brgyan pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4158: phyi rol pa'i lta log sum brgya drug cu yang zung 'jug med de /
NK129(to)003:4159: rtag pa dang chad pa phyogs re ba kho na'o //
NK129(to)003:4160: nang pa ni bdag med pa gnyis dang /
NK129(to)003:4161: rtag chad phyogs lhung bral ba'o //
NK129(to)003:4162: phyi rol pa'i spyod pa yang me lnga pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4163: dbugs gsum la sogs pa byed cing /
NK129(to)003:4164: nang pa ni pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK129(to)003:4165: dge ba'i rtsa ba bcu spyod pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4166: rig ni sdom pa rnams la spyod pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4167: yang tri sin du a pa ta ra'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)003:4168: bstan dang ston pa rtogs dpyod tshul bltas dang //
NK129(to)003:4169: chos rtag bzhi dang bshad pa khyad par che //
NK129(to)003:4171: phyi pa ni ston pa gsum dang /
NK129(to)003:4172: ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug la bsten cing /
NK129(to)003:4173: nang pa ni skyabs dkon mchog gsum la brten pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4174: ston pa yang mu stegs rang rtog drug tu 'dod cing /
NK129(to)003:4175: nang pa ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig par 'dod do //
NK129(to)003:4177: mu stegs pas rtag pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4178: chad pa gnyis rang rgyud so sor 'dod la /
NK129(to)003:4179: sangs rgyas pa ni rang bzhin du bdag med par 'dod pas khyad par che ste /
NK129(to)003:4182: zung du 'jug pa la sogs pa'i khyad par du che ba'o //
NK129(to)003:4184: phyi pa ni bya khyi'i dka' thub bam /
NK129(to)003:4185: mi dge ba bcu la spyod /
NK129(to)003:4186: nang pas byams snying rje dang tshogs gnyis dge ba bcu la spyod de /
NK129(to)003:4189: skye 'jig tha dad dang bral ba rtag /
NK129(to)003:4190: gnod pa thams cad dang bral bas bde /
NK129(to)003:4191: thams cad rang la grub pas bdag /
NK129(to)003:4192: glo bur dri mas ma gos gtsang /
NK129(to)003:4195: mi rtag sdug bsngal nyon mongs bcas //
NK129(to)003:4196: de nyid ngo shes zung du bral //
NK129(to)003:4199: phyi pa ni ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug lha mi'i dbang po 'dod ces /
NK129(to)003:4200: nang pa ni mya ngan las 'das pa sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid 'dod de /
NK129(to)003:4201: de dag ni phyi nang gi rnam bzhag mdo tsam bstan pa yin /
NK129(to)003:4202: de la khyad par che ba nang pa rang la'ang che chung gnyis de /
NK129(to)003:4204: shes rab dang snying rje che bas theg pa chen po la /
NK129(to)003:4205: de nyid chung bas na theg pa chung ngu'o //
NK129(to)003:4206: de yang snying rje sems bskyed chen por dmigs shing /
NK129(to)003:4207: shes rab chos kyi dbyings su khyab pas chen po'o //
NK129(to)003:4208: rang don gtso bor gol zhing chos kyi de nyid ma rtogs pas chung ngu'o //
NK129(to)003:4209: yang theg chung shes rab chung bas gang zag gi bdag las chos kyis bdag ma rtogs /
NK129(to)003:4210: snying rje chung ste sems can la bdag las gces pa'i sems bskyed ma slong /
NK129(to)003:4211: theg chen ni shes rab che ste gang zag gi steng du chos kyi bdag med rtogs /
NK129(to)003:4212: snying rje che ste chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK129(to)003:4213: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje dang ldan no //
NK129(to)003:4214: khyad par bsdu na theg pa chen po ni /
NK129(to)003:4215: theg chung las dpag pa bdun gyi che ste /
NK129(to)003:4216: mi rtogs pa'i don la dmigs pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:4217: zab cing rgya che bar dmigs /
NK129(to)003:4219: rang don las gzhan don bsgrub /
NK129(to)003:4220: gang zag gis bdag med pas /
NK129(to)003:4221: chos kyi bdag med mngon du gyur /
NK129(to)003:4222: thabs che ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i sar phyin /
NK129(to)003:4223: brtson 'grus che ba ni sdug bsngal gyis spyod nas /
NK129(to)003:4224: rang don mi bsgrub bar gzhan gyi sdug bsngal mthong bas brtson 'grus kyis dang du len /
NK129(to)003:4225: las che ba ni rang don zhi bde mi bsgrub ste /
NK129(to)003:4226: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa mthar 'don /
NK129(to)003:4227: yang dag pa'i bsgrub pas che ba ni 'phags pa dang dgra bcom pa 'dod pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:4228: sangs rgyas kyis stobs dang mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4229: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4232: gtong ba che dang blo che ba dang mthu che dang //
NK129(to)003:4233: rgyal ba rnams kyi theg chen mchog la zhugs pa dang //
NK129(to)003:4234: go cha chen po bgos shing bdud kyi sgyu 'dul ba //
NK129(to)003:4235: de yi phyir na theg pa che zhes rab tu brjod //
NK129(to)003:4237: ci phyir 'di ni byang chub theg chen bya zhe na /
NK129(to)003:4238: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan zlo /
NK129(to)003:4239: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te /
NK129(to)003:4240: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK129(to)003:4242: de dag gi ni theg pa'i khyad par dang /
NK129(to)003:4243: thun mong gi rnam bzhag kyang mdor bstan pa yin no //
NK129(to)003:4244: spyi don bdun gyi tha ma bstan bcos 'di nyid ji ltar brtsam zhing don du 'gyur ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4245: bstan pa spyi'i rnam par bzhag pa yin pas kun gyis tshad mar rig pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4246: mjug dge rtsa smon lam bkra shis pa'i mtha' rgyas
NK129(to)003:4247: dang bcas pa bstan pa dang gang zag la phan
NK129(to)003:4249: dang po ji ltar brtsam pa ni /
NK129(to)003:4250: gtso bor rgyal ba'i bka' dang /
NK129(to)003:4253: rang gis thos pa'i rgya bskyed de /
NK129(to)003:4254: lung rigs kyi 'jug pa rnams kyis gtan la phab pas te /
NK129(to)003:4255: bstan bcos stod smad bar gsum du mi 'gal ba'i dbang po mi 'gyur ba'i gzer /
NK129(to)003:4256: mkhas pa'i lung rigs kyis legs par grub pa rnams yin no //
NK129(to)003:4257: don du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK129(to)003:4258: gang zag rtog ge ba'i rigs la sogs te /
NK129(to)003:4260: yang lung ma bstan gtam 'chol phyogs 'chas su smra ba mang po yod de /
NK129(to)003:4261: de dag ni dper na khyi rgan gcig gis tho la mir bzung nas 'khang pas /
NK129(to)003:4262: gang yin med par khyi thams cad phyogs su zugs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4263: bong bu g.yang la phul na mdo ru 'gro ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4265: lug sngon ma gcig gis mchong na /
NK129(to)003:4266: 'chi ngo shes pa'i chu dong du kun mchong ba ltar /
NK129(to)003:4267: rdzogs chen gyi chos byang bu bcur 'brel gcig bltas
NK129(to)003:4268: pa dang rtogs dpyod byed ma myong ba'i ban d+he
NK129(to)003:4270: phyogs gtam khol 'dod du smra zhing /
NK129(to)003:4271: rnying ma chos ma dag go zhes smra bas /
NK129(to)003:4272: de dag gis mthong na yang /
NK129(to)003:4274: mos pa mi ster kyang rgyu mtshan shes shing gting yid ches pa'i rgyur 'gyur la /
NK129(to)003:4275: gang gi kyang dag pa mi ster na ni /
NK129(to)003:4276: gong gi dpe rnams dang mtshungs pas /
NK129(to)003:4277: sangs rgyas la yang legs pa'i skar mas dag pa ma byin pa dang 'dra'o //
NK129(to)003:4278: yang rdzogs pa chen po rnying ma la mos pa'i gang zag rnams kyis mthong na ni /
NK129(to)003:4279: nges pa'i shes pa khyad par can dang /
NK129(to)003:4280: sa thob pa'i dga' ba lta bu sgom par rigs so //
NK129(to)003:4281: gnyis pa kun gyis tshad mar rigs shing /
NK129(to)003:4282: rang 'dod phyogs gcig gi chos 'di'i che ba khol phyung su bshad pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)003:4283: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de nyid /
NK129(to)003:4284: phyi dang nang gsang ba gsum gyi lha mi'i ston par ji ltar byon pa'i tshul gyis khog phub /
NK129(to)003:4285: bka' bstan bcos kyi rnam bzhag /
NK129(to)003:4286: rgya bod kyi 'brel tshul chos rang rang gi spyi dang rang rang gi mtshan nyid /
NK129(to)003:4287: rgyal ba'i bka' dang lung gis 'gal med du bsgrub nas bstan pa yin te /
NK129(to)003:4288: legs par brtags shing dpyad na /
NK129(to)003:4289: ma dag par 'dzin pa rnams dag phyogs su yid 'dren pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4290: mos par gnas pa rnams mi phyed pa'i dad pa thob pas /
NK129(to)003:4291: kun gyis spyi mthun du bstan pa'i rnam dbye /
NK129(to)003:4292: shing rta chen po'i srol du 'gro ba kun gyi e ma ho /
NK129(to)003:4293: a la la ho zhes smra ba brjod par rigs so //
NK129(to)003:4294: gsum pa 'jug dge rtsa smon lam gyis ji ltar bsngo ba ni /
NK129(to)003:4295: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gnyis te /
NK129(to)003:4296: gnas skabs su sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa /
NK129(to)003:4297: mdo sngags gsar rnying bka' gter thams cad la phan pa'i rgyur gyur pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4298: gang zag ma rtogs pa ma rig pa'i dbang du bsgribs pa rnams gsal ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4299: rtogs pa can rnams yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba dang /
NK129(to)003:4300: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa mnyam yangs sgor mor gnas pa la /
NK129(to)003:4301: phyogs 'dzin gyi 'dod pas zla khams su mi byed cing /
NK129(to)003:4302: thams cad la sgo du ma nas phan pa'i rgyur bsngo ba yin cing /
NK129(to)003:4304: spyir snying po can gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba mtha' dag dang /
NK129(to)003:4305: khyad par du pha mas gtsor byas drin gyis bskyangs pa dang /
NK129(to)003:4306: gdul byar gyur pa rnams sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK129(to)003:4307: 'dzin skyong srung ba la sogs khur du che zhing
NK129(to)003:4308: / gol 'chugs med pa'i lam mchog /'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i theg par zhugs te /
NK129(to)003:4309: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag nyid chen po
NK129(to)003:4310: sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid thob par bsngo
NK129(to)003:4311: ba'o // 'di ni bstan pa'i srog shing /
NK129(to)003:4312: thun mong gi chos 'byung don spyi dang rang rang
NK129(to)003:4313: gi mtshan nyid rnams ma 'dres so sor bstan na
NK129(to)003:4314: / ngo bo dbyer med gcig tu don bsdus pa yin pas /
NK129(to)003:4315: dgos 'dod kun 'byung yid bzhin nor bu lta bu bstan pa'i skabs tha ma ste bdun pa'o //
NK129(to)003:4316: blo gros mtha' yas dbang po'i gzhu yi rab brgyan cing //
NK129(to)003:4317: shes bya'i gnas la ma rmongs pa yis shes rab mda' //
NK129(to)003:4318: blo gros blo gsal skyes bu'i yid la rab tu 'phen //
NK129(to)003:4319: yid kyi dga' ston gzhon nu'i brtse ba'i rgyan du 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:4320: sprin bral mkha' la nyi shar ji bzhin 'od stong ni //
NK129(to)003:4321: 'gro ba'i 'dul zhing gling bzhi kun tu khyab che bar //
NK129(to)003:4322: ma rig mun sel shes bya'i snang ba rgyas par gyur //
NK129(to)003:4323: rig pa'i gzhon nu bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan phyogs bcur 'phyar //
NK129(to)003:4324: shes bya'i mkha' la 'dod dgu'i chu 'dzin 'khrigs //
NK129(to)003:4325: dga' ba'i char gyis gdul bya'i lo tog rnams //
NK129(to)003:4326: dge legs rgya mtsho'i 'bras bu rab smin cing //
NK129(to)003:4327: skal bzang rgya mtsho dpal dang 'byor pa yi //
NK129(to)003:4328: shes bya'i gter la mi 'dzad longs spyod cing //
NK129(to)003:4329: don gnyis rin chen bang mdzod brnyes par 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:4330: chos tshul 'di ni rin chen dpal bzang zhes grags pa //
NK129(to)003:4331: bka' gter phal mo'i don rnams ma lus khong du chud //
NK129(to)003:4332: rgya bod mkhas pa'i grub mtha' kun kyang lkog gyur min //
NK129(to)003:4333: kho bo'i yid mkhar shes bya'i skar tshogs rab tu bkra //
NK129(to)003:4334: ma dag log pa'i skye bo rnams kyis rab rtsod kyang //
NK129(to)003:4335: gdul bya'i snang ngor nam mkha'i 'brug sgras zil gyis mnan //
NK129(to)003:4336: dus matha'i gter ston o rgyan chen po'i gsung 'dzin zhes //
NK129(to)003:4337: theg pa'i yang rtse 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i mchog /
NK129(to)003:4338: deng sang dus na kho bo'i snying la yang dag shar //
NK129(to)003:4339: las can mang po'i blo yi mun pa rab bsal nas //
NK129(to)003:4340: dri bral ye shes thar pa'i gling du mang zhig bskyal //
NK129(to)003:4341: kho bo ma smad ma 'ongs dus na dkon par 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:4342: bka' lung rtogs pa'i shes rab ral gri mkha' la 'phyar //
NK129(to)003:4343: mi shes mun pa'i gti mug dra ba rab bcad nas //
NK129(to)003:4344: shes bya kun gsal bstan pa'i nyi ma rgyal gyur gcig /
NK129(to)003:4345: bshes gnyen dam pas lung rigs phug la legs brtags na //
NK129(to)003:4346: 'dod dgu'i 'byung gnas rgyal po'i bang mdzod ci bzhin 'gyur //
NK129(to)003:4347: deng sang dus na gter gyis bstan skyong rata na gling //
NK129(to)003:4348: o rgyan zhes grags pha de'i rjes bzung bu yin no //
NK129(to)003:4349: ma rtog log rtog phyogs 'dzin dra ba rab bcad nas //
NK129(to)003:4350: khe dang dregs pa rnyed dang 'dod pa'i blo yis ni //
NK129(to)003:4351: tshad mar ma bzhag rang gi 'dod blo kho na yis //
NK129(to)003:4352: deng sang bod kyi slob dpon rnams ni rang che 'dod //
NK129(to)003:4353: gzu bor ma bzhag 'phags pa'i bka' dang 'gal bas na //
NK129(to)003:4354: mkhas par 'dod kyis de nyid yang dag phyogs dang 'gal //
NK129(to)003:4355: de phyir kho bo'i blo ni gzu bor bzhag byas te //
NK129(to)003:4356: rgyal dgongs theg pa ma lus kun la legs par brtags //
NK129(to)003:4357: thos dang mthong ba'i bang mdzod kun gyis phyug byas te //
NK129(to)003:4358: lung rigs kun gyis phyug pa'i blo gros rin chen gyis //
NK129(to)003:4359: phyogs dus kun nas bde legs rgya mtsho'i dga' ston 'gyed //
NK129(to)003:4360: bstan pa rin chen nyin mo'i snang ba rgyas par shog /
NK129(to)003:4361: bdag ni sngon nas phar phyin drug sogs kyi //
NK129(to)003:4362: bsag pa'i dge ba ji rnyed yod pa dang //
NK129(to)003:4363: sangs rgyas bstan la dga' ba gang thob pa'i //
NK129(to)003:4364: dge ba 'di ni pha mas gtso byas pa'i //
NK129(to)003:4365: lus can 'gro ba ma lus thams cad kun //
NK129(to)003:4366: shes bya ma rmongs thams cad mkhyen par shog /
NK129(to)003:4367: chos tshul 'di yang nam mkhas gar khyab par //
NK129(to)003:4368: skal bar ldan rnams 'dod dgu'i dga' ston 'gyed //
NK129(to)003:4369: dge legs rgya mtsho'i dpal la longs spyod cing //
NK129(to)003:4370: sangs rgyas bstan la phan pa'i 'od zer gyis //
NK129(to)003:4371: phyogs dus kun du ma rig mun bsal nas //
NK129(to)003:4372: shes bya'i snang ba rab 'byams rgyas par shog /'di las byung ba'i dge tshogs rgya mtsho des //
NK129(to)003:4373: bdag kyang deng nas sangs rgyas ma thob bar //
NK129(to)003:4374: bka' dang lung rigs bstan bcos la sogs te //
NK129(to)003:4375: shes bya kun la ma rmongs blo gros rgyas //
NK129(to)003:4376: mtha' thug rin chen 'od gsal snying po'i lam //
NK129(to)003:4377: mtha' ru phyin nas kun bzang mchog thob shog /
NK129(to)003:4378: bkra shis dge legs nyin mor byed pa'i dpal bzang gis //
NK129(to)003:4379: lus can kun la rtag tu bde ba'i dpal 'byin cing //
NK129(to)003:4380: 'dod dgu'i re ba skal bzang du mas brgyan pa yi //
NK129(to)003:4381: dus gsum kun tu rnam dag dge ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK129(to)003:4382: zab yangs rgya che kun gyi 'byung gnas rgya mtsho nas //
NK129(to)003:4383: 'dod dgu'i rin chen nor bu mchog ni legs blangs te //
NK129(to)003:4384: skyes dgu kun gyi rnam par mtho ba'i rgya mtshan rtser //
NK129(to)003:4385: 'dod dgu'i rin chen gter la spyod pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK129(to)003:4386: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i gnas //
NK129(to)003:4387: 'gro ba kun gyis 'di la rab tu basngagasa pa yi //
NK129(to)003:4388: sangs rgyas bstan pa rab tu snang ba'i nyin byed kyis //
NK129(to)003:4389: dus gsum kun tu ma rig sel ba'i bkra shis shog //
NK129(to)003:4390: chos 'byung bstan pa'i sgron me rtsod bzlog seng ge'i nga ro zhes bya ba 'di ni /
NK129(to)003:4392: gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor pa /
NK129(to)003:4397: ston zla 'bring po'i tshes bcu nas dbu btsugs te /
NK129(to)003:4398: khrid kyi thun bar la nye bar sbyar te /
NK129(to)003:4399: khyi zla ba'i yar tshes la /
NK129(to)003:4400: lho phyogs mon bod kyi mtshams /
NK129(to)003:4401: g.yu mtsho sngon mo'i mgul bde chen gling gi gtsug
NK129(to)003:4402: lag khang du legs par sbyar ba'i yi ge pa
NK129(to)003:4403: ni / yar 'brog gi slob dpon shes rab bzang pos bgyis so //
NK129(to)003:4404: dge ba 'dis sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa nyi ma ltar khyab par gyur cig //
